\id LUK  
\h Luke 
\toc1 Luke Sut Kipana Thupha 
\toc2 Luke 
\toc3 Lk 
\mt1 LUKE  
\mt2 KIPANA THUPHA  
\mt3 Mijouse dinga huhhingpu  
\is1 Thusim'a thilsoh gilpen Pathen amangsa holdoh le huhhing dinga ahunglut  
\is1 Gospel Luke lekhabu sung thu umdan  
\ip Gospel khat cheh hin ama ama al-na khat cheh aneiyuve, ajeh chu alekhabu sunhon Jesu hinkho le anatoh atahlang dan'u lamdang cheh ahi. Luke hi Paul nungjui ho lah a khat, Juda mi hilou, louthem, Rome gamhop Macedonia apat ahi. Gospel sunga thilsoh ho hi ama tah in anato ahipon, ahin phatah a akholchil dimdem'a amittah a ana muho a kon alahson ahi \xt Lk 1:1-3\xt*. Athu kholgil natoh hin Gospel danga umlou manlutah thusim phabep eipeuve. Luke hin ahithei chan'a athusim lhingkeiya seiding agot ahi, tichu-Jesu pen thusim abulhingset a, ahin damlai thusim, athi chule athodoh thusim ho panna ahi.  
\is1 Lekhabu jihpa chule ajih kum  
\ip Luke, Gentile mi, louthem chule solchah Paul kiloipi pan, hiche gospel hi AD 59 le 63 sunga ajih ahi.  
\is1 Koi henga chule ipi dinga ajih ham?  
\ip Luke in Theophilus kiti Gentile mi, tahsan thah mi ahilouleh Jesu chung chang henom mi hitei dinga ginchat um, dinga asut ahi. Theophilus kiti chu “Pathen ngailu,” tina ahin, hijeh chun kimkhat in hiche lekhabu hi Pathen ngailu ho dinga kijih hi dingin jong aseiyuve. Luke in akineppi chu ahileh Theophilus le lekhabu simjousen Pathen mi ngailutna hi nam jouse–Juda le Chidang namdang chungah akibange, ti ahet diu hi ahi.  
\c 1  
\s1 Thumakai  
\p
\v 1 Mi tampin eiho lah a ana guilhung thilsoh ho chung chang sutdoh agouvin ahi.  
\v 2 Ama hon amittah a mu seijui masaho thulhut amangcha uvin ahi.  
\v 3 Thil jouse abul'a pat phatah a kholchil ahitoh lhon'in, keiman jong chingthei tah a nangma dinga jihdoh ding kakigel lhah ahitai, jana sangpen chang Theophilus,  
\v 4 chutia chu thutah nana kihil jouse chu ahimong nai ti nanopna ding ahi.   
\s1 Gabriel Vantil Zechariah henga akilah  
\p
\v 5 Judea gam'a Herod leng ahi laiyin, Zechariah kiti Judah thempu khat ana um'in ahi. Ama chu Abijah thempu loi lah a khat ahin chule a'inneipi Elizabeth jong chu Aaron thempu khailhah a kon ahi.\x + \xo 1:5 \xt 1 Thusimbu 24:10\x*  
\v 6 Zechariah le Elizabeth chu Pathen mitmun achonpha lhon'in, Pakai dan thupeh le chonna dan jouse chingthei tah a jui ahi lhon'e.  
\v 7 Elizabeth in nao avop theilou jeh chun cha aneilhon pon, chule ani lhon'in hateh in ateh gel lhontai.  
\v 8 Nikhat Zechariah chun Hou-In sungah Pathen kin abolin, ajeh chu chuche hapta sunga chu mopohna chang ahi.  
\v 9 Thempuho chonna ngai banga, ama chu Hou-In muntheng sunga lut a chule thil namtui hal dinga lhendoh hi ahi.  
\v 10 Thil namtui akihal jing laiyin, mipi tamtah pamlangah ading'un taona amang uve.  
\v 11 Zechariah muntheng sunga aumpet in Pakai vantil khat ahengah ahung kilah in, maicham phung jetlam achun adingin ahi.  
\v 12 Zechariah in hichu amu phat in akithing'in hatah in akicha tan ahi.  
\v 13 Ahivangin vantil chun aseiyin, “Kicha hih in Zechariah! Pathen'in nataona asangtai. Na inneipi Elizabeth in chapa khat nahinpeh ding, chule amin John nasah ding ahi.  
\v 14 Nangman kipana lentah nanei ding, chule mi tampi ama pen a kipah ding ahi,  
\v 15 ijeh inem itile ama chu Pakai mitmua hung len ding. Aman ju kiti le khamna thei thil kiti atohkhah thei louding. Ama chu apen masang jenga jong Lhagao Theng dimset ding ahi.\x + \xo 1:15 \xt Minbu 6:3\x*  
\v 16 Chule aman Israel mi tamtah Pakai a Pathen'u henga alehei ding ahi.  
\v 17 Ama chun Elijah lhagao le thahat aken ding ahi. Aman mipi ho chu Pakai hung na dinga agontup ding ahi. Mipa te lung achate chunga aheiya chule doudal lungput neiho michonphaho chihna akisan sah ding ahi,” ati.\x + \xo 1:17 \xt Malachi 4:5,6\x*  
\v 18 Zechariah chun vantil jah a aseiyin, “Hitobang hi aso ding ken iti kahet thei ding ham? Tun keima kateh tan, chule ka inneipi jong kum tamtah alhing tai,” tin adong tai.  
\v 19 Chuin vantil chun aseiyin, “Keima Gabriel kahi! Pathen angsung tah a ding kahi. Ama ahi keima nahenga hiche Kipana Thupha podinga eihin sol ah;\x + \xo 1:19 \xt Daniel 8:16; 9:21\x*  
\v 20 Ahinlah tun, nangman kasei na tahsan pon, chujeh a nangma nathipbeh ding chule nao apen tokah a paothei louva naum ding ahitai. Ajeh chu ka thusei chengse hi aphat cha guilhung tei ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 21 Achutilai chun mipi hon Zechariah chu ahung potdoh ding angah jingun, ipi bol'a hibanga hi sot den hitam tin alungdong gam tauvin ahi.  
\v 22 Achainakeiya ahung potdoh phat chun ama apaodoh thei tapon ahi. Chuin ama hon amaiso le apaothei louva kon chun Hou-In muntheng sunga chu mu anei hinte ti ahedoh un ahi.  
\v 23 Zechariah in Hou-In a athempu natoh hapta alhin phat in inlam'a akile tan ahi.  
\v 24 Phat chomkhat jouvin ajinu Elizabeth chu ahung gai paiyin chule lha nga jen potdoh louvin aum thipbeh tan ahi.  
\v 25 “Pakai iti phat hitam!” tin aphongdoh in “Aman ka chaneilou jeh a jumna eilah mang peh tai,” ati.   
\s1 Gabriel Vantil Mary henga akilah  
\p
\v 26 Elizabeth naovop kal lhagup lhin'in, Pathen'in Gabriel vantil chu Galilee gam Nazareth kho ah,  
\v 27 nungah theng Mary hengah asol'in ahi. Amanu chu Joseph kiti Leng David insung khailhah pasal khat toh kicheng dinga got a um ahitai.\x + \xo 1:27 \xt Matt 1:18\x*  
\v 28 Gabriel chu amanu hengah akilah in aseitai, “Chibai, sahluttah nu! Pakaiyin naumpi,” ati.  
\v 29 Lungdong le lung kika lahlah pum in Mary in vantil thusei chu ipi tina ahi agel tai.  
\v 30 “Kicha hih in, Mary,” tin vantil chun aseitan ahi, “Ajeh chu nangman Pathen lunglhaina nakimutai!”  
\v 31 “Nangma gaiyin natin chapa khat nahin ding chule amin Jesu nasah ding ahi.\x + \xo 1:31 \xt Matt 1:21\x*  
\v 32 Ama hung len ding chule Chungnung pen Chapa kiti ding ahi. Pakai Pathen'in apu David laltouna apeh ding ahi.\x + \xo 1:32 \xt 2 Samuel 7:12,13,16; Isa 9:7\x*  
\v 33 Chule Israel chunga tonsot a vai apoh ding, alenggam in beitih aneilou ding ahi!” ati.  
\v 34 Mary'n vantil chu adongin, “Hinlah, hichu iti hithei ding ham? Keima nungah theng kahi,” ati.  
\v 35 Vantil chun adonbut in, “Lhagao Theng na chunga hung chu ding, chule chungnung pen thaneina in na lekhu ding ahi. Hijeh a chu naosen apeng ding chu atheng hi ding chule ama chu Pathen Chapa kiti ding ahi.  
\v 36 Ipi aval um ding ham, nasopinu Elizabeth in jong ateh nungin nao avop tai! Mi hon aching'ah ahi atiuvin, hinlah tun chapa khat avop in lhagup alhingtai.  
\v 37 Ajeh chu Pathen dingin ima ahimo aumpoi” ati.\x + \xo 1:37 \xt Semtilbu 18:14\x*  
\v 38 Mary'n adonbut in, “Keima Pakai sohnu kahi, kachunga lhung ding nasei jouse hung guilhung hen,” ati. Chuti chun vantil chun amanu chu adalhatai.   
\s1 Mary in Elizabeth agavil  
\p
\v 39 Ni phabep jouvin Mary jong Judea gam thinglhang lang,  
\v 40 Zechariah chenna khoa chun acheloi chel'in ahi. Amanu insung alut in Elizabeth chu chibai aboh e.  
\v 41 Mary'n chibai aboh gin ajah chun Elizabeth naosen chu a-oisung a chun ahung kichom in, chule Elizabeth chu Lhagao Theng adimset tan ahi.  
\v 42 Elizabeth in kipanan ka cheng ahinlon Mary jah a chun aseitai, “Pathen'in numei jouse chunga phatthei naboh ahitai, chule na cha jong anunnom'e.  
\v 43 Ipi jeh a hibanga jana kachan a ka Pakai nu in eihung vil ham?  
\v 44 Nei lemna awcheng kajah chun kasunga naocha kipah in ahung kichom'e.  
\v 45 Anun nom nahi, ajeh chu Pakaiyin asei chu abol ding ahi ti na tahsan e,” ati.   
\s1 Mary in Pathen avahchoi  
\p
\v 46 Mary'n adonbut in “Ka lhagaovin Pakai achoi-an e.  
\v 47 Kalhagao eihuhhing pu Pathen chunga iti kipa thanom hitam!  
\v 48 Ajeh chu aman asoh numei nu dinmun ave jingin, chule tu apat a khang jousen nunnom eiti diu ahitai.\x + \xo 1:48 \xt 1 Samuel 1:11\x*  
\v 49 Ajeh chu Hatchungnungpa chu atheng ahi, chule aman keima din thil loupi abol'e  
\v 50 Aman ahepina akhang akhang'in ama gingte amusah jinge.  
\v 51 Aban thahat chun kichat um tahtah thil abol'e! Aman mikiletsah le hoitho ho athecheh ji'e.  
\v 52 Leng chapa te alaltou nauva kon'in aloilhan mi kineosah te adomsang ji'e.\x + \xo 1:52 \xt Job 5:11; 12:19\x*  
\v 53 Aman agilkel te thilpha phan avah in chule ahao te khutgoh keovin asoldoh ji'e  
\v 54 Aman asoh Israel akithopin khoto dingin ageldoh e.  
\v 55 \x + \xo 1:55 \xt 1 Samuel 2:1-10\x*Ajeh chu aman hiche kitepna hi iputeu, Abraham, chule achate dinga asem ahi.”\x + \xo 1:55 \xt Semtilbu 17:7\x*  
\v 56 Mary chu Elizabeth kom'a lhathum tobang aum jouvin a'inlam ah akile tai.   
\s1 John Pen  
\p
\v 57 Elizabeth chu anaoso phat alhin phat in amanun chapa khat ahingin ahi.  
\v 58 Chuleh aheng akom le asopi chengin Pakaiyin akhotona ho ajahdoh phat un, mijouse amanu toh akipah khom cheh tauve.  
\v 59 Naosen chu niget alhin in, amaho abon'un cheptansah dingin ahung'un ahi. Ama hon apa banga amin Zechariah sah ding agouvin,\x + \xo 1:59 \xt Thempu Dan 12:3\x*  
\v 60 ahivangin Elizabeth in, “Ahipoi, amin John ahi,” atitai.  
\v 61 “Ipi natim?” tin amaho ahung eojah jengun “Na insung uvah hitobang min chu aum khapoi,” atiuve.  
\v 62 Hijeh chun naosen min chu apan ipi akisah nom am ti mit-heiyin adongun ahi.  
\v 63 Aman lekhasutna pheng athum'in, mijouse lungdong in alhan “Amin John ahi” tin ahinjih e.  
\v 64 Chutah chun Zechariah jong ahung paothei tan chule Pathen avahchoi pan tai.  
\v 65 Akimvel'a cheng chengse din kichatna alhung tan chule Judea thinglhang gam sungse ah thilsoh umchan chu akithejal soh tai.  
\v 66 Chuche thilsoh jajouse chun athilsoh ho chu alungin aching geh un, “Hiche chapang hi ipibep ahungsoh tadem?” atiuvin ahi.   
\s1 Zechariah in gaothu asei  
\p
\v 67 Chuin apa Zechariah chu Lhagao Theng adimset tan chule hiche gaothu hi aphongdoh in ahi:  
\v 68 “Vahchoiyun Pakai, Israel Pathen chu; ajeh chu aman amite avil'in alhatdoh tai  
\v 69 Aman huhhing hattah khat asoh David khailhah a kon'in eipeuve.  
\v 70 Athemgao thengte henga malaiya akitepna banga  
\v 71 Tua eiho igalmite uva kon le eihotbolte uva konna huhdoh a um ding ihitauve.  
\v 72 Aman ipu ipateu khotonan akitepna thengho ageldoh jingin–  
\v 73 Akitepna ipuluiyu Abraham kom'a ana kitepna bangtah in  
\v 74 i-galmiteuva kon'in eihuhdoh uve, Pathen kichatna beihel'a ijen theina diuvin  
\v 75 Then na le chondihna a ihin laiseuva dingin  
\v 76 “Chule kachapa, nangma chungnung pen themgao kiti ding nahi; ajeh chu nangman Pakai lampi semtoh sa nakoi ding ahi.\x + \xo 1:76 \xt Malachi 3:1\x*  
\v 77 Nangman amite, achonset nau ngaidam na'a konna huhhingna akimudoh nadiu naseipeh ding ahi.  
\v 78 Pathen mikhotona nemheo vanga jingkhovah chu van'a konna eiho chunga hung kisukeh go ahitai.  
\v 79 Muthim'a touho le thina lim'a touho vah pedinga, chule chamna lampi komu peh dinga ahi,” ati.\x + \xo 1:79 \xt Isa 9:2\x*  
\v 80 John chu ahung khanglen in chule lhagaovin ahung hatdoh in ahi. Chule Israel kom'a lhangphonga natoh apat kahsen ama gamthip lah dungah aumin ahi.   
\c 2  
\s1 Jesu pen  
\p
\v 1 Chuphat lai chun Rome gamvaipo, Augustus chun Rome gamsung pumpia minsut ding thupeh ahin neitan ahi.  
\v 2 (Hiche minsut amasapen hi Quirinius in Syria gam apohlai anahi).  
\v 3 Mijouse ama ama hung kondohna khopi ah minsut na a kijihlut dingin akile un ahi.  
\v 4 Chule Joseph chu leng David chilhah ahijeh chun, Judea gam Bethlehem, David gollui laiya achenna in'a ache angaitai. Chua chun ama akholjin in Galilee gam Nazareth kho a pat in akipatdoh e.  
\v 5 Aman agolngai Mary chu akipuiyin, amanu chu agaiyah ahi akichen in ahi.  
\v 6 Chule chumun a aum laiyun, naoso phat chu ahung lhing tan ahi.  
\v 7 Amanun acha masa, chapa khat ahingin, pon'in phatah in ajel in gan ankong'ah alupsah e, ajeh chu gemun amaho dia onglou anahi.   
\s1 Vantil ten Jesu pen aphondoh u  
\p
\v 8 Chuche jan chun kelngoi chingho loujao anai dungah aum'un, kelngoiho aventup u ahi.  
\v 9 Phulou helouvin Pakai vantil khat aheng uvah ahung kilah in, chule Pakai loupina in akimvel'u asalvah soh e. Amaho akichauvin,  
\v 10 ahivangin vantil chun alhamon in, “Kicha hih'un” tin aseiyin “Keiman nangho Kipana Thupha, mijouse dinga kipana hinso ding kahin pohpeh uve.  
\v 11 Huhhingpu, ahi, Messiah chu, Pakai chu tunin David khopi, Bethlehem ah apengtai!  
\v 12 Chule nang hon hiche melchihna a hi nahetdoh thei diu ahi: Nanghon naosen pon ajol jol'a kitup sel'a kijel, gan ankonga kilupsah nagamu diu ahi,” ati.  
\v 13 Phulou helouvin vantil chu vanmi janel honpi hon ahinjop un–van sepai hotoh–Pathen avahchoiyun chule hitin aseiyuve,  
\v 14 “Van chungnung pen'a Pathen loupi hen, chule leiset chunga Pathen lunglhaina miho lah a cham leng hen,” atiuve.  
\v 15 Vantil te van lam'a akile phat un kelngoi chingho khat le khat akihouvun, “Bethlehem a cheu hite! Hiche thilsoh ho Pakaiyin eiseipeh uhi gaveu hite,” akitiuve.  
\v 16 Amaho khosung a chun kinloi tah in acheuvin Mary le Joseph agamu uvin, chule naosen chu gan ankong a chun analum'e.  
\v 17 Ama amu phat uvin kelngoi chinghon thilsoh ho le vantil in naosen chung changa amaho jah a aseiho mijouse aseipeh tauvin ahi.  
\v 18 Kelngoi chingho thusei jajouse chu alungdong lheh jeng tauvin,  
\v 19 ahivangin Mary'n hitiho jouse hi alungsungah akoiyin khatvei vei kom le ahin geldoh ji'e.  
\v 20 Kelngoi chingho akelngoi hon teu hengah akile kit un, athilmu hou le ajah hou jal'in Pathen aloupisah un chule avahchoi tauve. Vantil in aseipeh u bang chet in thil asoh e.   
\s1 Jesu sopi ten Mose dan ajui u  
\p
\v 21 Niget jouvin naosen chu chep atanpeh un amin Jesu asah tauve, hichu vantil in akijil masanga pat a ana minsahsa ahitai.\x + \xo 2:21 \xt Thempu Dan 12:3; \xt Lk 1:31\x*   
\s1 Jesu hou in a apuiyu  
\p
\v 22 Chuin kisuhthengna thilto phat alhing tan, Mose dan'in chapang khat apen jouva bol dinga angeh dungjuijin; chuti chun anu le apan Pakai henga pehdoh dingin Jerusalem'a ahin pui lhon'e.  
\v 23 Pakai danthu chun hitia hi asei ahi, “Numei cha masa chu pasal ahia leh, amapa chu Pakai henga kikatdoh ding ahi.”\x + \xo 2:23 \xt Potdohbu 13:2,12\x*  
\v 24 Chuin Pakai danthua kingeh bangtah in kilhaina chu atoh lhonin ahi–vakhu kop khat ahilou le vapal ni hiji ahi.\x + \xo 2:24 \xt Thempu Dan 12:6-8\x*  
\v 25 Chuphat lai chun Jerusalem ah Simeon kiti mikhat anaum'e. Ama chu michonpha le Pathen hou guttah chule Messiah ahunga Israel ahung lhatdoh ding kinem'a ngahjing khat anahi. Lhagao Theng achungah achun,  
\v 26 chule Pakai Messiah amutokah a thilou dinga ana seipeh anahi.  
\v 27 Hiche ni chun Lhagao chun Hou-In sungah apuilut in ahi. Chuin Mary le Joseph chun naosen chu Pakai kom'a danthua kingeh dungjuiya ahung pehdoh lhon chun,  
\v 28 Simeon chu anaum'in ahi. Aman naosen chu alan Pathen athangvah in, hitin ati,  
\v 29 “Chungnungpen Pakai, tun nasohpa lungmongin thisah tan nakitepna bangin,  
\v 30 Keiman na mihuhhingna kamutai,  
\v 31 Mijouse dinga nagon chu,  
\v 32 Ama hi namtin vaipi henga Pathen phongdoh ding vah chu ahi, chule ama hi nami Israel te loupina chu ahi.”\x + \xo 2:32 \xt Isa 42:6; 49:6; 52:10\x*  
\v 33 Jesu nu le pa chu ama chung chang thu kisei ho jeh chun alungdong lheh jeng lhon'e.  
\v 34 Chuin Simeon in amaho chu phatthei aboh in chule Mary, naosen nu kom'a chun aseitai, “Hiche chapang hi Israel sunga mi tamtah lhuhna dinga got a um ahi, ahivanga midang tampi a dinga kipana hi ding ahi. Ama hi Pathen'a konna melchihna a hung kisol ahin, hinlah mi tamta 'in adoudal ding ahi.  
\v 35 Chuho jeh a mi tamtah lunggel thuhpen ho kiphongdoh ding ahi. Chule chemjam in nalhagao asutkhah ding ahi.”  
\v 36 Themgao khat amin Anna kiti khat jong Hou-In a chu umah ahi. Amanu chu Phanuel chanu Asher phung'a mi ahin, chule hateh a teh ahitai. A-inneipu chu akichen lhon kum sagi bep sunga thi ahitai.  
\v 37 Chutia chu amanu hin kum somget le li jen meithai hinkho ahin man ahi. Amanun Hou-In adalha ngai pon, asun ajanin aum jingin, anngol le taona pumin Pathen ahou jinge.  
\v 38 Simeon chun Mary le Joseph kom'a thu aseilai chun amanu jong ahungin Pathen avahchoi pantai. Chapang chung chang thudol Pathen'in Jerusalem ahuhdohna dinga gingcha tah a ngah jing ho jouse kom'ah aseiyin ahi.   
\s1 Nazareth khoa Jesu ahung kile kit  
\p
\v 39 Jesu nu le pan Pakai danthu dungjuiya bol dinga lom cheng abulhit soh lhon phat in, a-in'u Galilee gam Nazereth kho ah akile tauve.\x + \xo 2:39 \xt Matt 2:23\x*  
\v 40 Chumun a chun chapangpa chu tahsa damthei tah le hattah in ahung khanglen in ahi. Ama chu chihna adimset in chule Pathen khotona achungah aum'e.   
\s1 Jerusalem Hou-In a Jesu  
\p
\v 41 Kumseh le Jesu nu le pa Kalchuh Kut mang'in acheji lhonin ahi.\x + \xo 2:41 \xt Potdohbu 12:1-27; Danbu Ni Na 16:1-8\x*  
\v 42 Jesu kum som le ni alhin chun angaima bangin hiche kut mang ding chun acheuve.  
\v 43 Kut kichaiyin inlang Nazereth a kile din akipan tauvin, ahin Jesu chu Jerusalem ah aumden tan ahi. Anu le apan atil'in hichu ahedoh lhon pon,  
\v 44 ajeh chu kholjin dang hotoh kilhon khom dan a angaito lhon ahi. Ahivangin ama chuche nilhah a ahung kilulah loubeh phat in asopi aheng akom le aloi agol ho kom'ah aga vele lhontai.  
\v 45 Amulhon loubeh phat in Jerusalem lamah amaholdin akile kit lhon tai.  
\v 46 Nithum jouvin achainakeiyin Hou-In sungah agamudoh lhonin, houhil ho lah a atouva, athuseiyu angaiya, chule thudoh anei chu amudoh lhon tai.  
\v 47 Ama thusei jajouse chun athuhet le athudoh donbut ho chu adatmah lheh jeng tauve.  
\v 48 Anu le apan ima lunggel je jong ahelhon tapoi. Chuin anun ahin seiyin, “Chapa,” “Ipi jeh a hiche hi keini kom'a nabol ham? Napa le keiman mun jouse kahol lhon'a lunggim'a kahi lhon tai,” ati.  
\v 49 “Ahivanga ipi jeh a neihol khoh u ngai ham?” tin adongin, “Nahet lou uham kapa in'a kaum ding mong ahi hi?” tin adonge.  
\v 50 Ahivangin ipi aseina ahi ahedoh lhon pon ahi.  
\v 51 Chuin amaho chutoh Nazareth lam'a akile un chuva chun anu apa thunoiya aumtai. Chule anun hitiho jouse hi alungthim'ah aguh in avop jingin ahi.  
\v 52 Jesu chu chihna le atahsa in akhangin chule Pathen le mihem deisahna in aum tan ahi.\x + \xo 2:52 \xt 1 Samuel 2:26; Thuchihbu 3:4\x*   
\c 3  
\s1 Twilutsah John in lhang asap  
\p
\v 1 Rome gamvaipo Tiberius vaipoh kal kum som le nga lhin kum ahitan, Pontius Pilate chu Judea gamvaipo ahin; Herod Antipas chu Galilee gam vaipo ahin; asopipa Philip chu Iturea le Traconitis gamsungsea vaipo ahin; Lysanias chu Abilene gam vaipo ahi.  
\v 2 Annas le Caiaphas chu Thempu Chungnung ana hilhon'e. Hiche phatlai hin Pathen a kon'in gamthip lah a um, Zechariah chapa John hengah thu ahunglhungin ahi.  
\v 3 Chuin John chu amun amun'ah Jordan vadung pang langto gel'ah achen, mihon alungheiyu vetsahna a baptize achanna diuvin thu ahillhang len chule Pathen henga ngaidam channa dia akilehei diuvin aseiye.  
\v 4 Isaiah chun John chung chang thu ana seiyin hitin ati, “Ama hi gamthip a khosam aw ahi, Pakai hungna ding alampi semtoh un! Ama dingin lampi sutheng un,\x + \xo 3:4 \xt Isa 40:3-5\x*  
\v 5 Phaicham lah kidip ding, chule molboh ho le thinglhang lah kinot cham ding, akon ho kisujang ding, chule mun phol lah ho kisunam ding,  
\v 6 Chutengleh mijousen amu ding, huhhingna Pathen'a kon hung kisol chu,” ati.  
\v 7 Mihonpi chu John henga baptize chang dinga ahung uchun, aman hitin aseiye, “Nangho gulse son ho! Koi ham Pathen lunghanna hunglhung dinga kon jamdoh dinga nagihsal uvah?\x + \xo 3:7 \xt Matt 12:34; 23:33\x*  
\v 8 Chonset a kon lung naheiyule Pathen lam a nakile'u chu nahin dan uva kon'in tahlang'un. Nanghon khat le khat kom'ah, ‘Bitna kanei nauve, ajeh chu Abraham son kahiuve’ tin moh sei hih un. Hichu imacha ahipoi, ajeh chu ka seipeh nahiuve, Pathen'in hiche song hoa konna jong Abraham son le pah asemdoh thei ahi.\x + \xo 3:8 \xt Jn 8:33\x*  
\v 9 Tu jenga jong Pathen thutanna heicha gottupsa, thingphung ajungho tutan dinga phasadem'a um ahitai. Henge, thingphung aga phalou jouse chu phuhlhuh a uma meilah a selut hi ding ahi.” ati.\x + \xo 3:9 \xt Matt 7:19\x*  
\v 10 Mihonpi chun adong'un, “Ipi kabol diu hitam?” atiuve.  
\v 11 John in adonbut in, “Sangkhol ni neiyin, khat chu avaicha ho peuvin. An neh ding neiyin agilkel te jong hoppeh in,” ati.  
\v 12 Lepthol'a natong kaidong ho jong baptize chang din ahungun chule adong'un, “Houhil, ipi kabol diu hitam?” atiuve.\x + \xo 3:12 \xt Lk 7:29\x*  
\v 13 Aman adonbut in, “Gamsung kivaipohna in angeh kalval in kai dong hih un,” atipeh'e.  
\v 14 “Ipi kabol diu hitam” tin sepai phabep khat in jong ahung dongun ahi. John in adonbut in, “Alamlouvin sum kilah hih un ahilou le adih louvin mi hehset bol hih un, chule na losan'a chun lung lhaiyun,” ati.  
\v 15 Mijousen Messiah chu hungvah dinga aginchat cheh u anahin, chule John chu Messiah chu hi ngap hitam ti ahetnom ten'un ahi.  
\v 16 John in athudoh uchu adonbut in hitin aseiye: “Keiman nangho twiya baptize ka chansah nahiuvin, hinlah keima sanga lenjo khat ahunge–nasatah a lenjo ahidan chu keima asoh hi ding le akengchot khao sutlham dingin jong kalhing joupon ahi. Ama chun nangho Lhagao Theng le meiya baptize nachan sah ding'u ahi.  
\v 17 Ama phol jap-ngimna mangcha a changsi le atah lhehkhen dinga phasadem'a um ahitai. Chuteng aman changchilna phol asuhthenga changtah chengse chu achangsal'a asun'a asiho vang chu mit theilou meilhum sunga aselut ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 18 John chun Kipana Thupha miho kom'a aseiphong na achun chutobang gihsalna kamcheng jong amangchan ahi.  
\v 19 John in jong lhangphong tah in Galilee gam vaihompa, Herod Antipas chu, Herodius, asopipa jinu, akichenpi jeh le athilse bol adang tamtah jeh chun demna aneiyin ahi.\x + \xo 3:19 \xt Matt 14:3,4; Mk 6:17,18\x*  
\v 20 Hijeh chun Herod in John chu songkul'ah akhum'in, achonsetna dang toh hiche hi akibelap tan ahi.   
\s1 Jesu twilut  
\p
\v 21 Nikhat mihonpi chu baptize achan laiyun, Jesu ama tah jong baptize achangin ahi. Ama atao leh vanho ahung kihongin,  
\v 22 chule Lhagao Theng, tahsa lim pu'in van vakhu bangin ahung kumsuh in achunga chun achu e. Van'a kon chun aw khat in hitin ahin seiye, “Nangma kangailut tah kachapa nahi, chule kipana lentah neihin pohpeh e,” ati.\x + \xo 3:22 \xt Semtilbu 22:2; Labu 2:7; Isa 42:1; Matt 3:17; Mk 1:11; Lk 9:35\x*   
\s1 Jesu penna khanggui  
\p
\v 23 Jesu chu kum somthum alhingtai, aman japi lah a natoh ahinpat chun. Jesu chu Joseph chapa tin akihen ahi. Joseph chu Heli chapa ahi.  
\v 24 Heli chu Matthat chapa ahi. Matthat chu Levi chapa ahi. Levi chu Melki chapa ahi. Melki chu Jannai chapa ahi. Jannai chu Joseph chapa ahi.  
\v 25 Joseph chu Mattathias chapa ahi. Mattathias chu Amos chapa ahi. Amos chu Nahum chapa ahi. Nahum chu Esli chapa ahi. Esli chu Naggai chapa ahi.  
\v 26 Naggai chu Maath chapa ahi. Maath chu Mattathias chapa ahi. Mattathias chu Semein chapa ahi. Semein chu Josech chapa ahi. Josech chu Joda chapa ahi.  
\v 27 Joda chu Joanan chapa ahi. Joanan chu Rhesa chapa ahi. Rhesa chu Zerubbabel chapa ahi. Zerubbabel chu Shealtiel chapa ahi. Shealtiel chu Neri chapa ahi.  
\v 28 Neri chu Melki chapa ahi. Melki chu Addi chapa ahi. Addi chu Cosam chapa ahi. Cosam chu Elmadam chapa ahi. Elmadam chu Er chapa ahi.  
\v 29 Er chu Joshua chapa ahi. Joshua chu Eliezar chapa ahi. Eliezar chu Jorim chapa ahi. Jorim chu Matthat chapa ahi. Matthat chu Levi chapa ahi.  
\v 30 Levi chu Simeon chapa ahi. Simeon chu Judah chapa ahi. Judah chu Joseph chapa ahi. Joseph chu Jonam chapa ahi. Jonam chu Eliakim chapa ahi.  
\v 31 Eliakim chu Melea chapa ahi. Melea chu Menna chapa ahi. Menna chu Mattatha chapa ahi. Mattatha chu Nathan chapa ahi. Nathan chu David chapa ahi.  
\v 32 David chu Jesse chapa ahi. Jesse chu Obed chapa ahi. Obed chu Boaz chapa ahi. Boaz chu Salmon chapa ahi. Salmon chu Nahshon chapa ahi.  
\v 33 Nahshon chu Aminnadab chapa ahi. Aminnadab chu Admin chapa ahi. Admin chu Arni chapa ahi. Arni chu Hezron chapa ahi. Hezron chu Perez chapa ahi. Perez chu Judah chapa ahi.  
\v 34 Judah chu Jacob chapa ahi. Jacob chu Isaac chapa ahi. Isaac chu Abraham chapa ahi. Abraham chu Terah chapa ahi. Terah chu Nahor chapa ahi.  
\v 35 Nahor chu Serug chapa ahi. Serug chu Reu chapa ahi. Reu chu Peleg chapa ahi. Peleg chu Eber chapa ahi. Eber chu Shelah chapa ahi.  
\v 36 Shelah chu Cainan chapa ahi. Cainan chu Arphaxad chapa ahi. Arphaxad chu Shem chapa ahi. Shem chu Noah chapa ahi. Noah chu Lamech chapa ahi.  
\v 37 Lamech chu Methuselah chapa ahi. Methuselah chu Enoch chapa ahi. Enoch chu Jared chapa ahi. Jared chu Mahalalel chapa ahi. Mahalalel chu Kenan chapa ahi.  
\v 38 Kenan chu Enosh chapa ahi. Enosh chu seth chapa ahi. Seth chu Adam chapa ahi. Adam chu Pathen chapa ahi.   
\c 4  
\s1 Jesun lhepna ato  
\p
\v 1 Chuin Jesu, Lhagao Theng dimset pumin, Jordan vadunga kon'in akile tan ahi. Ama chu gamthip a din Lhagao puidoh in aumin,  
\v 2 hichea chun diabol lhep patep in ni somli sung aum'e. Jesun hiche phat sungse chun ima anepon chule gilkel lheh jengah ahitai.  
\v 3 Chuin diabol chun ahengah ahinseiyin, “Nangma Pathen chapa nahi le hiche song hi changlhah pheng akisona din seiyin,” ati.  
\v 4 Ahin Jesun aseipeh in, “Ahipoi! Pathen Lekhabun mihem changlhah bouseh a hing louding ahi” ati.\x + \xo 4:4 \xt Danbu Ni Na 8:3\x*  
\v 5 Chuin diabol chun apuitouvin, phat chomkhat kah sungin vannoiya lenggam ho avetsah sohkeiyin ahi.  
\v 6 “Hiche lenggam ho loupina le achung uva thuneina nangma kapeh ding nahi,” tin diabol chun aseiyin, “Ajeh chu aboncha keiya ahin kapeh nom nom kapeh thei ahi.  
\v 7 Aboncha nangma kapeh ding nahi nangman keima nei hou leh,” tin aseitai.  
\v 8 Jesun adonbut in, “Pathen Lekhabun hitin aseiye, ‘Nangman Pakai na Pathen bouseh nahou ding, ama kin jeng bou nabol ding ahi’” atipeh tai.\x + \xo 4:8 \xt Danbu Ni Na 6:13\x*  
\v 9 Chuin diabol chun Jerusalem Hou-In tingvum ah apuiyin chule aseitai, “Pathen Chapa nahi le chomlhan!  
\v 10 Ajeh chu Pathen Lekhabun hitin aseiye, Aman avantil te navengtup ding le nahoidam dingin thupeh hin neiyin te.\x + \xo 4:10 \xt Labu 91:11,12\x*  
\v 11 Chule ama hon akhut uvin natuh intin, chutia chu nangman nakengpeh jeng jong song chunga naki suhkhah louding ahi,” ati.  
\v 12 Jesun adonbut in, “Pathen Lekhabun hitin jong aseikit e, Nangman Pakai na Pathen na patep louding ahi” ati.\x + \xo 4:12 \xt Danbu Ni Na 6:16\x*  
\v 13 Diabol chun Jesu alhep patep jou phat in, phat gomkom umkit kah a din adalha tai.   
\s1 Jesun Galilee gam a Pathen natoh apat  
\p
\v 14 Chuin Jesu Galilee langah Lhagao Theng thahatna dimset pumin akiletai. Ama chung chang thulhut ho agamkai pumpi ah gangtah in akithejal soh tai.  
\v 15 Akikhopnau in tin'ah thu ahil jin mijousen apahcha lheh e.   
\s1 Nazareth khoa Jesu kisang talou  
\p
\v 16 Ama Nazareth kho, ahung seiletna khoa ahung chun, abolngai jing bangin Sabbath nin akikhopnau in'ah alut in Pathen Lekhabu sim dingin adingdoh in ahi.  
\v 17 Isaiah themgao lekhajol chu apeuvin ahi. Aman lekhajol chu alhamlhan hitia kijihna mun chu amudoh tai:  
\v 18 “Pakai Lhagao kachungah aum'e, ajeh chu mivaicha ho dinga Kipana Thupha podingin thao einui, Aman sohchang ho akilhadoh diu thu phongjal din eisol'e—mitchon kho amu ding, suhnem a umho kijalen sah ding ahiuve.\x + \xo 4:18 \xt Isa 61:1,2\x*  
\v 19 Chuleh Pakai khotona phat ahunglhung tai,” kiti lai chu asimdoh tai.  
\v 20 Lekhajol chu anungjel in, lhachale pa khut ah anungpeh in, atoutai. Kikhopna in'a mijousen ama chu mitlha louvin aveuvin,  
\v 21 chuin aman amaho jah a thu aseipan tai. “Pathen Lekhabua kisun tua najah u chu tuni tah hin aguilhung tai!” ati.  
\v 22 Mijousen aseipha lheh jengun chule akamsunga konna aphondoh lungsetna thu ho chu kidang asauvin ahi. “Hiche hi iti ham?” tin ama hon adongun, “Hiche hi Joseph chapa hilou ham?” atiuve.  
\v 23 Chuin aman aseiyin, “Nanghon lung opkai loubeh a hiche thuchih hi nei seikhum tei diu ahi: 'Louthem, nangma kisudam in'–aledohna, ‘Capernaum a nabol tobang thil kidang ho chu hilai nakhomun'a jong bol'in’” tiuvin nate.  
\v 24 Ahivanga thutah chu ka seipeh nahiuve, themgao koima ama gamsungah min apom ngaipoi.”\x + \xo 4:24 \xt Jn 4:44\x*  
\v 25 “Tahbeh in Elijah phat laiyin Israel gamsungah ngaichat khoh tah nei meithai tamtah anaum'e, vankot kum thum le akeh akikha a gamsunga kel nasatah ana lhun chun.\x + \xo 4:25 \xt 1 Lgt 17:1\x*  
\v 26 Ahivangin Elijah chu koima kom'ah ana kisol poi. Gamchom mi kom joh a sol anahi–Sidon gam'a Zarephath khoa meithai nu kom.\x + \xo 4:26 \xt 1 Lgt 17:8-16\x*  
\v 27 Chule themgao Elisha phat laiyin jong Israel gamsungah miphah tampi ana um'in, ahivangin Syria mi Naaman bouseh suhdamin anaum'e,” ati.\x + \xo 4:27 \xt 2 Lengte 5:1-14\x*  
\v 28 Hiche thu ajah phat un, kikhopna in'a umho chu alunghang tauvin ahi.  
\v 29 Achomdoh un, aman'un akhochen nau kol mong lama chun apui tauve. Hiche kol'a chu sotlhah ding atiu ahi,  
\v 30 ahivangin akikahlah uva akihehdoh in akiva mang tai.   
\s1 Lhagaoboh voppa  
\p
\v 31 Chuin Jesu Capernaum kiti Galilee gam kho khat ah achen, chukom mun'a chun choldo nikho seh le akikhopnau in'a chun thu ahil ji'e.  
\v 32 Hikom'a jong chun mihon athuhil chu kidang asalheh un ahi, ajeh chu aman thuneitah a asei jeh ahi.\x + \xo 4:32 \xt Matt 7:28,29\x*  
\v 33 Khatvei akikhopnau in'a aumpet in, thilhavop khat–lhagao boh in avop khat–Jesu henga chun ahung pengjah jengin,  
\v 34 “Che mangin! Ipi jeh a kalah uva hung kikumlut nahim, Nazereth Jesu? Keiho sumang dinga hung'ah nahim? Keiman nangma koi nahi kahenai–Pathen Mithengpa!” atin ahi.  
\v 35 Jesun athusei alatan in, “Thip in! ?Hiche mipa a kon chun hung potdoh in,” tin thupeh aneitan ahi. Chutah chun thilha chun mipa chu lhonglaiyah ahin seplhun, mihonpin avetjing lai chun; chuin ama a kon chun ima bolsebe talouvin ahung potdoh tan ahi.  
\v 36 Kidang san mipi ho chun aphongdoh un, “Ipi thuneina le thilbol theina hiche mipa hin anei hitam! Lhagaoboh jeng jong athun anungin, athupeh a kon'in ajam uve!” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 37 Chuche gamkai pumpi a chun Jesu thu chu khotin'ah akithang tan ahi.   
\s1 Jesun Peter nupanu adamsah  
\p
\v 38 Chuche nikhoa akikhopnau in adalhah jouvin, Jesu Simon in'ah achen, hikom'a chun Simon nupanu khosihpi jeh a nasatah a dammo agatoh khan ahi. “Lungset in sudam teiyin,” tin mijousen athum tauve.  
\v 39 A-jalkhun kom'ah adingin, akhosih chu aphoh thip tan ahileh akhosih chun amanu adalhatai. Chuin amanu athoudoh pai ngallin amaho ding anneh sem in apangtai.   
\s1 Nilhah a Jesun mi tamtah adamsah  
\p
\v 40 Nisa alhum toh lhon'in, chuche nilhah chun, khosung pumpia a-insungmi damlou neiho jousen Jesu hengah ahin puiyun ahi. Itobang natna hijongleh akhut in atohkhah chan chu suhdamin aum tauve.  
\v 41 Mi tamtah chu thilhavop ahiuvin; chule thilha ho chu athupeh a kon'in ahung potdoh un, apengjah un, “Nangma Pathen Chapa nahi,” atiuvin ahi. Ahivangin ama Messiah ahi ahetjeh u chun, aman amaho chu aphohthip in thu aseidoh sah tapoi.   
\s1 Thuseiphong dinga Jesu kipatdoh  
\p
\v 42 Ajing jingkah matah in Jesu munthip lah khat ah achedoh tan ahi. Mihonpi chun ama chu muntin aholle un, achaina kheh a amu phat uvin, aman amaho adalhah nalou diuvin atao tauve.  
\v 43 Ahivangin aman adonbut in, “Keiman Pathen Lenggam Kipana Thupha hi khodang'a jong kaseiphong ding ahi, ajeh chu hiche dinga chu eikisol ahi,” ati.  
\v 44 Chuti chun akholjin abanjop in, Judea gam pumpia akikhop nau in tin'ah thu ahillhang len ahi.   
\c 5  
\s1 Nga tamtah amatsah chule seijui masaho akou  
\p
\v 1 Nikhat Jesun Galilee dillen panga thu asei laiyin, mihonpi tamtah in Pathen thu ngainom na jal'in aneh chinto tauvin ahi.\x + \xo 5:1 \xt Matt 13:1,2; Mk 3:9,10; 4:1\x*  
\v 2 Kong ni akeuva twipi pamchin'a akingah amudoh tan, ajeh chu ngaman miho chun adalhah uva alen'u akisop u ahi.  
\v 3 Kong khatpa sunga chun alut in, kong neipa Simon jah a Jesun twi lah a asotlut dingin aseiye. Hijeh chun kong sunga chun atouvin, mihonpi chu chua kon'in thu ahil'in ahi.  
\v 4 Thu asei jouvin Simon jah a, “Tun chen, lithuh langjep ah, na len chu seplhan, nga themkhat man dingin,” ati.  
\v 5 “Pipu” tin Simon in ahin donbut in, “Jan khovah hel'a habol'a kabol u ahin chule ima manlou kahiuve. Hinlah nangman nasei ahileh len seplha kit inge,” ati.\x + \xo 5:5 \xt Jn 21:3\x*  
\v 6 Tu vang'in alen'u nga adimset in akehlha pan tai!\x + \xo 5:6 \xt Jn 21:6\x*  
\v 7 Kithopi angeh nauva kon'in akivoppi hou kong dang khat ah ahungun, chule chomlou kah in kong teni chu anigel'in nga adimset in alhalut pai ding ahilhon tai.  
\v 8 Simon Peter in thilsoh ho amuchet phat in Jesu masangah adilsun chule aseitai, “Oh Pakai, lungset in nei dalhan–keima navel'a um dingin kachonse behseh jenge,” ati.  
\v 9 Ijeh inem itile nga chujat amat jeng uchu kidang asah val ahi, adang ho jong chutima chu ahiuve.  
\v 10 Akiloipi teu, James le John, Zebedee chapa teni jong chun kidang asalhon'e. Jesun Simon adonbut in, “Kicha hih in! Tu apat a miman joh a napan ding ahitai!” ati.  
\v 11 Chule tolgo lah alhun lhun uchun, ama hon thil jouse adalhauvin Jesu nung ajui tauve.   
\s1 Jesun miphah khat adamsah  
\p
\v 12 Kho khat a hin Jesun phat sottah phah nat a dammo khat amui. Hiche mipa chun Jesu amu chun amai tol'a asulut in adamsah din athum'e. “Pakai” tin aseiyin, “Nalung ahileh nei sudam theiyin chule nei sutheng theiye,” ati.  
\v 13 Jesun akhut alhaangin atham'in, “Kalung ahi” tin aseiyin, “Damin!” ati. Chupet tah chun phahnat na chu abeihel tai.  
\v 14 Chuin Jesun amapa chu koima jah a thilsoh ho aseipeh louna din ahilchah tai. Aman aseipeh in, “Thempupa kom'a chen chule aman na vechil hen. Mose dan'in angeh dungjuiya atiphah nat kiboldam peh hon apeh dinga lom ho kichoiyin. Hiche hi japi lah a suhthenga naum phondohna ahi,” ati.\x + \xo 5:14 \xt Thempu Dan 14:1-32\x*  
\v 15 Jesun chutia ahilchah jeng vang chun, athilbol theina thu ho gangjep joh in thejal ahin, chule mihonpi tamtah athusei ngai ding le anatnau damsah nomna jeh in ahung uve.  
\v 16 Ahin Jesu ataodin gamthip lah a achemang jin ahi.   
\s1 Jesun Langthi Khat Adamsah  
\p
\v 17 Nikhat Jesun thu ahil laiyin, Pharisee phabep khat le hou dan thuhil ho ama kom naina ah atou uve. (Hiche miho hi Galilee le Judea chule Jerusalem gam pumpi khotin'a hungdoh hiu leh akilom'e). Chule Pakai misuhdamna thil boltheina chu Jesu kom'ah hatah in aumin ahi.  
\v 18 Mi phabep khat in elbai nakong khat alupna pumin ahin pouvin ahung uve. Insunga Jesu kom pohlut tei agouvin,  
\v 19 hinlah mihonpi jeh chun aphajou tapouve. Hijeh chun inchungah akaldoh un inting aphelhauvin, chuin ama hon adamloupa chu alupna pheh pumin mihonpi lah, Jesu maikoh laitah achun ahin khaisuh uve.  
\v 20 Atahsan jeu amuchun Jesun mipa kom'a chun aseitai, “Gollhang, na chonset akingaidam tai” atipeh e.  
\v 21 Ahivangin Pharisee ho leh houdan thuhil ho chu amaho le amaho akihouvun, “Ama hi koiya kigel ham? Pathen taitom ahi! Pathen bouseh in chonset angaidam thei ahi,” ati tauve.  
\v 22 Jesun ipi agel'u ahen, hijeh chun amaho chu adongin, “Ipi jeh a na lungsung uva hiche hi nadoh uham?  
\v 23 Hoiche joh sei dinga baijo em ‘Na chonset kingaidam ahitai’ kiti le ‘Dingin lang lamjot tan’ tihi? ati.  
\v 24 Hijeh a chu keiman Mihem Chapan leiset ah chonset ngaidamna tha aneiye ti kavetsah ding nahiuve,” ati. Chuin Jesun elbai nakong pa lam ngan akiheiyin aseitai, “Dingin, nalupna pheh kilahdoh inlang, inlam'ah chetan,” ati.  
\v 25 Chuin gangtah in, mihon avetjing layin, mipa chu ahung chomdoh in, alupna akilahdoh in, chule inlam Pathen thangvah pumin achetai.  
\v 26 Mijouse chu lungdkonna le tijatnan alodim un, chule Pathen avahchoiyun, “Tunin thil kidang ho kamu uve,” tin aphongdoh uve.   
\s1 Jesun Levi akou  
\p
\v 27 Phat chomkhat jouvin, Jesun khopi adalhah le, kaidong khat amin Levi kiti akai dkonna mun'ah amun, “Neijuiyin lang ka seijui hin,” tin Jesun aseitai.  
\v 28 Hiti chun Levi jong akipatdoh in, thil jouse adalhan ama ajuitai.  
\v 29 Chujouvin Levin a'in ah Jesu jin-ja-um hinan an-nehkhom abol in ahi. Levi tohkhompi kaidong tampi le maljin dangin jong an anekhom uve.  
\v 30 Ahivangin Pharisee ho leh ahoudan thuhil houvin Jesu seijui ho hengah aphunchel uvin, “Ipi dinga khutobang aboh hotoh naneh uva nadon khom uham?” atiuvin ahi.\x + \xo 5:30 \xt Lk 15:1,2\x*  
\v 31 Jesun adonbut in, “Mi damthei ten louthem angaicha pouve–adamlou ten vang angaicha uve.  
\v 32 Keima achonpha a kigel ho kouva hung kahipoi, amavang chonse ahi kihetdoh a lunghei ding ho kouva hung'ah kahi bouve,” ati.   
\s1 Anngol thudol'a Jesu thudoh aneiyu  
\p
\v 33 Nikhat mi phabep in Jesu jah a, “Twilutsah John seijui hon an angol'un atao jom jingun, chule Pharisee ho seijui hon jong chutima chun abol uve. Ipi jeh a nangma seijui hon phatseh a aneh uva adon jing jengu hitam?” tin aseiyun ahi.  
\v 34 Jesun adonbut in, “Moupui golvahna a maljin hon moulang toh mou aloplaiyuva an angol ngaiyum? Tahbeh in achutipoi.”  
\v 35 Amavang moulang chu nikhat amahoa konna kilamang ding ahi, chuteng tah le ama hon an angol diu ahi.” ati.  
\v 36 Chuin Jesun hiche thutekah hi apen ahi: “Koiman ponhal vonthah a kon'in acheplhan chule vonlui behnan aneipoi. Ijeh inem itileh vonthah chu seding ahitai, chule hiche vonthah hal chu vonlui chutoh kijot louding ahi.”  
\v 37 “Chuleh koiman lengpitwi thah peng luiyah akhum ngaipoi. Ijeh inem itile lengpitwi thah chun savun peng chu aphutjah ding, lengpitwi chu kisujah ding chule peng chu kisuse ding ahi.  
\v 38 Lengpitwi thah chu savun peng thah a khum ding ahi.  
\v 39 Ahin koima lengpitwi lui don'in athah chu adeiji tapoi. ‘Aluipa ma aphajenge’ ati jiuve,” tin aseiye.   
\s1 Jesu Seijuihon Cholngah Nikhoa Changvui Asiu  
\c 6  
\s1 Jesu Seijuihon Cholngah Nikhoa Changvui Asiu  
\p
\v 1 Cholngahni khat Jesun bulei lai ajot lai hin, aseijui ten changvui asihtan un, akhut uvah anoiyun, chang chu aneuvin ahi.\x + \xo 6:1 \xt Danbu Ni Na 23:25\x*  
\v 2 Ahivangin Pharisee ho phabep in, “Ipi jeh a nang hon dan na suhkeh uva Cholngah nia bolngailou changga nalo lhah uham?” atiuve.  
\v 3 Jesun adonbut in, “Pathen Lekhabua kisun David le aloiten agilkel pettah uva ipi anabol'u nasimdoh khah lou u ham?  
\v 4 \x + \xo 6:4 \xt 1 Samuel 21:1-6\x*Ama Pathen in'a alut in, dan asukeh in, thempu ho bouseh in anehthei changlhah theng chu anen ahi. Akiloipi ho jong phabep khat apen ahi.” ati.\x + \xo 6:4 \xt Thempu Dan 24:9\x*  
\v 5 Chule Jesun aseiben, “Mihem Chapa hi Cholngahni chung jenga jong Pakai ahi” ati.   
\s1 Jesun Khut Jetlang Ngoi Pasal Khat Adamsah  
\p
\v 6 Cholngah nikho dang khat a Jesun kikhopna in'a thu ahil laiyin mikhat akhut jetlang ngoi khat aumin ahi.  
\v 7 Houdan thuhil ho le Pharisee hon Jesu chu avelhi keuvun ahi. Hiche pa chu asuhdam poupouleh Cholngah nin na atonge tia ngohna nei ding atiu ahi.  
\v 8 Ahivangin Jesun alunggel'u ahen ahi. Akhut ngoipa jah a chun, “Hungin lang mijouse masangah hung ding tem'in,” tin akou tai. Hijeh chun mipa jong chu malangah ahungin ahi.  
\v 9 Chuin Jesun anelkal ho jah a, “Ken nangho thudoh khat kaneiye. Danthun Cholngah nia thilpha bol aphal'am, ahilouleh thilse bolna ding nikho ham? Hiche nikho hi hinkho huhhingna ding nikho hai ahilou le suhsetna ding nikho ham?” ati.  
\v 10 Aman amaho chu khat khat in ahin golvet vet in chule mipa jah a chun aseitai, “Nakhut lhaangdoh in” ati. Chuti chun mipa chun akhut alhaangdoh in ahile thahsem phat ahitai.  
\v 11 Hiche a hin Jesu galmi ho chu alunghang un ama chu ilo ding ham ti akihou khom tauve.   
\p 
\v 12 Nikhat hitiho jou sotlou laiyin Jesu molchung khat ah taona mang din ache touvin, chule jan khovah in Pathen hengah ataove.  
\v 13 Ajing khovah in aseijui te jouse akoukhom sohkeiyin amaho lah achun solchah dingin som le ni alhengdoh in ahi. Amin hou chu hiche ahi:  
\v 14 Simon (Peter asah), Andrew (Peter sopipa), James, John, Philip, Bartholomew  
\v 15 Matthew, Thomas, James (Alphaeus chapa), Simon (Zealot tia kikou),  
\v 16 Judas (James chapa), chule Judas Iscariot (khonunga ajohdohpa) ahiuve.   
\p 
\v 17 Molchunga pat amaho ahungsuh uchun aseijui ho Jesu toh, mun beh achamlai len khat ah adingun, anungjui tamtah chule mihonpi chun aumkimvel uve. Hichea chun mipi Judea gam pumpi le Jerusalem a kon chule sahlam Tyre le Sidon gam twipang langa pat a hung jong aumun ahi.  
\v 18 Amaho chu ama thusei ngai ding le anatna hou kijendam sah dinga hungu ahi; chule lhagao boh in asuh genthei ho jong jendam in aum uve.  
\v 19 Mijousen ama chu tohkhah agocheh un ahi ajeh chu suhdamna thaneina chu ama a konna potdoh ahi, chule mijouse asudam in ahi.   
\s1 Jesun phattheina chule dana thudol ahil  
\p
\v 20 Chuin Jesun aseijui te henglam ngan aseitai, “Avaichate Pathen'in phatthei naboh uhen, Ijeh inem itile Pathen Lenggam chu nanghoa ahi.  
\v 21 Tua gilkel te Pathen'in phatthei naboh uhen, ijeh inem itile lungnachima naum diu ahi. Tua kap te Pathen'in phatthei naboh uhen, ijeh inem itile phat khat leh nanui diu ahi”  
\v 22 Phattheinan nangah uve, Mihem Chapa najui jeh uva mihon namuda uva napampai uva nataitom uva chule aphalouva nagaosap tengu leh.\x + \xo 6:22 \xt 1 Pet 4:14\x*  
\v 23 Hichu aso tengleh kipah un! Henge, kipah in kichom un! Ijeh inem itile tohphatman lentah in Van gam ah nangah uve. Chule geldoh jingun, apu apateu chun khanglui lai themgao ho jong chutobang chun anabol uve.”\x + \xo 6:23 \xt 2 Thusimbu 36:16; Act 7:52\x*  
\v 24 “Ipi lungkham nan nangau hitam nangho ahaote ho, ijeh inem itile nakipanau chu tua bou naneiyu ahitai.  
\v 25 Ipi lungkham nan nangau hitam nangho tua thaochet a uma ninglhing te, ijeh inem itile gilkelna nasatah phat khat in na ngah jing uve. Ipi lungkham nan nangau hitam tua nui te, ijeh inem itile nanui nau chu kana le lunghem na kisoh ding ahi.  
\v 26 Ipi lungkham nan nangau hitam nangho japin apachat ho, ijeh inem itile apu apateu jong chun themgao lhem ho ana pachat u anahi.”   
\s1 Melma Chunga Lungsetna Nei Ding  
\p
\v 27 “Ahin, nangho thu ngainom ho, keiman kasei ahi, nagalmi teu ngailu'uvin! Namuda teu hengah thilpha bol'un.”  
\v 28 Nasamse teu phattheiboh un. Nasukha teu dingin taovun.  
\v 29 Mi khat touvin nabengphe langkhat abeh le, nabeng langkhat jong dopeh in. Khattouvin na ponlen alah got leh na sangkhol jong peh than.  
\v 30 Athum chan chu pein; chule nathil nanga konna akilahdoh tengleh, nunglah ding gohih in.  
\v 31 Min nang nabolna dinga nadei dan bang bangin midang kom'ah bol'in.”\x + \xo 6:31 \xt Matt 7:12\x*  
\v 32 “Nangman na ngailuho bou na ngailut le, ipi jeh a naki thang-at ding ham? Michonse ten jong angailu teu angailut u ahi!  
\v 33 Chuleh na chunga thilpha bol ho kom bouseh a thilpha nabol leh, ipi jeh a nakithang-at ding ham? Michonse ten jong hichan chu abol'u ahi!  
\v 34 Chuleh nangman nahin sajou ding ho kom'a bou sum naphal leh, ipi jeh a nang kithang-at ding nahim? Michonse ten jong michonse te kom ma'a abon'a nungmu dinga aphal thei ahi.”  
\v 35 “Na galmiteu ngailu uvin! Amaho kom'ah thilpha bol'un. Nungmu ding kinem louvin phal'un. Chuteng van'a kon natohphat man'u chu len ding ahi, chule Chungnung pen chate umchan tahtah natho diu ahi, ajeh chu ama hi kipaje helou ho leh migilou ho dinga pha ahi.  
\v 36 Napau mikhoto them ahi banga nangho jong khoto them nahi diu ahi.”   
\s1 Midang Chunga Thutanna  
\p
\v 37 “Midang chungthu tan hih in chule nang chungthu jong kitan louding ahi. Midang demna thu seihih in, achutiloule na chunga hunglhung ding ahi. Midang ho ngaidam in nang jong naki ngaidam ding ahi.  
\v 38 Pein, chutileh namu ding ahi. Nathilpeh chu aboncha a nangma kom hung kile ding ahi–akison chahkheh, lo chahkheh sa, mun a-konna dinga, letset a chule naphei chunga kisunglha ding ahi. Napehdoh jat chun namu ding jat aphotchen ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 39 Chuin Jesun thutekah hicheng hi aseiye: “Mitcho khat chun midang kaihoi theiyin tem? Anilhon'a kokhuh a lhalut lhon talou ding ham?”\x + \xo 6:39 \xt Matt 15:14\x*  
\v 40 Jillai ho ajilkungpau sangin alenjo poi. Amavang jillai khat bulhingset a kichuh chu ajilkungpa tobang hi ding ahi.”\x + \xo 6:40 \xt Matt 10:24,25; Jn 13:16; 15:20\x*  
\v 41 “Chuleh ibol'a naloi nagol mit a bohhal um chu na lunggimpi ham nangma mit a inkam uma chu?”  
\v 42 Nangma mit a inkam kimu louva, 'Jol, namit a bohhal um chu nalahdoh peh inge,' tia seiding iti nagel theiyu ham? Miphalhem, amasan nangma mit a inkam chu kilahdoh masat in, chutileh nagol mit a bohhal um chu abol ding dan nahet ding ahi.”   
\s1 Thingphung Agan Akihedoh In Ahi  
\p
\v 43 “Thingphung pha khat in ga phalou asodoh theipoi, chule thingphung phalouvin ga pha asodoh ngaipoi.  
\v 44 Thingphung khat chu agan akihen ahi. Theichangga lingphung hoa kon'in akilou khapoi, chule lengpiga jong lingboh ah akilou poi.\x + \xo 6:44 \xt Matt 12:33\x*  
\v 45 Miphan alungsung thil kholna pha a kon'in thilpha asodoh in, chule migilouvin alungsung thil kholna phalouva kon'in thilse asodoh e. Nasei chu ipi hileh na lungsunga hung kondoh ahi.”\x + \xo 6:45 \xt Matt 12:34\x*   
\s1 Song chunga tun ding  
\p
\v 46 “Hijeh a chu ibol'a ‘Pakai, Pakai!’ tia neikou jing uham, kasei bon bollou uva?  
\v 47 Keiman koiham khat kahenga hunga, ka thuhil ngaiya, chule eijui ho chu itobang hidiu ham navetsah unge.  
\v 48 Ama chu mikhat inkhat sa a abulphu ding thuhtah a laiya akhombul song chunga phut tobang ahi. Twi ahungsoa in chu ahin nuh jongleh dettah a kisa ahijeh chun adingdet kheh in ahi.  
\v 49 Amavang koi hileh athu jaa chule nunglou ho chu mikhat akhombul umlouva insa tobang ahi. Twipi ahungsoa hasuh a asuh le alhupai jitai.” ati.   
\c 7  
\s1 Jesun sepai lamkaipa sohpa adamsah  
\p
\v 1 Jesun hiche ho jouse miho kom'a aseijou phat chun, Capernaum langah akile tai.  
\v 2 Hiche lai chun Rome sepai jalamkai khat dinga asoh sahlut tah khat chu hatah in adammon thi ding kon cha ahitai.  
\v 3 Sepai jalamkai pan Jesu chung chang ajahdoh phat in, aman ja umtah Juda upaho asolin, ahinkou uva asohpa ahung damsah din asol'e.  
\v 4 Hijeh chun ama hon jong ngehkhoh tah in Jesu chun mipa akithopi din atao tauve. “Napanpina chang dinga lom khattou aum leh, ama hi ahi,” atiuvin ahi  
\v 5 “Ajeh chu aman Juda miho eilungset un kikhopna in jong eisah peh uve,” atiuve.  
\v 6 Hijeh chun Jesu jong amaho toh alhon'in achetai. Ahivangin in ahunglhun masangjep un, sepai jalamkai pan loi phabep asol'in hitin agasei sah e, “Pakai, ka-in'a hung dingin nang le nang kisugim hih in, ajeh chu keima chutobang loma jana chang dinga kilom kahipoi.”  
\v 7 Keima hungdoh a nangma toh kimuto dinga jong lhingjou lou kahi. Naum na'a kon chun thu chu seijengin, kasohpa suhdam'a um ding ahi.  
\v 8 Ken hiche hi kahenai, ajeh chu keima jong kachunga ho thunoiya um kahin, chule kenjong ka sepai ho chunga thuneina kanei ahi. Keiman “Chen” ti bouseh kasei le acheuvin, “Hungin” katileh ahung uve. Chule ka sohte kom'ah “Hiche bol'in kati leh abol jeng uve,” atiuve.  
\v 9 Jesun hiche thu ajah doh phat in, atija lheh jenge. Mihonpi anungjui ho heng lam angan hitin aseiye, “Ka seipeh nahiuve, hitobang tahsanna hi Israel pumpi sungah kamukha poi!” ati.  
\v 10 Chuin sepai jalamkaipa loiho chu a'inah akile tauvin ahileh sohpa damthengsel'a anaum chu amu uvin ahi.   
\s1 Jesun Meithainu Chapa Athisa Akaithou  
\p
\v 11 Chomkhat jouvin Jesu aseijui ho toh Nain kho langah acheuvin, mihonpi tamtah in ajui uve.  
\v 12 Thivui dinga hung kijotdoh honkhat khopi kelkot phunga chun atohkha uvin ahi. Khangdong athipa chu meithainu chapa changkhat seh ahin, chule khosunga pat mihonpi tamtah in amanu aumpiu ahi.  
\v 13 Pakaiyin amanu amu chun, alungsung khotonan adimtan ahi. “Kap hih in!” tin aga lhamon e.  
\v 14 Chuin thikong lama chun achen atongkhan ahile apoho adingden'un ahi. “Gollhang” atin “Ka seipeh nahi, thoudoh in” ati.  
\v 15 Chuin athiah pasal chapang chu ahung toudoh in thu aseipan tai! Chule Jesun anu anungpeh tan ahi.  
\v 16 Kichatna lentah in mihonpi chu alonvuh tai, chule ama hon Pathen avahchoiyun, “Thil nasatah bolthei themgao khat ilah uvah akisepdoh tai,” atiuvin chule “Pathen'in tunin amite aviltai,” atiuve.  
\v 17 Chule Jesu chung chang thusoh Judea gam pumpi le akimvel thinglhang gamkai ho'ah thechansoh in aumtai.   
\s1 Jesu le John Baptist  
\p
\v 18 Twilutsah John seijui hon Jesu thilbol jouse chu John aseipeh tauve. Hijeh chun John in aseijui te lah a mini akouvin,  
\v 19 chule adong dingin Pakai kom'ah asoltai. “Nangma Messiah kanga jingu chu nahim, ahilouleh achom dang khat kavet nahlai diu ham?” agatisah e.  
\v 20 John seijui tenin Jesu amu lhon phat in aseilhon tai, “Twilutsah John in hiche dong dinga eihin sollhon ahi, Nangma Messiah, kanga jing pau chu nahim, ahilouleh achom dang khat kavet jing nahlai diu ham?” atilhon e.  
\v 21 Hiche pettah a chu Jesun mi tampi anatnau, adammona hou asuhdam pet, lhagao boh vop ho aboldam pet, chule khomulou ho kho amusah pet anahie.  
\v 22 Jesun John seijui teni chu aseipeh in, “John hengah kile lhonin lang nathilmu lhon le nathujah lhon chengse seipeh lhon tan–mitchon kho amun, elbaiyin lam ajot in, miphah ho jendam ahin, nangong'in kho ajan, mithiho kaithouvin aumin, chule Kipana Thupha hi mivaichate hengah seiphong'in aumtai.”\x + \xo 7:22 \xt Isa 35:5,6; \xt Isa 61:1\x*  
\v 23 Chule seipeh lhon'in, keima jeh a kiheimang louho chu Pathen'in phatthei aboh'e,” ati.  
\v 24 John seijui tenin adalhah jouvin Jesun ama thudol mihonpi jah a chun aseiyin ahi. “Itobang mi vedinga gamthip a chu nache uham? Ama chu huimut ling le pengdon anem ham?  
\v 25 Ahiloule ponsil man tamtah a kivon mi mu dinga naki ginchat um? Ahipoi, von hoitah kivon ho leh nomsa tah a hing ho chu leng inpia bou akimui.  
\v 26 Themgao ve nahiu ham? Henge, chule themgao sanga chungnung jo ahi.  
\v 27 John chu Pathen Lekhabu in hitia aseipa chu ahi, 'Ven, Keiman na masangah ka thu lhangsam kasol'e, chule aman nalampi namasanga asemtup ding ahi.'\x + \xo 7:27 \xt Malachi 3:1\x*  
\v 28 Ka seipeh nahiuve, anahing jouse lah a, koima John sanga lenjo aumpoi. Ahin Pathen Lenggam a aneopen jeng jong chu ama sangin alenjon ahi!” ati.  
\v 29 Hiche thu ajah tah un, mipi jouse–kaidong ho jengin jong–Pathen lampi chu adih ahi ti apom'un ahi, ajeh chu amaho John khut a baptize ana chang ahiuve.\x + \xo 7:29 \xt Matt 21:32; Lk 3:12\x*  
\v 30 Amavang Pharisee ho leh hou danthu themhon Pathen thilgon apampaiyun ahi, ijeh inem itile ama hon John twilutsah chu apomlouvu ahi.  
\v 31 “Tukhang mite hi ipi toh katekah tadem?” tin Jesun adongin “Iti kahilchet ding ham?” ati.  
\v 32 Amaho hi kailhang lah a chapang kichem tobang ahiuve. Amaho aloi agol ho kom'ah aphunchel un, 'Keihon moupui golvah la kasauvin, nalam pouve' hijeh chun thivuina la joh kasauvin chule nakap pouve.  
\v 33 Ajeh chu Twilutsah John chun aphat ho changlhah neh ahilou le lengpitwi don kiti ho hin asumang pon, chule nang hon, 'Thilhavop ahi' natiuve.  
\v 34 Mihem Chapan, alangkhat ah, anen adonin, chule naseiyun, 'Milop jukham chule kaidong ho le chonse dang ho jol le gol!' natiuve.  
\v 35 Ahinla chihna chu adih ahi ti anungjui ho hinkho'ah tahlangin aum'e, ati.   
\s1 Chonse numei khat in ngaidamna akisan  
\p
\v 36 Pharisee ho lah a khat in Jesu toh nilhah an nehkhom din angeh in, hijeh chun Jesu jong ama in'a chun achen an nedin atoutai.  
\v 37 Chukom mun'a an aneh ding chu numei jonthanhoi a chonse khat in ahetphat in, amanun songval bom khat ah thao namtui man tamtah kikhum ahinchoiye.\x + \xo 7:37 \xt Matt 26:7; Mk 14:3; Jn 12:3\x*  
\v 38 Chuin amanu chu adilsun Amapa kengmuh achun adilsun akaptai. Amitlhi akengmuh lamah avalhan, hichu asam in athehgo in ahi. Chuin akengmuh chu namtui athe in achop chuh chuh tan ahi.  
\v 39 Pharisee mipa anne a koupa chun hichu amu phat in ama le ama akihoulim in, “Hiche mipa hi themgao ahipou pouleh, itobang numei ham athamkha nu hi, amanu hi michonse ahi! ti ahet tei ding ahi,” atin ahi.  
\v 40 Chutah chun Jesun alunggel chu ahin donbut in, “Simon” tin Pharisee pa kom'a chun, “Thilkhat nakom'ah kaseinom'e” ati. “Sei jengin, houhil” tin Simon in adonbut paiyin ahi.  
\v 41 Chuin Jesun hiche thusim hi aseipeh tai: “Mikhat in mini sum abatsah in–khatpa dangka ja-nga chule khat dangka som-nga.  
\v 42 Ahin anigel lhonin asajou lhon tapon, hijeh chun hepi na neitah in angaidam in abat lhon akahpeh tai. Chujou chun koijoh chun ama chu ngailu jon tem tia nagel em?” tin adongtai.  
\v 43 Simon in adonbut in, “Keigel in abat tamjopa chu,” ati. “Hichu adih e” tin Jesun aseitai.  
\v 44 Chuin numeinu heng lam ngan akiheiyin Simon jah a aseitai, “Hiche numeinu hichea dilsu nu hi ven. Keima na'in a kahung lut chun, nangman twi kakenga vutkhu sillhahna ding neipepon, ahivangin hiche nu hin amitlhi twiyin asop lhan, chule asam in atheh ngim in ahi.”  
\v 45 Nangman chibai neiboh pon, ahin kahung lut a pat hichenu hin kakeng muh achop chop jong anga hih laiye.  
\v 46 Nangman kalua olive thao nuding na gelkhoh pon, amanu vang hin kakeng phang thao namtuiyin anui.”  
\v 47 “Ka seipeh nahi, amanu chonsetna ho–tamtah ahiuvin, ngaidam ahitai, hijeh a chu amanun ngailutna lentah eimusah ahi. Amavang mi akingaidam lhom chu akipah lhom in ahi” ati.  
\v 48 Chuin Jesun numeinu jah a, “Na chonsetna ho kingaidam ahitai” ati.  
\v 49 Dokhanga tou miho chu amaho le amaho akihouvun, “Hiche mipa hi koi hiya michonse jong angaidam ham?” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 50 Chule Jesun numeinu jah a aseitai, “Na tahsanin na huhhing ahitai, lungmongin chetan,” ati.   
\c 8  
\s1 Numei phabep in Jesu akilhon piu  
\p
\v 1 Chujouvin Jesu anai vellah kho ho vil dingin akipandoh in, Pathen Lenggam chung chang Kipana Thupha seiphong leh hillhang le akop in ahi. Aseijui som le ni ho jong akipuiyin,  
\v 2 lhagao boh vop a kon le anatna kisudam numei phabep khat jong ahiuve. Amaho lah a chun Mary Magdalene, thilha sagi anodoh peh nu;\x + \xo 8:2 \xt Matt 27:55,56; Mk 15:40,41; Lk 23:49\x*  
\v 3 Chuza jinu Joanna, Herod sumkolveina vesuipa; Susanna; chule adang mi tamtah Jesu le aseijui te anei agouva panpina hin tohdoh jing ho jong ahiuve.   
\s1 Muchi thepa thulem  
\p
\v 4 Nikhat Jesun thusim khat thulem'in mihonpi tamtah, kho chom chom'a kon hung kisutoa athusei ngai dinga hung ho kom'ah hitin aseiye:  
\v 5 “Loubol mikhat amuchi tu dingin achedoh tai. Aloulai dungah athe len ahileh, muchi abang chu lamsih a achun, chuva chun chotphan aumin, chule vachaten anedoh tauve.  
\v 6 Muchi adang songlah a achui. Ahung khang doh in, ahin akehdoh chu agoplha loiyin asunou ding alhomjeh in athidoh tai.  
\v 7 Muchi adang chu linglah a achun, ahung kehdoh in chule ling chun adeplih jitai.  
\v 8 Muchi adang khat kit chu leipha laiyah achui. Hiche muchi chu akhang in, ga ahin son ana kitu sangin ajat jakhat in agan ahi!” ati. Hiche asei jouvin ahung pengjah jengin, “Koi hileh angaina ding nakhang nei chanin angaiya chule ahetchet ding ahi,” ati.   
\s1 Jesun thulem aseina abidoi  
\p
\v 9 Aseijui hon hiche thulem hi ipi kiseina ham adongun ahi.  
\v 10 Aman adonbut in, “Nanghon Pathen Lenggam thuguh nahet theina diuva phalpehna chang nahiuve. Amavang midang ho hilna a thulem kaman hi Pathen Lekhabua kisun guilhunna dinga ahi: 'Ahin vet tengu leh, amu tahtah lou diu ahi. Ajah tengu leh, ahet theilou diu ahi.'”\x + \xo 8:10 \xt Isa 6:9\x*   
\s1 Jesun muchi thulem ahilchet  
\p
\v 11 “Hiche hi thulem kisei avetsahna chu ahi: Muchi chu Pathen thu ahi.  
\v 12 Lamsih a chu muchin avetsah chu, thu kisei jaa ahivanga agiloupa hunga atahsan theina louding le asochat louna dinga alungsunga kon alahmang peh miho aseina ahi.  
\v 13 Muchi songlah a chu hon avetsah chu, thu kisei jaa chule kipah tah a kisanta, ahivanga jung akhothuh loujeh uva phat chomkhat kah a bou tahsan, lhepna atotengu leh lhuji ho aseina ahi.  
\v 14 Muchi linglah a chu hon avetsah chu, athu ja a ahivanga athujah chu leiset gimna haosatna chule nopsahna hon atomchah a khangdoh thei talou ho aseina ahi. Hijeh chun apilhing thei tapouvin ahi.  
\v 15 Chule muchi leipha laiya chu chun milungtheng, lungthim pha, Pathen thu jaa nung ho, chule lungneng tah a ga tamtah sodoh ho aseina ahi.”   
\s1 Meivah Lheng Akikhu Den Ngaipoi  
\p
\v 16 “Koiman meivah avah in chule lheng'in akhun ahilou le jalkhun noiyah asel ngaipoi. Meivah chu atunna ah akitungin, chuva chun avah chu insunga lut jousen amuthei bouve.\x + \xo 8:16 \xt Matt 5:15; Lk 11:33\x*  
\v 17 Ijeh inem itile akiselguh jouse lhangphonga hung kipodoh ding, chule akiphongdoh lou jouse meivah noiya kipodoh ding mijouse kihetsah ding ahi.”\x + \xo 8:17 \xt Matt 10:26; Lk 12:2\x*  
\v 18 “Hijeh chun iti najah uvem chingtheiyun. Kathuhil ngai jouse, hetthem theina kipeh be ding. Amavang thungai louho chu, ahetsa dan'a agel hou jeng jong amahoa konna kilamang ding ahi.” ati.   
\s1 Jesu Le A-Insung Mite\x + \xo 8:18 \xt Matt 25:29; Lk 19:26\x*  
\p
\v 19 Chuin Jesu anu le asopiho ama toh kimu din ahungun, ahin mihonpi jeh chun ama kom nailut thei louvin aum tauve.  
\v 20 Koiham khat in Jesu aseipeh in, “Nanu le nasopiho polangah aum uve, chule naki mutopi nom uve,” atipeh tai.  
\v 21 Jesun adonbut in, “Kanu le kasopi ho chu koi hileh Pathen thu jabol a athua nungho chu ahiuve” ati.   
\s1 Jesun twipi aphothip  
\p
\v 22 Nikhat Jesun aseijui te jah a aseiyin, “Dil gal langkhat ah galkaiyu hite” ati. Hijeh chun kong sungah alut un akipatdoh tauve.  
\v 23 Konga akitol laiyun, Jesu chomkhat kichol din a-imu'e. Ahin sotlou laiyin, huipi hattah twipi chungah chun anungsuh e. Kong chu twi adim tan, amaho setoh tei ding dinmun'ah achu tauve.  
\v 24 Aseijui te acheuvin aga kaithou un, “Pipu, Pipu, alhalut ding ihitauve!” tin apengjah jeng tauve. Jesu athodoh phat in, huipi le twi kinonglai chu aphohthip tai. Chuin apettah in huipi athip'in ima jouse anomsel tai.  
\v 25 Chuin amaho chu adongin, “Natahsan'u hoiba ham?” ati. Amaho akihoulhi chilchel'un, “Thupeh anei teng huipi le twi kinong jengin jong athu angaiye!” akitiuve.   
\s1 Jesun Gerasene gam a thilhavop adamsah  
\p
\v 26 Hichun amaho Galilee apat in dil gallang, Gerasene gamkai ahunglhung tauve.  
\v 27 Jesu konga konna apotdoh leh, mikhat thilhavop khat ahungin ahung kimupin ahi. Phat sottah amapa chu in beiya chule sagoh keova khopi pam lhanmol lah a cheng ji ahi.  
\v 28 Jesu amu mu chun apeng'in chule amasanga alhu jengin ahi. Chuin ahung peng in, “Ipi jeh a kakom'a hung kikumlut nahim, Jesu, Chungnung pen Pathen Chapa? Lungset tah in, katao ahi, nei gimbol hih in,” ati.  
\v 29 Ijeh inem itile Jesun hiche lhagao boh chu amapa a konna ahungdohna dinga ana thupehsa ahitai. Hiche lhagao boh hin mipa hi athunun ji ahi. Akimattup a thihkhaova akibultuh jeng jongleh, aman imalouva atumtan jia gammang lah adelji, apumpia thilha thaneina noiya um ahitai.  
\v 30 Jesun adongin, “Namin ipi ham?” ati. “Janel” tin ahin donbut e, ajeh chu hiche mipa chu thilha tampin abop ahi.  
\v 31 Thilha ho chun Jesun atosin bei onghom'a asol louna diuvin angeh tauve.  
\v 32 Hiche mun'a chu voh hon tampi mollanga lha ahiuvin, chule thilha ho chun hiche vohchaho sunga alutna diu joh in athum'un ahi. Hijeh chun Jesun phalna apen,  
\v 33 chuin thilha ho chu mipa a kon'in ahung potdoh'un vohchaho sungah alut uvin, chule vohcha honpi chu molchung akensuh apat chun alhaisuh un dillen a chun alhai lhauvin alhum lut gam tauve.  
\v 34 Achinghon thilsoh chu amu phat un, anai vel'a khoho le akimvel thinglhang gam ho ah alhailut un thusoh chu athejal le tauve.  
\v 35 Thilsoh umchan vedingin mipi ho ahung lhaidoh uve. Mihonpi chomloukah in Jesu hengah ahung kikhom un, chule hiche mipa thilha ho a konna kilha ongpa chu amu uvin ahi. Amapa chu Jesu kengbul'ah atouvin, von akivon'in, chule alimgeh tan, chule amaho chu abonun akicha tauvin ahi.  
\v 36 Chuin thilsoh umchan muho chun adang ho jah a thilhavop pa chu iti suhdam'a um ham ti aseipeh un ahi.  
\v 37 Chuin Gerasene gamkaiya mipi ho jousen Jesu hengah agam'u adalhah a achemang nadin angeh tauve, ajeh chu kichatna nasatah huinun chun alodim u ahitai. Hijeh chun Jesu jong kong sungah alelut in adalhatai, dil gallang khat legalkai kit dingin.  
\v 38 Mipa thilha kinodoh peh pa chun ama toh lhonkhom din athum'in, ahin Jesun inlang joh a asol'in, hitin aseipeh e,  
\v 39 “Ahipoi, na insung mite kom joh a chen lang, chule Pathen'in nadinga nabolpeh jouse hi gaseipeh tan,” ati. Hijeh chun amapa chu khopi dung lah a achen, Jesun thil loupi abolpeh ho aseiphong len ahi.   
\s1 Jesun numei chapang athisa akai thou chule numei thisan long adamsah  
\p
\v 40 Dil gallang a chun mihonpin Jesu ana lem'un ahi, ajeh chu ama hon ana nga jingu ahi.  
\v 41 Chuin Jairus kiti akikhopnau in'a lamkai khat, ahungin Jesu kengbul'a abohkhup in a'ina akilhonpi din ahung tem'e.  
\v 42 Achanu changkhat seh, kum som le ni bep chu, thiah ahi. Jesu amapa chutoh alhon khom'in ahileh ama chu mihonpi chun atom chahkheh jengun ahi.  
\v 43 Mihonpi lah a chun numei khat kum som le ni jen thilong'a damlou aumin, amanun damna akimu jou lou ahi.  
\v 44 Jesu nung lang'a pat ahungin, amanun Jesu ponmang athamtai. Apettah chun athilon atang hel tai.  
\v 45 “Koiham ei tongkha?” tin Jesun ahin dongtai. Mijousen ahilounau aseiyun chuin Peter in, “Pipu, mihonpi hin nasuhkhah ahi,” ati.  
\v 46 Ahivangin Jesun aseiyin, “Koiham khat in thamkhah ding lungput neimonga eitham ahi, ijeh inem itile keiya konna suhdamna thaneina apot kahei,” ati.  
\v 47 Numei nu chun ki-immang thei kahi tapoi ti ahet phat in, kithing pumin akengbul'ah adilsu tan ahi. Mihonpi chun ipi jeh a atohkhah ham chule adampai jeng thu ahilchet ho chu ajauvin ahi.  
\v 48 “Chanu” tin amanu jah a chun, “Natahsan in nadamsah ahitai, lungmongin chetan” ati.  
\v 49 Amanu kom'a thu aseijing laiyin, kikhopna in'a lamkai pa, Jairus, in'a kon thupole khat ahung vailhungin ahi. Aman amapa jah a aseipeh in, “Nachanu athitai. Tua houhil nasuhboi chu phachomlou ding ahitai,” ati.  
\v 50 Ahin Jesun thilsoh ajah chun, Jairus jah a hitin aseiye, “Kicha hih'in. Tahsan poupouvin, amanu suhdam'a um ding ahi,” atipeh e.  
\v 51 Amaho in ahunglhun phat un, Jesun Peter, John, le James, chule numei chapangnu nu le pa tailou midang koima toh alut ding anompoi.  
\v 52 In chu mi tamtah akap le amaovah dimset a um ahi, ahin aman aseiyin, “Kap tahih un! Athi ahipoi, a-imu ahi bouve,” atipeh e.  
\v 53 Ahivangin mihonpi chun anuisat un, ajeh chu athitai tichu hoitah a ahet u ahi.  
\v 54 Chuin Jesun akhut in atuh in chule aw sangtah in, “Ka chanu, thoudoh in!” tin aseitai.  
\v 55 Chuin hiche pet tah chun amanu hinna chu ahung kilen, kinloitah in ahung dingdoh e! Chuin Jesun neh ding khattou apeh diuvin aseipeh tai.  
\v 56 Anu le apa chu akipah val behseh jengin, ahin Jesun thilsoh chu koima kom'a seidoh lou din ahilchah e.   
\c 9  
\s1 Jesun som le ni ho asol tan ahi  
\p
\v 1 Nikhat Jesun aseijui som le ni ho chu akoukhom in, thilha ho jouse le natna jouse suhdamna thahatna le thilbol theina apen ahi.  
\v 2 Chuin aman amaho chu Pathen Lenggam thudol mijouse seipeh ding leh adamlou te damsah dingin asoldoh e.  
\v 3 “Najin na diuvah imacha kipoh hih un,” tin ahilchah e. “Tenggol ham, sakhao ham, anneh ding ham, sum ham ahilouleh von khel jeng jong kipoh hih un.  
\v 4 Na chena chan uvah khopi na dalhah tokah uvin nalhun nau in a chun um'un.  
\v 5 \x + \xo 9:5 \xt Lk 10:4-11\x*Chule khopi khat chun nangho lem ding adauva ahileh, na kengphang uva vutkhu ho thinglhauvin, hiche miho chu aso so kiso tauhen tia lhahdohna in,” ati.\x + \xo 9:5 \xt Act 13:51\x*  
\v 6 Hiti chun ama hon khotin'a gamchot apan'un, Kipana Thupha lhangsap chule ana damlou damsah toh abol uve.   
\s1 Herod In Jesu Akimupi Nom  
\p
\v 7 Herod Antipas, Galilee gamvaipopan Jesu natoh thilbol jouse ajahdoh phat in alungboi dentai. Mi konkhat chun Twilutsah John athilah a kon thoudoh kit ahi atiuve.\x + \xo 9:7 \xt Matt 16:14; Mk 8:28; Lk 9:19\x*  
\v 8 Adang hon Jesu chu Elijah ahilouleh themgao ho lah a khat athia kon thoukit ahi atiuve.  
\v 9 “Keiman la John kathat tan,” tin Herod in aseiyin, “Ahileh hiche mipa, athusim kajah pa hi koiham?” ati. Chule ama chu mutei ding atup jing tan ahi.   
\s1 Jesun Mi Sang Nga Val Jen Avahva  
\p
\v 10 Seijui ho ahung kileu chun, Jesu hengah athilbol jouseu aseipeh tauve. Chuin ama amaho chutoh guhthim chan Bethsaida kho langah ache tauvin ahi.  
\v 11 Ahivangin mihonpi chun hoiya ache aholdoh un chule ajui tauve. Aman amaho chu alem in, Pathen Lenggam thudol ahil'in, chule ana damlou ho asudam in ahi.  
\v 12 Nilhangkai vaigei thim lang hin seijui som le ni akom'a ahungun asei tauve, “Mihonpi hi naivellah khoho le loujao dungah soldoh tan, anneh le jan gena ding akimu theina diuvin. Hikom munthip a hin neh ding imacha aumpoi,” ahung tiuve.  
\v 13 Ahivangin Jesun aseiyin, “Nanghon amaho vah un” ati. “Ahin keihon changlhah pheng nga le nga ni bouseh kaneiyuve,” tin ahin donbut un, “Ahilou le kacheuva neh ding mihonpi hijat dinga hi kagachoh diuva na ngaitom?” atiuve.  
\v 14 Ajeh chu chukom'a chu mi pasal sang nga jen umah ahi. Jesun adonbut in, “Mi somnga nga bep a aloi loiya tou dingin seipeh un,” ati.  
\v 15 Hijeh chun mipi abon'un atou tauve.  
\v 16 Jesun changlhah pheng nga le nga ni chu alan, vanlam aven, phatthei abohtai. Chuin changlhah ho chu ahal hal'a asuhkeh toh kilhonin, changlhah le nga chu aseijui te kom'ah ahin pedoh doh jengin, ama hon mipi ho ahoppeh uve.  
\v 17 Chuin abon'un aduchan chan aneuvin, chule chomkhat jouvin seijui hon nehmoh paipeh som le ni alohdoh uve.   
\s1 Peter in atahsanna aphondoh  
\p
\v 18 Nikhat achangseh a tao dingin Jesun mihonpi adalhan ahi. Aseijui te bouseh toh um ahin, aman hitin adong tai, “Mihon kei hi koi ahi eiti uvem?” atileh,  
\v 19 ama hon adonbut un, “Abangin Twilutsah John nahi atiuvin, abangin Elijah, chule adang hon malai themgaoho lah a khat thoukit nahi atiuve,” atipeh uve.\x + \xo 9:19 \xt Matt 14:1,2; Mk 6:14,15; Lk 9:7,8\x*  
\v 20 Chuin aman amaho chu adong'in, “Nanghon la koi ahi neiti uvem?” atileh Peter in adonbut in, “Nangma Messiah, Pathen a kon hung kisol chu nahi,” ati.\x + \xo 9:20 \xt Jn 6:68,69\x*  
\v 21 Jesun aseijui te koi ahi koima kom'a aseidoh louna diuvin agihsal'in ahi.   
\s1 Jesun athi ding le athodoh kit ding asei masah  
\p
\v 22 “Mihem Chapa hin gim genthei tampi athoh ding,” tin ahin seiyin, “Ama chu upaho, thempuho, chule houdan thuhil hon ahin pampai diu ahi. Ama chu tha a um ding, amavang anithum nileh athilah a konna kaithouva um ding ahi” ati.  
\v 23 Chuin mihonpi jah a chun aseiyin, “Nangho koi tobang kanungjui nom naum uleh, nangma chang kingailutna a kon'in kiheidoh un, na thingpel niseh in kiput un, chule neijuiyun.\x + \xo 9:23 \xt Matt 10:38; Lk 14:27\x*  
\v 24 Na hinkho na huhhing nom le nachan ding, amavang keima jal'a nakatdoh le nahuhhing ding ahi.\x + \xo 9:24 \xt Matt 10:39; Lk 17:33; Jn 12:25\x*  
\v 25 Chuleh ipi phatchomna mun natem, vannoi pumpi neiyin lang nangma tah kisusen kisumang le chun?  
\v 26 Khattouvin keima le ka thusei eijachatpi leh, Mihem Chapan jong ama chu aloupina a chule Pa le vantil thengte loupina a ahung kile tengleh ajachatpi ding ahi.  
\v 27 Thutah ka seipeh nahiuve, tutua hikom'a ding ho lah a mi phabep in Pathen Lenggam amu tokah uva thina atolou diu ahi,” ati.   
\s1 Jesu vou kikhel  
\p
\v 28 Niget hamkhat jouvin Jesun Peter, John, le James ho cheng hi molchung khat ah tao dingin apuitouve.  
\v 29 Chuin atao laiyin, amaiso ahung kikhel'in, chule avon'ah ho kidangtah in abangsel jengin ahi.  
\v 30 Phulou helouvin mini, Mose le Elijah ahung kilah lhonin Jesu toh akihoulim pan tauve.  
\v 31 Amaho chu vet dingin aloupi lheh jengui. Chule amaho chu leiset a pat a apotdoh ding thu, Jerusalem a guilhung vah ding thun akihoulim un ahi.  
\v 32 Peter le adang teni chu ihmu lhugam ahi tauve. Akhahdoh uchun, Jesu loupina chu amu uvin chule mini ama toh adinkhom chu amu uve.  
\v 33 Mose le Elijah in adalhah kigot pan laiyuvin, Peter in, aseijeng jong helou khop in ahung eodoh in, “Pipu, hilai mun'a ium uhi anom'e! Liim munthum hetjing nan song uhite–khat nang ding, khat Mose ding, chule khat Elijah ding,” ahinti e.  
\v 34 Ahin, hitia asei jeng vang chun, meilhang khat in alekhu tauvin, meilhangin atomkhum toh lhonin kichat nan amaho alodim tauve.  
\v 35 \x + \xo 9:35 \xt 2 Pet 1:17,18\x*Chuin meibol lah a kon chun awgin khat in hitin ahin seiye, “Hiche hi Kachapa ahi, Kalhendoh pa ahi. Athu ngaiyun,” ati.\x + \xo 9:35 \xt Isa 42:1; Matt 3:17; 12:18; Mk 1:11; Lk 3:22\x*  
\v 36 Awgin athip chun Jesu chu achangseh anahitai. Hiche athilmu hou chu chuche phat lai chun koima kom'ah aseidoh pouve.   
\s1 Jesun lhagaoboh vop chapangpa adamsah  
\p
\v 37 Ajing'a molchunga pat ahung suh jou uchun, mihonpi tamtah in Jesu akimupi uve.  
\v 38 Mihonpi lah a mikhat chun ahin kouvin, “Houhil, lungset in kachapa neivet peh in tia katao ahi, ajeh chu ama bouseh hi kacha neisun ahi.  
\v 39 Lhagao gilouvin aman jin, phulouvin apengjah jin, chule akam ah achilphon alhajin ahi. Ahehlhujin achangin amoh dalhah jipoi.  
\v 40 Na seijui te hengah einodoh pehna diuvin kathum'in hinlah anodoh jou pouve,” ahung ti.  
\v 41 Jesun aseitai, “Nangho tahsan bei le midihlou ho! Nangho itih chan kaumpiuva kakhongai jing ding nahiu ham?” ati. Chuin mipa jah a chun, “Nachapa hikom'ah hinpuiyin,” ati.  
\v 42 Chapang pa ahung machon jep laiyin, thilha chun tol'ah ahin sulhun, nasatah in aveingoi jenge. Ahivangin Jesun lhagao gilou chu aphoh thip in chapangpa chu asudam tai. Chuin aman amapa chu apa alepeh kittai.   
\s1 Jesun athi ding le athokitna ding avel'a asei  
\p
\v 43 Chutobang thilsoh Pathen thilbol theina kidangtah amu uchun mipi chu atiu ajalheh jeng tai. Athilbol ho jouse mijousen adatmah laiyin, Jesun aseijui te jah a hitin aseiye,  
\v 44 “Ngaiyuvin chule ka thusei hi geldoh jingun. Mihem Chapa hi agal mite khut a pehdoh a um ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 45 Ahin ama hon ipi aseina ham ahethei pouve. Athupina chu amahoa konna kiselguh ahi, hijeh chun ahethei pouve, chule doh ding jong kicha kit ahiuve.   
\s1 Alen pen koi ham?  
\p
\v 46 Chuin aseijui te koi alenpen ham ti akinel salah lah jeng tauvin ahi.\x + \xo 9:46 \xt Lk 22:24\x*  
\v 47 Ahin, Jesun alunggel u ahen, hijeh chun chapang neocha khat akom'a dingin apuiye.  
\v 48 Chuin aman amaho jah a aseiye, “Koi hileh hitobang chapang neocha keima thalheng'a sang'a chun keima eisan ahi, chule keima eisanga chun eisol'ah kapa jong asan ahi. Nalah uva aneopen chu alenpen ahi,” ati.\x + \xo 9:48 \xt Matt 10:40; Lk 10:16; Jn 13:20\x*   
\s1 Jesu min pan ho  
\p
\v 49 John in Jesu jah a, “Pipu, koiham khat in namin'a thilha anodoh kamu uvin, ahivangin eiho loilah a ajao loujeh in angah dingin ka seipeh tauve,” ahin ti.  
\v 50 Ahivangin Jesun adonbut in, “Kham hih un, koi hileh na doudallou phot chu nanga ding ahi” ati.   
\s1 Samaria kho khat in Jesu sang talou  
\p
\v 51 Van'a lahtouva aumna ding phat ahung naitoh lhonin, Jesu Jerusalem jon din dettah a kigellha pumin achen ahi.  
\v 52 Aman thupo leho Samaria khokhat ah, availhun na dinga akigot theina diuvin asol masan ahi.  
\v 53 Ahivangin hiche khoa mipi ho chun Jesu chu asang tapouve, ajeh chu ama Jerusalem jona achejing lai ahi.  
\v 54 James le John in hiche amudoh lhon phat in, amanin Jesu jah a, “Pakai, van'a konna amaho gouvam jeng ding mei ikou lhah diu ham?” atilhon e.\x + \xo 9:54 \xt 2 Lengte 1:9-16\x*  
\v 55 Ahin Jesu akiheiyin amani chu aphoh in ahi.  
\v 56 Hijeh chun amaho khochom khat ah ache tauve.   
\s1 Jesu seijui hi dinga kilom ho  
\p
\v 57 ama hon chutia lam ajot laiyun, koiham khat in Jesu jah a, “Nache na chan'ah najui inge,” ati.  
\v 58 Ahin Jesun adonbut in, “Si-al hon chenna ding ko aneiyun, vacha ten gena ding bu aneiyun, ahivangin Mihem Chapan alu ngapna ding jeng jong aneipoi,” atipeh e.  
\v 59 Aman midang khat jah a, “Hungin, neijuiyin” ati. Mipa chu anom in hinlah hitin aseiye, “Pakai, amasan inlam kileng ting kapa gavui masa tadinge,” ati.  
\v 60 Ahivangin Jesun aseipeh in, “Lhagaova thi hon amithi hou kivuiyuhen! Nangma kin chu chele a Pathen Lenggam thudol seiphong chu ahi,” ati.  
\v 61 Achom khat in aseiyin, “Henge Pakai, keiman najui inge, ahin amasan ka insung mite toh gakivailhah tadinge,” ati.\x + \xo 9:61 \xt 1 Lgt 19:20\x*  
\v 62 Ahin Jesun aseipeh in, “Koi hileh akhut a langkon tuhta chule nunglam ve chu Pathen Lenggam a dingin alhing poi,” ati.   
\c 10  
\s1 Jesun som sagi le ni asoltan ahi  
\p
\v 1 Tun Pakaiyin seijui adang mi somsagi le ni alhengdoh in amaho chu akop kop'in khotin le muntin vilding agot naho ah asol in ahi.  
\v 2 Hiche ho cheng hi amaho ahilchahna ahi: “Lousoh ga khoptup ding atam, ahin natong ho alhome. Hijeh chun Pakai hengah taovun ama chu ga chomtup dia mopo ahi; alouva natong ding mi ahin solbe nadin thum'un.\x + \xo 10:2 \xt Matt 9:37,38\x*  
\v 3 Tun cheuvin, chuleh geldoh jingun keiman si-al lah a kelngoi kisol tobanga kasol nahiuve.\x + \xo 10:3 \xt Matt 10:16\x*  
\v 4 Sum le pai ima kipoh hih un, sakhao jong kipoh hih un, kengchot akop in jong pohih un. Chuleh lampi dungah khattou lem dingin kingapa hih un.”  
\v 5 “Khattou in'a nalut tengu leh, amasan 'Pathen lungmon konna hiche in'a hin umhen' ti masauvin.  
\v 6 Hichea cheng ho chu alungmon uleh, phattheina chu umden ding; achutilou uleh, phattheina chu naheng uva hung kile ding ahi.  
\v 7 In khat a kon inkhat ah vahle hih'un. Munkhat bou ah um unlang, ama hon napeh peh uchu neuvin chule don'un. Min phatah a najen nau san ding kiphalam hih un, ajeh chu anatong chun alosan amu ding mong ahi.”\x + \xo 10:7 \xt 1 Crth 9:14; 1 Tim 5:18\x*  
\v 8 “Khopi khat a nalut uva nasan uleh, namasanga ahin luidoh doh uchu neuvin.  
\v 9 Adamlou sudam'un lang seipeh un, 'Pathen Lenggam chu tun nakom uva aumtai' tiuvin.  
\v 10 Ahin khopi khattou in nasanda uleh, alampiu dunga chun chedoh unlang seiyun,\x + \xo 10:10 \xt Act 13:51\x*  
\v 11 'Nakhopiu sunga vutkhu ho geiyin kakeng uva kon'in kathing lhauve, nasoso kisoh dinga dalhah nahiuve ti vetsahnan. Chule hiche hi heuvin–Pathen Lenggam chu anaitai!'\x + \xo 10:11 \xt Matt 10:7-14; Mk 6:8-11; Lk 9:3-5\x*  
\v 12 Ka seipeh nahiuve thupi kitan nileh agilou Sodom kho chu chutobang khopi ho sanga phajep diu ahi”.\x + \xo 10:12 \xt Semtilbu 19:24-28; Matt 11:24; \xt Matt 10:15\x*   
\s1 Lunghei lou khopi ho ada ahiuve  
\p
\v 13 “Itobang lunghem nan na nga lhon hitam, Korazin le Bethsaida! Ijeh inem itile nalah a thil kidang kibol ho hi agilou Tyre le Sidon khohoa kibol hitave leh, sotlaiya pat in amipi hon achonset nauva kon lungheina nei untin, khaodip pon kisil untin chule akisih u tahlang nan aluchung uvah vutvam kiloi tauvinte.\x + \xo 10:13 \xt Isa 23:1-18; Ezekiel 26:1—28:26; Joel 3:4-8; Amos 1:9,10; Zechariah 9:2-4\x*  
\v 14 Henge, Tyre le Sidon khopi teni hi thupi kitan nileh nangho sanga phajep diu ahi.  
\v 15 Chule nangho Capernaum mite, van gam'ah jabolna chang nauvin natem? Nachan loudiu ahi, thina mun'a na chesuh joh diu ahi,” ati.\x + \xo 10:15 \xt Isa 14:13-15\x*  
\v 16 Chuin aseijui te jah a aseiyin, “Koi hileh nathuhil'u kisan a chun keijong eisan ahi. Chule napampai chan'u chun keijong eipampai ahi. Chule koi hileh keima eipampai chan chun Pathen, eihinsolpa apampai ahi” ati.\x + \xo 10:16 \xt Matt 10:40; Mk 9:37; Lk 9:48; Jn 13:20\x*   
\s1 Seijui som sagi le ni ho hung kile kit  
\p
\v 17 Seijui somsagi le ni ho ahung kileuvin, thanom tah in thulhut ahin bol'un ahi. “Pakai, thilha ho jeng jong kathu uvin anunge nangma min kapat ule,” atiuve.  
\v 18 “Henge” tin amaho aseipeh in, “Keiman Satan van'a konna kolphe banga alhahsuh kamui!  
\v 19 Veuvin, keiman nangho galmi thilbol theina chunga thuneina kapeh nahiuve, chule nang hon gul le aipi chunga lam najot diu chule nachilgoi dingu ahi. Imachan na suhkhah lou diu ahi.\x + \xo 10:19 \xt Labu 91:13\x*  
\v 20 Amavang lhagao gilou nathu uva anun jeh in kipah hih un, ahin van gam'a namin'u akijihlut jeh joh in kipah un,” ati.   
\s1 Jesu kipana  
\p
\v 21 Hiche pettah chun Jesu Lhagao Thenga kipana adimset tan, chuin hitin aseiye, “O Hepa, van le lei Pakai, hiche thil ho nangman aching le athem'a kigel hoa pat a naselguh a, chapang ho henga na phondoh jeh in kakipah'e. Henge Pa, hitia kibol hin nangma nalunglhai sah e,” ati.  
\v 22 “Kapan keima ima jouse chunga mopohna eipeh ahitai. Pa tailou koiman Chapa chu dihtah in ahepoi, chule Chapa tailou le Chapa in hetsah dinga alhen ho tailouvin koiman Pa chu dihtah in ahepoi” ati.\x + \xo 10:22 \xt Jn 3:35; \xt Jn 10:15\x*  
\v 23 Chuin amaho changseh aumpet un, aman aseijui te heng lam ngan aseiye, “Na thilmu chengseu mu ah mit ho chu anunnom e.  
\v 24 Ka seipeh nahiuve, themgao ho le lengho tamtah in na thilmu chengseu hi mu ding ana galdot jingu ahin, hinlah ana mupouve. Chuleh najah hou hi jah ding ana galdot jing'u ahin, hinlah ana japouve,” ati.   
\s1 Samaria miphapa  
\p
\v 25 Nikhat hou danthua them khat Jesu patep dingin ading doh in hiche thudoh hi adonge, “Houhil, tonsot hinna kanei theina dia ipi kabol ding ham?” ati.\x + \xo 10:25 \xt Matt 22:35-40; Mk 12:28-34\x*  
\v 26 Jesun adonbut in, “Mose dan in ipi asei em? Iti nasim am?” tin adongtai.  
\v 27 Mipa chun adonbut in, “Nangman nalung pumpin, na lhagao pumpin, na thaneina pumpin, chule na lungthim pumpin Pakai na Pathen chu ngailun. Chule nangma na kingailut bangin naheng nakom ngailun,” tin aseiye ati.\x + \xo 10:27 \xt Danbu Ni Na 6:5; \xt Thempu Dan 19:18\x*  
\v 28 “Adih e” tin Jesun aseipeh in, “Hichu bol'in chule nahin ding ahi!” ati.\x + \xo 10:28 \xt Thempu Dan 18:5\x*  
\v 29 Mipa chun athilbol them akichan nom'in, hijeh chun Jesu chu adongin, “Koiham kaheng kakom?” ati.  
\v 30 Jesun thusim khat in adonbut in: “Judah mikhat Jerusalem a pat Jericho lam jonin ajinsuh in ahi, chule ama chu lamkah ah migucha michom hon abulu un, aponsil aho-lhah peh un, avouvin, chule athisa tobangin lam pang'ah adalha tauve.”  
\v 31 “Thempu khat in agatoh khan, hinlah mipa chuva akijam amu mu chun, lampi pang langkhat joh apal in adalha tai.  
\v 32 Hou-In lhacha leho khat agachen chule chukom'a akijam chu amun, ahin aman jong lamsih lang khat ah apeldoh tai.”  
\v 33 “Chuin musit a um Samaria mikhat ahung pheiyin, mipa amu chun, avoujang nat peh tan ahi.”\x + \xo 10:33 \xt 2 Thusimbu 28:15\x*  
\v 34 Akom'ah ache naiyin, Samaria mipa chun akivohna maha chu ajen'in olive thao le ju asunkhum in, atompeh tai. Chuin mipa chu ama sangan chungah ahin puiyin, in khat ah ahin puilut in chukom'a chun ajenlen ahi.  
\v 35 Ajingin in-ngahpa chu dangka cheng ni apen, aseiyin, 'Hiche pa hi anavesui in. Achunga lutjat hiche sanga atamjoh khah le, kahung kit teng kapeh ding ahi,'” ati.  
\v 36 “Tun seiyin hiche mithum ho lah a chu koipen tah chu hiche mipa gucha michom hon avoh pau dinga aheng akom hi ham?” tin Jesun adong tai.  
\v 37 Mipa chun adonbut in, “Akhoto pa chu ahi,” ati. Chuin Jesun aseiyin, “Adih e, tun chenlang chutobang chun gabol tan,” ati.   
\s1 Mary le Martha  
\p
\v 38 Jesu le aseijui te Jerusalem lam jona achejing laiyun, khokhat ahung lhungun, chua chun Martha kiti nun a-in'a dingin alemin ahi.\x + \xo 10:38 \xt Jn 11:1\x*  
\v 39 Asopinu Mary chu Pakai kengbul ah atouvin, athuhil chu angaiye.  
\v 40 Ahivangin Martha chu jan anneh lentah agon jeh chun alunggim in ahi. Jesu kom'ah ahungin ahung seitai, “Pakai dih theilou nasah lou khattou ham kasopinu thipbeh a atouva ken natoh jouse katoh? Eihung kithopina dingin hinsol in,” ati.  
\v 41 Ahivangin Pakaiyin amanu hengah aseiyin, “Ngailut Martha, nangma hitiho jouse chunga hi lunggima lung himo nahi!  
\v 42 Thil khat bouseh khohsah le lunggimna ding aum'e. Maryn hichu akimudoh in, chule amanu a konna kilamang theilou ding ahitai,” ati.   
\c 11  
\s1 Jesun tao ding dan ahil  
\p
\v 1 Khatvei hi Jesu munkhat ah taona mangin aum'e. Ahin chai chun, aseijui te lah a khat akom'ah ahungin aseiye, “Pakai, taoje neihil'un John in aseijui te ahil bangin” ahung ti.  
\v 2 Jesun aseiyin, hitia hi natao dingu ahi: “Hepa, namin chu thengtah in kikoi hen, na Lenggam hunglhung loi hen.  
\v 3 Niseh a kangaichat u anneh nei peuvin,  
\v 4 chule kachonset nau ngaidam in, kachung uva chonse ho ka ngaidam bangun. Chule lhepna ah nei lhahlut sah hih un” ati.  
\v 5 Chuin tao ding dan ahilben, hiche thusim hi amangchai: “Tekah nan nangma jankhangkim in naloi nagol in khat ah nachen, changlhah pheng thum palah ding nadei jal'in naga chetai. Nangman akom'ah naseiyin,  
\v 6 'Kaloi khat tuchun eivil dingin ahung vailhungin, chule keiman ima nehsah ding kaneipoi, tin nathum tai.'  
\v 7 Chuleh tekahnan, ama chun alupna dan sunga kon chun, 'Nei suboi tahih in. Kot jong tujana dinga kikhah ahitai, ka insung mite le keima jong jalkhun'a kabon chauva umah kahi tauve. Nakithopi thei ponge,' ahinti.  
\v 8 Hinlah hiche hi ka seipeh nahi–ihamtin ajol le agol ahijeh chun bol hih jong le, nangman kot sottah nasuh suh jenga ahileh, ama thoudoh intin nathil thum chan chu napeh ding ahi, jahcha louhel'a napansot jeh a chu,” ati.  
\v 9 “Chule hijeh a chu ka seipeh nahiuve, thum jing jengun, chule nathum chu namu ding ahi. Hol jingin chule namu ding ahi. Kot chu kiu jingin chutileh kot chu na kihonpeh ding ahi.  
\v 10 Ajeh chu athum chan'in akisan in, ahol jousen amun. Chule kot kiu jouse akot kihonpeh ding ahi.”  
\v 11 “Pate ho, nacha teuvin nga athum leh, akhel'a gul napeh um?  
\v 12 Ahilouleh ahtui athum nauva aipi napeh uvam? Henge nape pouve!  
\v 13 Hijeh a chu nangho mi chonsen bon nacha teu thilpha pehje nahet uleh, van'a um napauvin Lhagao Theng iti napehda diu ham athum ho jouse dinga” ati.   
\s1 Jesu chule Beelzebul  
\p
\v 14 Nikhat Jesun mi apao theilou khat a kon'in thilha anodoh peh in ahi, chule thilha chu apotdoh jou chun, mipa chu ahung paodoh pan tai. Mihonpi chun kidang asauvin,  
\v 15 ahin mi phabep khat chun, “Athilha nodoh chu lungdon ding ahipoi. Aman athilbol theina khu Satan, thilhate lengpa a konna amu ahi,” atiuve.\x + \xo 11:15 \xt Matt 9:34; 10:25\x*  
\v 16 Adang hon, Jesu patep nom nan, van'a kon melchihna kidang, athaneina photchetna a avetsah dingin angeh un ahi.\x + \xo 11:16 \xt Matt 12:38; 16:1; Mk 8:11\x*  
\v 17 Alunggel u ahetan, hijeh chun aman aseitai, “Itobang lenggam hileh khat le khat kidouna a kibung khen kiti chu amangthah ding ahi. Insung khat jong kidouna a kibung khen chu lhulham ding ahi.  
\v 18 Nanghon keima Satan in eisuh thahat danin naseiyuve. Ahin Satan chu akikhentel'a ama le ama akidou le alenggam chu iti khantou tantem?  
\v 19 Chuleh kei chu Satan suhthahat kahi leh, nalah uva thilha nodoh ho la? ama hon jong thilha anodoh u ahi, hijeh a chu ama hon nathusei jeh uva chu nahin dem diu ahi.  
\v 20 Amavang keiman Pathen thahatna jal'a thilha kanodoh ahileh, Pathen Lenggam chu nalah uva hunglhung ahitai.  
\v 21 Ajeh chu Satan banga mihat tah khat chu amanchah kimkeiya akivon a a'inpi akiventup tengleh anei agou ho bit ahi–  
\v 22 ama sanga thahatjo khat in ahung bulhu a, athaneina alahmanga, agal manchah achom'a, chule anei agou apoh mang ho ahopcheh kah a chu.”  
\v 23 “ Koi hileh keima toh pangkhom lou chun eidoudal ahin, chule koi hileh eitoh khompi lou chun eidouna na atoh ahi.”\x + \xo 11:23 \xt Mk 9:40\x*   
\s1 Lhagao gilou hung kile kit  
\p
\v 24 “Lhagao gilou khat in mihem khat adalhah tengleh, nelgam lah dungah achejin, kicholna ding mun aholjin ahi. Ahin khatcha amulou tengleh aseijin, 'Kahungdoh na mipa kom'a kile tange,' ati.  
\v 25 Hijeh chun akilen ahileh ana umnasa in chu akitheh thengsel'a chule kitup sel'a aum chu amun ahi.  
\v 26 Chuin hiche lhagao chun ama sanga giloujo lhagao sagi ma amun, chule amaho abon'un hiche mipa sunga chun alut un acheng tauve. Chuin chuche mipa chu amasa a sangin akhoh cheh jitai,” ati.   
\s1 Nopna tahbeh  
\p
\v 27 Hitia thu asei lai chun, mihonpi lah a kon chun numei khat in ahin kouvin, “Pathen'in nanu phatthei boh hen–nahung kondohna naobu, chule nahin chep noi jong,” ati.  
\v 28 Jesun adonbut in, “Ahin hiche sanga chu Pathen thu jaa anatoh a podoh ho chu anunnom cheh ahiuve” ati.   
\s1 Jonah melchihna  
\p
\v 29 Mihonpin Jesu anehchinto laitah un, aman hitin aseiye, “Hiche khang gilou hin melchihna kidang kavetsah dingin asei sei jeng uvin; ahin melchihna kapeh ding chu Jonah melchihna bouseh hi ding ahi.\x + \xo 11:29 \xt Matt 16:4; Mk 8:12\x*  
\v 30 Ama chunga thilsoh cheng chu Pathen'in Nineveh mite henga asol ahi ti melchihna ahi. Mihem Chapa chunga thilsoh jong hiche miho dinga Pathen sol ahi melchihna ahi.”\x + \xo 11:30 \xt Jonah 3:4\x*  
\v 31 “Sheba lengnun, thupi kitan nikho leh hiche khang mite douna a ding doh ding themmo achan ding ahi, ijeh inem itile ama mun gamla tah a kon'in Solomon chihna thungai dingin ahunge. Tun Solomon sanga lenjo khat hikom'ah aum'e–ahin nang hon athu nangai pouve.\x + \xo 11:31 \xt 1 Lgt 10:1-10; 2 Thusimbu 9:1-12\x*  
\v 32 Nineveh khomite jong thupi kitanni leh hiche khang mite douna a ding doh diu chule themmo achan diu ahi. Ijeh inem itile ama hon Jonah thuseiya kon'in achonset nauva kon lungheina aneiyuve. Tun Jonah sanga lenjo khat hikom'ah aum'e–ahin, nang hon athu nangai pouve.”\x + \xo 11:32 \xt Jonah 3:5\x*   
\s1 Jesun vah thudol ahil  
\p
\v 33 “Koiman meivah avah in chule aselmang in ahilouleh lo akhukhum ngaipoi. Chusang chun, meivah atunna ah akitung jin, chua kon chun insung lut jousen avah amuthei bou uve.”\x + \xo 11:33 \xt Matt 5:15; Mk 4:21; Lk 8:16\x*  
\v 34 “Namit chu natahsa dinga vah hin pedoh meivah ahi. Namit chu ahoi laisea, natichung pumpi chu vah dimset ahi. Ahin, aphatmo teng, natichung chu muthim in atom ahi.  
\v 35 Vah kaneiye tia nakigel chu muthim tahtah ahipoi ti kiphot chen in.  
\v 36 Vah a chu na dimset a, aning akah a muthim behlou nahileh, na hinkho pumpi chu, meivah vahtah in asalvah banga vahset ding ahi.” ati   
\s1 Jesun Pharisee ho le danthem ho aphosal  
\p
\v 37 Jesun thu aseilaiyin, Pharisee ho lah a khat in a-in'a anne dingin atem'in ahi. Hijeh chun ama alut in dokhanga atouna mun alotai.  
\v 38 A an vailhun pan, amasa a Juda chondan a khutsil bol louva an nedia atoulhah jeng chu amun adatmo lheh jengin ahi.  
\v 39 Chuin Pakai chun amapa jah a, “Nangho Pharisee ho hin khon le lheng apolam siltheng chingthei tah in nabol'un, ahin asunglam vang anen–kilosetna le gitlouna a dimset nahiuve!  
\v 40 Vo mingol! Pathen'in asung jong chule apolam jong asem gel hilou ham?  
\v 41 Hijeh chun asung lang jong mivaicha ho thilpeh peh a kon'in kisutheng un, chutile apumpia nathen dingu ahitai.”  
\v 42 “Itobang lunghem nan nangau hitam Pharisee ho! Ajeh chu nang hon som'a khat na honsung uva anche aneopen geiyin natoh dimdem'un, hinlah adih a thutan le Pathen ngailut na khohsah pouve. Henge, som’a khat napeh diu mong ahinai ahivangin athupijo thil ho notthap hih un.”\x + \xo 11:42 \xt Thempu Dan 27:30\x*  
\v 43 “Itobang lunghem nan nangau hitam Pharisee ho! Ijeh inem itile nang hon kikhopna in dunga touna thupi hoa tou le kailhang mun lah a navale nauva min chibai naboh ding nadeiyun ahi.  
\v 44 Henge ipi lungkham nan nangau hitam! Ijeh inem itile nangho loulaiya lhankhuh kiselguh tobang nahiuve. Mihon lepthol kibol chu helouvin achungah lam ajot un ahi” ati.  
\v 45 “Houhil” tin hou danthu them khat in ahin kouvin, “Nathusei chun keiho jong eisujum uve,” ati.  
\v 46 “Henge,” tin Jesun aseiyin, “Itobang lunghem nan nangau hitam nangho hou danthu themho! Ajeh chu nang hon pohjou louding houthua ngehna nasem uvin mipi na sugenthei uvin, hinlah nakhut jung khat jong apohgih u ngaijang pehna dingin nalam khapouve.  
\v 47 Lungkham na itobangin nangau hitam! Napu napa teuvin malaiya anathau themgao ho lhan nasem uvin ahi.  
\v 48 Ahin tahbeh in, napu napa teuvin ana bolkhel u napom u vetsahna a ahetoh a napan u ahitai. Ama hon themgaoho anathat un, chule nang hon amaho najopnau photchet nan alhan nasem uve!  
\v 49 Hiche hi Pathen'in achihna a nangho chung chang anasei chu, 'Keiman themgao le solchah aheng uva kasol ding, ahivanga ama hon abang athauva abang abolset diu ahi.'”  
\v 50 “Chutia chu, hiche khang mite hi vannoi kiphudoh a pat Pathen themgao kithat ho jouse chunga mopo diu ahi.”  
\v 51 Abel kitha a pat a Zechariah, maicham le muntheng kikah a kithat pa geiya hiche khang mite kingoh ding ahi.”\x + \xo 11:51 \xt Semtilbu 4:8; \xt 2 Thusimbu 24:20,21\x*  
\v 52 “Itobang lunghem nan nangau hitam nangho hou danthu them ho! Ajeh chu mipi a kon'in hetna kot-heh mihoa kon'in naladoh un, nangho tah jong lenggamsungah nalut pouve, chule adang alut ding jong najada uve,” ati.  
\v 53 Jesun adalhah got toh kilhonin, houdan thuhil ho Pharisee ho chun ahin galmimu cheh cheh un, chule thudoh tamtah doh a suh lunghang ding agouvin ahi.  
\v 54 ama hon thangkol'a osah ding hehset nathei thu seidoh sah ding atiu ahi.   
\c 12  
\s1 Jesun seijui ho atil khou  
\p
\v 1 Hiche pet chun, mihonpi chu asang ajan ahung khang in akisucheh chuh un chule khat le khat kichonkha ton aumun, Jesun hichun aseijui te henglam ahin ngan agih sal in, “Pharisee ho chol a kon'in kihong phauvin—aphatlhem nauva kon'in.\x + \xo 12:1 \xt Matt 16:6; Mk 8:15\x*  
\v 2 Phat ahung lhunge, thil akikhukhum jouse kiphongdoh ding ahi, chule aguha um jouse jong mijouse kom'a kihetsah ding ahi.\x + \xo 12:2 \xt Mk 4:22; Lk 8:17\x*  
\v 3 Muthim'a nasei jouseu chu khovah a kija ding ahi, chule kot kikhakhum na a olcha nakiseipeh toujong chu inchunga mijouse jah a kisamphong ding ahi!   
\s1 Gin Ding Koipen Ham?  
\p
\v 4 “Ngailut umtah jol le gol te, natahsa that thei ho chu kicha hih un.” Hiche jou le chun na chungah ima abolthei tapouve.  
\v 5 Ahin kichat ding koi ham naseipeh unge. Pathen kichauvin, aman nangho thana thei le damun'a lelutna thei thilbol theina tha anei ahi. Henge, kichat ding ama ahi .”  
\v 6 “Vasah nga man ijat ham–paisa ni man ham? Ahin Pathen'in khat jeng jong asumil pon ahi.  
\v 7 Chuleh nalu'a na samjang ho jeng jong aboncha kisimtoh soh ahitai. Hijeh chun kicha hih un; nangma vasah honpi jouse sanga manlujo nahi.”   
\s1 Mihem masanga Christa phondoh ding  
\p
\v 8 “Ka seipeh nahiuve, koi hileh hiche leiset a lhangphonga keima eiseidoh chan chu, Mihem Chapan jong Pathen Vantil te jaona a aseidoh ding ahi.  
\v 9 Amavang koi hileh hiche leiset a eiseilep chan chu Pathen Vantil te masanga kiseilep diu ahi.  
\v 10 Koi hileh Mihem Chapa douna thusei chan chu kingaidam ding ahi, amavang koi hileh Lhagao Theng taitom'ah vang chu kingaidam louding ahi.”\x + \xo 12:10 \xt Matt 12:32; Mk 3:29\x*  
\v 11 “Chuleh kikhopna in'a vaipo ho leh thuneiho anga athu tan dinga nahin kai tengu leh, iti nakiven ding ham ahilou le ipi nasei ding thu ah lunggim hih un.\x + \xo 12:11 \xt Matt 10:19,20; Mk 13:11; Lk 21:14,15\x*  
\v 12 Ajeh chu Lhagao Theng chun apettah a seiding napeh diu ahi,” ati.   
\s1 Hao jeh a ngolpa thulem  
\p
\v 13 Chuin koiham khat in mipi lah a kon chun ahin kouvin, “Houhil, kasopipa jah a kapa nei le gou eikihoppina dingin seiyin,” ati.  
\v 14 Jesun adonbut in, “Jol, kon nangni kah a thutan'a eipansah a, hiti khati iti kagel lhah ding ham?” ati.  
\v 15 Chuin aman aseiben, “Chingtheiyun! Neipap kiloset kiti jouseah kivengun. Hinkho hi nanei jat a kisim ahipoi,” ati.  
\v 16 Chuin aman thusim khat aseipeh tai: “Mihao khat hin loumun khat, alei phatah, ga hoitah tah sodoh aneiyin ahi.  
\v 17 Amapa achangin akihoulim in, ‘Ipi kabol ding hitam? Ka lousoh ga jouse koina ding mun la kanei pon,’ ati.  
\v 18 Chuin aman aseiyin, 'Kahetai! Ka changsal jouse phelha'ng ting asanga lenjo cheh thahsah inge. Chutileh keiman ka chang le mim jouse kholkhomna ding dan ninglhingset in nei tange.'  
\v 19 Chutengleh keima nomtah a katouva keima le keiman hitia hi kasei ding ahi, “Kajol, nangman kum sottah a ding ninglhing set a kikhol khom naneiye. Tun lung olmo hih in! nen lang, don'in lang, chule kipah in!” tinge ati.  
\v 20 “Ahivangin Pathen'in amapa jah a chun, 'Mingol! Tujan ma ma'a nathi ding ahitai. Chutengleh nanatoh ga jouse hi koi chang tantem?' ati.  
\v 21 “Henge, lei gouthil bouseh kholkhom'a Pathen toh haosatah a kiguijopna neilou mi chu angol ahi” ati.   
\s1 Lungkham hih un  
\p
\v 22 Chuin, aseijui te kom lang ngan Jesun aseitai, “Hiche jeh a hi keiman nitin hinkho a dingin lunggim hih un kati ahi—neh le chah ninglhing set a chule sil le chen lhingset a kanei ding hinam tin.  
\v 23 Ajeh chu hinkho hi anneh ding sanga lujo, chule natahsa jong sil le chen sanga lujo ahi.  
\v 24 Va-ah ho khu veuvin, ama hon tula atu pouvin, at la a-at pouvin ahilou le khol la akholkhom pouvin, ajeh chu Pathen'in avahnai. Chule nangho vacha ho sanga ama dinga loupijo nahiuve!  
\v 25 Nalunggim nau jousen nahinkho phatbih khat ajopbe theiyem?  
\v 26 Chule lunggim nan imacha chutobang thil neocha jong alolhin sah theilou leh, thil lentah chunga jong lunggim chu ipi phachom ding ham?”  
\v 27 “Lily pah ho le akhan doh dan khu veuvin. Ama hon na jong atong pouvin chule avon hou jong akisem thei pouvin, ahin, Solomon jeng jong, aloupina jouse a akivon chun amaho tobang lom'in ahoijou poi.\x + \xo 12:27 \xt 1 Lgt 10:4-7; 2 Thusimbu 9:3-6\x*  
\v 28 Chuleh Pathen'in pahcha ho tunia uma jinga meilhum sunga selut ding bon kidangtah a akhohsah a ahileh, aman nangma thon louva na khohsah teitei ding ahi. Ipi bol'a hibanga tahsanna neo hi naneiyu ham?”  
\v 29 “Chuleh ipi kaneh ding ham ipi kadon ding ham tin lungboi hih un. Hiche ho thil'a chun lunggim hih un.  
\v 30 Hiche thil ho hin vannoi pumpia atahsanlou ho lungsung alodim'in ahi, ahivangin Napauvin na ngaichat chengseu chu ahemasa jitai.  
\v 31 Pathen Lenggam chu thil jouse sangin hol'un, chule aman na ngaichat chan'u napeh diu ahi.”   
\s1 Van'a gou khol  
\p
\v 32 “Hijeh chun kicha hih un, hon lhom ho. Ajeh chu nangho lenggam peh ding hi napau dinga kipana lentah ahi.”  
\v 33 “Nanei nagou ho joh un lang angaicha ho peuvin. Hichun van'a gou nakhol peh dingu ahi! Chule van gam a sumdip hon chultih anei pouvin chule atovong aum khapoi. Nagou khol chu bitkeiya um ding ahi; guchan jong aguhmang theilou ding ahi chule nget in jong asuhset theilou ding ahi.  
\v 34 Nanei nagou umna'a chu nalung ngaichat jong aum ding ahi.”   
\s1 Hetman Louva Jesu Hung Kit Ding  
\p
\v 35 “Natohna dingin kivontup san umun chule na thaomei vah jing'un;\x + \xo 12:35 \xt Matt 25:1-13\x*  
\v 36 na Pakai pa moupui golvah na a kon ahung kile ding nanga bangin. Chutileh ahung lhun'a kot ahinsuh tengleh kot nahonpeh a nalutsah theina dia phasadema naum ding ahi.\x + \xo 12:36 \xt Mk 13:34-36\x*  
\v 37 Soh ho kiging jinga umho le ahung kile ding ngah jing ho chu kipaman kipe diu ahi. Thutah kaseipeh nahiuve, ama tah in amaho chu atousah ding, atai akikhi ding, amaho chu atou uva aneh laiyuva chu ajen ding ahi!  
\v 38 Ama jankim lah ahilou le khovah kon'a hung maithei ahi. Ahin, ahung pet a kiging jinga um sohte chu kipaman apeh ding ahiuve.”  
\v 39 “Hiche hi hethem in, in-neipan itih phatchet a gucha hung ding ham ti heleh, aman a-in chu veihonga aumsah louding ahi.\x + \xo 12:39 \xt Matt 24:43,44\x*  
\v 40 Nangjong kiging jinga naum jing ding ahi ijeh inem itile Mihem Chapa chu naginchat lou pettah uva hung ding ahi,” ati.   
\s1 Lhacha kitah chule lhacha kitahlou  
\p
\v 41 Peter in adongin, “Pakai hiche thutekah chu keihoa ding bou hai mijousea ding ham?” ati.  
\v 42 Chuin Pakaiyin adonbut in, “Soh kitah le lung limgeh chu apakai pan insung pumpi le sohdang ho chunga jong mopohna apeh a avahsah ho chu ahi.  
\v 43 Apakai pa ahung kile a asohpan na phatah a atoh ahung mu leh, kipaman um ding ahi.  
\v 44 Thutah ka seipeh nahiuve, hitobang soh chu apakai pan anei jouse chunga mopohna apeh ding ahi.  
\v 45 Ahinlah, iti tantem asohpa chun, 'Kapakai pa hi tem'in hung ponte' tin gel henlang, asoh dang ho vohen, neh nom nehen, ju kham kham jeng taleh?  
\v 46 Apakai pa chu seiphong masalou leh ginchat umlou pettah in hungin tin, chuteng aman asohpa chu asat goi goi ding mikitahlou ho toh asolmang tha ding ahitai.”  
\v 47 “Chule soh khat apakai pa dei he'a, ahivanga kigongtup lou chule akihilchahna ho tongdoh lou chu, nasatah a bolgimna ato ding ahi.  
\v 48 Ahivanga ahelou khattou chun thilse abol leh, ama chu gihsa louva kigimbol ding ahi. Koiham khat chu tamtah akipeh le, ama a konna chu tamtah kile ngeh ding ahi; chuleh khattou chu mopohna tamtah akipeh le, asanga tamjo chu kingeh ding ahi.”  
\v 49 “Keima vannoi hi meiya tih dinga kahung ahi, chule akoudoh hitaleh kati lheh jenge!  
\v 50 Keiman thoh hahsa tah baptize chan ding kamakho'ah kaneiye chule hichu akimolso kah a kalung khamna iti san tam!\x + \xo 12:50 \xt Mk 10:38\x*  
\v 51 Leiset a chamna hinpo dinga hunga nei gel'um? Ahipoi, keima miho kibung khensah dia hung'ah kahi!  
\v 52 Tu apat a insung ho kikhentel diu ahitai, thum'in eijop uva, nin eidoudal ding–ahilou le nin eijop a thum'in eidou ding ahi.  
\v 53 'Mipa chu chapa douna a chule chapa chu mipa douna a kibungkhen ding ahi; chanu douna minu chule minu douna a chanu; chuleh ateh in mou douna chule mouvin ateh douna a kikhenna um ding ahi'” ati.   
\s1 Phat Kihei Dan Hetna\x + \xo 12:53 \xt Micah 7:6\x*  
\p
\v 54 Chuin Jesun mihonpi lam aven aseiye, “Nanghon meibol lhumlam langa ahung umdoh phat le, nasei jiuvin, ‘Go hung juding ahi’ natiuve. Chuleh nangho nadih uve.  
\v 55 Lhanglam hui ahung nun tengleh, nasei jiuvin, ‘Tuni chu salheh ding ahi’ natiuvin, chule achuti ji'e.  
\v 56 Nangho mingol ho! Nanghon leiset chunga van umje nasuto theiyun, ahin nang hon tuphat umdan na ledoh thei pouve.”   
\s1 Nahehpa chutoh kicham teiyin  
\p
\v 57 “Ipi jeh a nangho dinga adih chu naki gellhah theilou uham?  
\v 58 Nangho thukitanna mun'a nahehse hou toh nache tengu leh, amun nalhun masangin kihoutohpi ding gon. Achuti louleh thutan vaihompa masanga nahehse pan nakai ding, aman vaipopa henga napehdoh a, aman songkul'a nakhum ding ahi.  
\v 59 Chule hichu aso leh nangman achainapen sum geiya napeh doh masang sea itinama jongleh nakilhadoh louhel ding ahi,” ati.   
\c 13  
\s1 Jesun lungheiyun tia asap phong  
\p
\v 1 Hiche phatlai hin Pilate in Galilee gam mi phabep in Hou-In a kilhaina gantha abollaiyun athat e tithu Jesu seipeh in aumin ahi.  
\v 2 “Hiche Galilee miho chu Galilee gam midang ho jouse sanga chonse joa na ngaito uvam?” tin Jesun adongin, “Hijeh a chu chutia thoh genthei athoh u ahi natiuvem?  
\v 3 Ahipoi, ka seipeh nahiuve, nalung nahei uva Pathen lam'a nakihei lou uleh nangho jong mangthah ding nahiuve.  
\v 4 Chuleh Siloam inting achima adellih mi som le get ho chu la? Amaho chu Jerusalem a dinga michonse pen ho hitauvam?  
\v 5 Ahipoi, chule ka seipeh kit nahiuve, nalung nahei lou uleh na manthah diu ahi” ati.   
\s1 Theichang aga umlou  
\p
\v 6 Chuin Jesun hiche thusim hi ahin seiye: “Mikhat in ahonsung ah theichang phungkhat atun chule avel vel in aga um ding ham tin ahung vejin, hinlah amapa alunglha lheh jeng jin ahi.  
\v 7 Achainan, hon lhoupa jah a, 'Kumthum hulteh kanga ahitai, ahin tuchan'in theichang khatbeh jong aga poi! Phuhlhu uvin,” ati. Honsungah mun alobep seuvin anohphah e,' ati.  
\v 8 “Hon lhoupan adonbut in, ‘Pakai phat khatvei peh ben, kumkhat umsah ben, chule keiman phate chan vesui ingting leiphatna ding tampi sung inge.  
\v 9 Khovei leh theichang imu le aphai. Imulou uleh, na phuhlhuh thei ahitai ati,'” tin aseiye.   
\s1 Jesun cholngah nikhoa aboldam  
\p
\v 10 Cholngahni khat hi Jesun kikhopna in'a thu ahil pet hin,  
\v 11 Numei khat lhagao boh in lamjot moa alha amui. Kum som le get jen tingbong'a dingjang thei louva alha ahi.  
\v 12 Jesun amanu amu chun, ahin kouvin aseitai, “Ngailut umtah numeinu, na natna a konna kisudam'ah nahitai!” ati.  
\v 13 Chuin amanu chu atham'in ahileh amanu jong chupettah chun adingjang thei tai. Pathen iti avahchoi hitam!  
\v 14 Ahivangin kikhopna in'a lhacha mopopa chun cholngah nia amisuhdam jeh chun nommo asan. “Hapta sunga nigup natohna ding um ahi,” tin mihonpi jah a chun, “Hiche nikho ho a chun hungun, Cholngahni hilouvin” ati.\x + \xo 13:14 \xt Potdohbu 20:9,10; Danbu Ni Na 5:13,14\x*  
\v 15 Ahivangin Pakaiyin adonbut in, “Miphalhem ho! Nabon uva Cholngah nia na natoh sohkeiyu chula! Na bongchal ham ahilou le na sangan ham Cholngah nia akihenna a pat a sutlham'a twi donsah dia napui jiu hilou ham?  
\v 16 Hiche lungset umtah numeinu, Abraham chanu hi, Satan in kum som le get jen soh a ahentang ahi. Cholngahni hijongleh chutobang suhdam chu dihlou ham?” ati.  
\v 17 Hichun agalmi ho asujum in, ahin mijousen thil kidang abol ho jeh chun akipah tauve.   
\s1 Ankam mu thulem  
\p
\v 18 Chuin Jesun aseiyin, “Pathen Lenggam chu itobang ham? Iti katekah ding ham?  
\v 19 Ankam mu neocha tobang mikhat in hon'a atu tobang ahi; ahung khangin chule thingphung ahung kisoh e, chule vachaten abah tin'ah gena ding bu akisah jiuve,” ati.   
\s1 Chol thulem  
\p
\v 20 Aman adong kit in, “Pathen Lenggam chu ipi toh kitekah ding ham?  
\v 21 Nupi khat in changlhah asemna a amanchah chol tobang ahi. Changbong atena dimthum'a chol neocha akoi ahivangin, apumpin ahin thulha jin ahi,” ati.  
\v 22 Jesu khopi ho leh khoneo tin'ah achen, achena chan'ah thu ahil'in, Jerusalem lam amano jinge.  
\v 23 Koiham khat in ahin dongin, “Pakai, mi themkhat bou huhhing'a um ding ham?” ati. Aman adonbut in,  
\v 24 “Pathen Lenggam lutna a kotjim lam'a lutna dingin kihabol un, ajeh chu mi tamtah in lutding agot ding ahivanga losam diu ahi.  
\v 25 In neipan kot akam jouteng, geisang val ding ahitai. Nangma pamlam'a nadin'a kot nakiu ding chule natao ding, ‘Pakai, keiho dingin kot neihon peh un!’ nati ding, ahivanga aman nahin donbut diu, ‘Keiman nangho koi nahiu ahilou le hoiya kon nahiu ka hekhapoi’ ati ding ahi.  
\v 26 Chuteng nang hon nasei diu, ‘Ahivanga nangma toh kaneh uva kadon uva, chule kalampiu lah dunga jong neina hil u chula’ nati diu ahi.  
\v 27 Chule aman hitia hi ahin donbut ding, ‘Ka seipeh nahiuve, keiman nangho kahekhapoi chule hoiya konna hung nahiu kahepoi. Kakom'a kon'in potdoh un, nangho thilse bolte ho.’”\x + \xo 13:27 \xt Labu 6:8\x*  
\v 28 \x + \xo 13:28 \xt Matt 8:11,12\x*”Chumun'a chu ka le hagel um ding ahi, ijeh inem itile Pathen Lenggam a chu Abraham, Isaac, Jacob, chule themgao jouse namu diu ahi, amavang nangma na kipaidoh ding ahi.\x + \xo 13:28 \xt Matt 22:13; 25:30\x*  
\v 29 Chule miho vannoi pumpi–solam le lhumlam apat, sah le lhang apat–Pathen Lenggam'a amun'u kilo dinga hung khom diu ahi.  
\v 30 Chule hiche hi kichin in: mi phabep tua minoinung pen dan'a um ho hi khonung leh alenpen hi diu ahi, chule tua alenpen ho hi aneopen hi diu ahi,” ati.\x + \xo 13:30 \xt Matt 19:30; 20:16; Mk 10:31\x*   
\s1 Jesun Jerusalem agihsal  
\p
\v 31 Hiche pet chun Pharisee ho phabep khat in ajah a, “Hikom'a kon'in potdoh in nakihinso nom leh! Herod in nathat doh nom'e!” atiuve.  
\v 32 Jesun adonbut in, “Cheuvin lang chuche si-al chu gaseipeh un, thilha kanodoh jing ding chule ana damlou kasuhdam jing ding, tunia jong jinga jong; chule anithumni le kahung lona kasuh bulhit ding ahi.  
\v 33 Henge, tuni le jing, chule ajing kit le kalampia chu ka chejom ding ahi. Ajeh chu Jerusalem tailouva themgao kithat thei louding ahi!”  
\v 34 “O Jerusalem, Jerusalem, themgaoho that le Pathen sottol leho songa seplih khopi! Ijat vei ahpin anoute alhaving noiya a-opkhum banga nachate khoptup ding kagot ham, ahivangin nei bolsah poi.  
\v 35 Chuleh tun, ven, na-in hi kidalha ahitai. Chuleh nangman neimu kit louding ahitai, ‘Pakai min'a hungpa anunnom'e!’ tia na seikit tokah a,” ati.\x + \xo 13:35 \xt Labu 118:26\x*   
\c 14  
\s1 Jesun cholngah nikhoa thongpohvei khat adamsah  
\p
\v 1 Cholngahni khat Jesu nilhah an nedin Pharisee ho lamkai khat in'ah achen, chule miho chun phatah in avelhiuvin ahi.  
\v 2 Hiche a chun mikhat, aban le akengho pom khat aumin ahi.  
\v 3 Jesun Pharisee ho leh danthu themho chu adongin, “Cholngah nikhoa misuhdam danthun aphal hai aphallou ham?” ati.  
\v 4 ama hon adonbut nom lou phat un, Jesun anapa chu atham'in chule asudam'in asolmang tai.  
\v 5 Chuin amaho lam ngan aseitai, “Nangho cholngah nia natonglou koi naum uvam? Nachapa ham ahilou le na bongchal hamkhat kokhuh a alhahlut le, aladoh dinga nakino ji hih um?” ati.\x + \xo 14:5 \xt Matt 12:11\x*  
\v 6 Avel'in adonbut thei kit tapouve.   
\s1 Jindot them chule lungnem  
\p
\v 7 Nilhah anne a hung jouse chun touna nom nom jabolna mun achu cheh u Jesun amu phat in, aman amaho chu hiche thumop hi apen ahi.  
\v 8 “Moupui golvah na a kouna namu tengu leh, jabolna munhoa tou hih un. Ijem tin nang sanga jabolna chang ding khat ana kikou kha taleh ipi tin tem?\x + \xo 14:8 \xt Thuchihbu 25:6,7\x*  
\v 9 Kinneipa chun ahung sei ding, “Na touna chu hiche mipa hi pen” ati ding ahi. Chuteng nangma najahcha ding ahi, chutengleh dokhang noiya kikoi touna hoa chu natou ding ahitai!  
\v 10 “Chusang chun, dokhang kengbul mun nemnung pen'a chun touvin. Chuteng kinneipan nahin mu ding nahenga hunga, ‘Jol, nang dingin mun phajep kaneiyuve!’ ahungti ding ahi. Chuteng nangma chu jin kikou dang ho masanga jana nachan ding ahi.  
\v 11 Ijeh inem itile ama kichoisang chan chu suhnem'a um diu ahi, chule akineosah chan chu dopsang'a um diu ahi” ati.\x + \xo 14:11 \xt Matt 23:12; Lk 18:14\x*  
\v 12 Chuin in-neipa chu aven, hitin aseiye “Nangman nehkhom ahilouleh golvah nabol teng,” naloi nagol ho, nasopiho, na inkote, chule naheng nakom mihao ho kou hih in. Ajeh chu ama hon nangma nahin koukit diu ahin, hiche bou chu natohga hi ding ahitai.  
\v 13 Chusang chun mivaichaho, chatmo ho, elbai ho, chule mitcho ho kou jon.  
\v 14 Chuteng michonpha thokitna a Pathen'in nanungsah joulou ding ho nakou jeh a nangma tohphatman napeh ding ahi,” ati.   
\s1 Van gam golvah loupi thulem  
\p
\v 15 Hiche thu ajah hin mikhat dokhanga Jesu toh toukhom khat in, “Pathen Lenggam'a golvah ankonga galhah ding iti anop tadem!” tin ahin phongdoh e.  
\v 16 Jesun adonbut nan hiche thusim hi aseipeh e: Mikhat hin golvah lentah abol in kouna lekha jong tamtah athot doh tai.  
\v 17 Golvah anneh khom chu gontup ahiphat in, asohte asol'in, akikou ho jah a, “Hungun golvah ankong gontup ahitai” agatisah e.  
\v 18 Ahivangin ama hon abon'un ahitheilou nau thu aseiyun ahi. Khat in, 'Tutah chun loumun kachon kavettoh lou akhoh'e, lungsettah in nei ngaidam in' ati.  
\v 19 Khat kit chun, 'Keiman tutah chun bongchal to-nga kahin chon, hithei nam ti kavet got ahi, lungset in nei ngaidam un,' ati.  
\v 20 Achom khat in, 'Tun ji kaneiyin, hijeh chun hung thei ponge,'” ati.  
\v 21 “Sohpa chu akilen apakai pa kom'ah ipi iti adonbut u aseipeh tai. Apakai pa chu alunghang in hitin ahinsei tai, ‘Kintah in chenlang, khopi sung lamlen tin'ah mivaicha ho, chatmo ho, mitcho ho, chule elbai ho gakou tan’ ati.  
\v 22 Asohpan hichu aboljou phat in, ahung hetsah in, ‘Mun a-ong nalaiye’ ahung ti.  
\v 23 Hijeh chun apakai pan aseiyin, ‘Chedoh inlang lamlen pam lah dung chule aning kahlah a um koi hijongleh, namu mu hin kouvin, ka-in mi adimna dingin’ ati.  
\v 24 Ajeh chu kakou masat ho chun golvah an chu aneokhat jong atekhah lou diu ahitai,'” ati.   
\s1 Jesu seijui hina amanlut dan  
\p
\v 25 Mihonpi tamtah chun Jesu nung ajuiyu ahin, ama akihei kol'in ajah uva aseitai,  
\v 26 “Nangho kaseijui nahi nom uleh, mijouse nahot u ngai ahi, tekah nan–nanu napa, naji nachate, nasopi ho, nangma hinkho tah jong, achuti louleh kaseijui nahi theilou diu ahi.\x + \xo 14:26 \xt Matt 10:37\x*  
\v 27 Chule na thingpel nakipoh a kanung najui louleh, kaseijui nahi theilou diu ahi.”\x + \xo 14:27 \xt Matt 10:38; 16:24; Mk 8:34; Lk 9:23\x*  
\v 28 “Ahivangin kipan hih un athoh hah ding dan nasimtoh masang'un. Ijeh inem itile, kon insah apat ding ham amasa a alut ding jat vetoh a, ajona dinga sum ninglhing ding hinam ti simtoh masa louva?  
\v 29 Achuti loule akhombul bou najoa sum nabei maithei ahi, chuteng chuleh mijousen na nuisat bep ding ahitai.  
\v 30 ama hon seiyunte, 'Hiche pa khu ahi, insah kipan'a aban ajona ding boldoh joulou pa khu'” tiuvinte.  
\v 31 “Ahilouleh, Leng khat galbol ding, koi athumop them hotoh toukhom'a, asepai sang som chun ama nokhum dinga hung kon sang som ni chu ajo ding hinam ti kigel masalou dingah?  
\v 32 Chuleh ajolou ding leh, palai sol'in tin, agalmi ho gamlat pet a chu kihoucham ding agot tei ding ahi.  
\v 33 Hijeh a chu nanei jouse napehdoh tokah a kaseijui nahi theilou diu ahi.”   
\s1 A'al tamsa chi  
\p
\v 34 “Chi hi asu-al dingin aphai. Ahin, a-al na chu mansah taleh, iti na-alsah kit ding ham?”  
\v 35 A-al lou chi chu leiset a dinga jong chule leithao a dinga jong phachom lou ahi. Paidoh in aumji tai. Koi hileh nakol neichan in ngai hen chule hetthem hen!”   
\c 15  
\s1 Kelngoi kimansah  
\p
\v 1 Kaidong ho leh adang michonse ho Jesu thuhil ngai dingin ahung jiuvin ahi.\x + \xo 15:1 \xt Lk 5:29,30\x*  
\v 2 Hiche hin Pharisee ho leh houdan thuhil ho aphunchel sah tan, michonse hotoh akipol'in nejong anekhom uve! tin asei tauve.  
\v 3 Hijeh chun Jesun hiche thusim hi aseipeh in ahi:  
\v 4 “Mikhat in kelngoi jakhat neihen chule alah a khat chu vahmang taleh, ipi bol tantem? Adang somko le ko ho chu gamthip a adalhah a chule avahmang pa chu amu tokah a agahol louding ham?  
\v 5 Chuteng ahin mu tengleh, kipah tah in a'in lam'a din alengkouvah hin kipoh tante.  
\v 6 Ahung vailhun tengleh amapan aloi agol chule aheng akom koukhom intin, ‘Nei kipa khom piuvin ajeh chu keiman ka kelngoi mangsa chu kakimutai’ tinte.  
\v 7 Chutobang a chu michonse khat in lungheina aneiya Pathen lama akile kit chun adang somko le ko lunghei ngailou michonpha ho chung sangin van'ah kipana aum'e!”   
\s1 Sum-Pum Kimansah  
\p
\v 8 “Ahilouleh, tekahnan, numei khat hin sum dangka som aneiyin chule khat amansah tai. Amanun meivah adet a insung pumpi atheh a chule chingthei tah a amu tokah a ahol louding ham?  
\v 9 Chule amanun hichu amuteng, aloi apai chule aheng akom cheng akoukhom ding, ‘Nei kipapiuvin, ajeh chu kasum mang kakinung mutai’ ati ding ahi.  
\v 10 Chutobang chun van'ah Pathen Vantil te panna in, michonse khat seh lunghei na chungah kipana aum'e,” ati.   
\s1 Chapa vahmangpa  
\p
\v 11 Athusei hilchet be theina din hiche thusim hi aseiyin ahi: “Mikhat in chapa ni aneiye.  
\v 12 Aneojo pan apa jah a, ‘Nathi masangin nanei nagou kachan ding ho tun kadei tai’ ati. Hijeh chun apan acha teni chu anei agou ho hoppeh dingin anomtai.”  
\v 13 “Ni phabep jouvin hiche chapa neojo pa chun anei jouse akisemtup in mun gamla tah a dingin achetai, chule hia chun asum le pai jouse hindan kinomsah nan asumang tai.  
\v 14 Chutia asum akiman chai phat chun, gamsunga chun kel nasatah alhan, kel athoh pantai.  
\v 15 Chumun'a loulhoumi khat in natoh apehna dingin akithujon, amapan jong aloumun langah vohchate vah dingin asol'in ahi.  
\v 16 Khangdong pa chu agilkel lheh tan, vohchate anehsah ji voh-an jeng jong chu tui lheh dingin amitmun akilang tan ahi. Ahivangin koiman neh ding ape tapon ahi.”  
\v 17 “Achainakeiya ahung khahdoh phat chun, ama le ama akihoulim in, 'Ka-in ah soh thalah ho jengin jong anehval set u anneh aneiyun, kei hiche'ah gilkel'a thi dingin kaum'e!'” ati.  
\v 18 Ka-in a kache ding kapa kom'a, “Hepa, van le nangma dounan kachonse tai,  
\v 19 chule keima nacha tiding hoi kahi tapoi. Lungset tah in soh thalah khat bangin nei sangin, tinge,” atitai.  
\v 20 “Chuin ama apa kom'a dingin inlam akile tai. Chule amapa mun gamla tah ahung gei nalaiyin, apan ahung amutan ahi. Ngailutna le khotona dimset pum'in achapa kom'ah alhaiyin, akolchuh chuh in, achoptai.  
\v 21 Achapan ahin seitai, 'Hepa, keima van le nangma dounan kachonse tai, chule tun nacha tidin jong kalhing jou tapoi,” ati.  
\v 22 “Ahinlah apan asohte kom'ah aseitai, Gang'un! Insunga ponsil hoipen pen hinchoiyun lang silpeh un. Akhutjung'a akibu ding khutjem le akise ding kengchot hinchoiyun.  
\v 23 Chule bongnou ivahthao uchu that un. Eihon golvah loupi tah a ilop diu ahi,  
\v 24 ajeh chu hiche kachapa hi athi ana hitan, tua hi hung hingdoh kit ahi. Amangsa anahin, tua hi kimukit ahitai.' Hiti chun golnop chu akipan tai.”  
\v 25 Chutia aumlai chun, chapa a upajo pa chu loulanga um natong ahi. Inlam ahung kile chun, in'a chun tumging le lam gin ajatan,  
\v 26 chuin asohte khat kom'ah ipi thilsoh um ham ti adongin ahi.  
\v 27 'Nasopipa hung kile ahi,' tin aseipeh un, 'Chuleh napan bongnou thaotah chu athapeh ahi. Damsel'a ahunglhun jeh a ilop u ahi,'” tin aseipeh tai.  
\v 28 “A upajo pa chu alunghangin insung alut tapon ahi. Apa ahungdoh in ahung tem'e,  
\v 29 ahin aman adonbut in, 'Kum hijat hi nasoh banga kaum chule bol'in nati jouse kada na umkhalou ahi. Chuleh hiche phat jouse achun nangman kaloi kagol hotoh kaneh khom diuvin kelcha nou khatbeh neinape khapoi.  
\v 30 Ahivangin hiche na chapan noti ho chunga nasum jouse aveichai nungin, nangman bongnou thaotah nathapeh in nalop peh e!'” ati.  
\v 31 “Apan ajah a aseiyin, 'Ven, kachapa ngaitah, nangma kakom'ah naum jinge, chuleh kanei jouse jong hi nanga ahi.  
\v 32 Eihon hiche kipa nikho hi ilop diu ahi. Ijeh inem itile nasopipa hi athi'ah ahitan chule hung hingdoh kit ahi! Amangsa anahin, hinlah tun akimutai!'” ati.   
\c 16  
\s1 Sumching kitahna beipa thulem  
\p
\v 1 Jesun hiche thusim hi aseijui te aseipeh e: “Mihaotah khat ana um'in, aman neiching khat ima ma vesuiya anganse aneiye, ahin anei chinna ah akitah poi ti thulamleng ahunge.  
\v 2 Hijeh chun apansah pan ama chu akouvin aseitai, ‘Ipi ham nathu kajah hi? Na neichin ho sutup inlang neihin pen ajeh chu na chungthu kisei ding ahitai’” ati.  
\v 3 Nei chingpa akingaiton, 'Tua ipi kabol ding? tin akihoulim'in, ka pakai pan la eihaisah ahitan, lei lai dingla katha ahatpon, chule thum ding la hibanga kakiletsah e.  
\v 4 Aphai, eihaisah tengleh loi le pai tampi kaneiya ama hon a-in'a eilhunsahna diuvin hitin bol inge,'” ati.  
\v 5 Hijeh chun apansah pa sumba jouse chu ahungkhom uva athu seitoh ahina din akoukhom sohtai. Amasapa jah a, “Ijat nabat ham?” ati.  
\v 6 Mipa chun adonbut in, 'Keiman olive thao twipai dim jaget kabai' ati. Chuin neichingpan aseipeh in, 'Aman kijihna lekha hi kilah loiyin lang twipai jali jih in'” ati.  
\v 7 “'Ahileh nangin ijat nabat em?' tin anina pa adonge. 'Keiman suhlou chang lhuh sangkhat kabai,' tin ahin donbut e. Neiching pan aseiyin, hin, 'lekha hi kilah inlang lhuh jaget in jih in,'” ati.  
\v 8 “Mihao pa chun chuche chondih lou neichingpan chingthei tah a abol chu apahcha tan ahi. Adih ahi, hiche vannoi chaten avel uva ho toh kipol ding dan hi khovah chate sangin achingjo uve.  
\v 9 Kijildoh ding chu hiche ahi: Vannoiya nagouthil ho se hi midang phatchomna le jol le gol kisem nan mangin. Chuteng, na lei gouthil ho jouse abeisoh teng cheho chun tonsot in'a dinga nana lem diu ahi.”  
\v 10 “Nangho thil neocha chunga nakitah ule, thil lentah ho chunga jong nakitah diu ahi. Amavang thil neocha chunga nakitahlou ule, mopohna lentah ho chunga jong kitah louding nahiuve.  
\v 11 Chuleh leiset gouthil chunga tahsan naumlou leh, kon van gou dihtah chunga na tahsan dingu ham?  
\v 12 Chuleh midang thil chunga nakitah louleh ipi jeh a nangma thil chunga nakitahsan ding ham?”  
\v 13 “Koiman pakai ni sohna atongkop theipoi. Ajeh chu nangman khat namuda a khat na ngailut tum ding ahi; khat dinga nakiphal theng'a khat nadonda thei ahi. Nanghon Pathen le sum soh na tongkhom thei pouvin nate,” ati.\x + \xo 16:13 \xt Matt 6:24\x*   
\s1 Danthu le Pathen Lenggam  
\p
\v 14 Pharisee ho, sum ngailu dehset hon, ajasoh keiyun ama chu anelpeh un ahi.  
\v 15 Chuin aman amaho jah a aseitai, “Jalah a miho mitmu a michonpha nahinom, ahin Pathen'in nalungthim ahei. Hiche vannoi miten ajabol chu Pathen mitmua thet umtah ahi.”  
\v 16 “Twilutsah John phatlai chan'a chu, Mose dan le themgao ho thuhil chu nakaihoi leuva pang anahi. Ahin, tun Pathen Lenggam Kipana Thupha chu seiphongin aum tan, chule mijouse lut ding athanom in ahi.\x + \xo 16:16 \xt Matt 11:12,13\x*  
\v 17 Ahivangin danthu chu apanna umtalou tina ahipoi. Van le lei amanthah ding hi Pathen danthu neopen khat kilekhup ding sanga gamchenga baijo ahi.”\x + \xo 16:17 \xt Matt 5:18\x*   
\s1 Nupa kida thudol'a Jesun ahil  
\p
\v 18 “Vetsahnan, mikhat chun ajinu ada a midang khat akichenpi le ajong'ah ahi. Chuleh koi hileh ajipan ahindasa numei kichenpi jong chu ajong'ah ahi” ati.\x + \xo 16:18 \xt Matt 5:32; 1 Crth 7:10,11\x*   
\s1 Mihaopa le Lazarus  
\p
\v 19 Jesun aseiye, “Mihaotah khat, ponsandup le tupat ponnem kisil'a loupitah a kivon le niseh a nomsatah a um khat anaum'in ahi.  
\v 20 Akelkot phunga chun Lazarus kiti tiphah natna dimset, mivaicha khat aumjin ahi.  
\v 21 Chutia Lazarus jong mihaopa dokhanga an lhajah ho ducha a aum laiyin, uicha ho ahung jiuvin atiphahna mun ho chu ahung leh jiuve.”  
\v 22 “Achainan, mivaichapa chu athitan chule Vantil te Abraham kom'a um dingin apotauve. Mihaopa jong athin avui tauve,  
\v 23 chule alhagao chu mithi ho lah a achetai. Chua athoh gentheina mun achun, Abraham gamla tah a aum chule Lazarus akom'a atou chu amun ahi.”  
\v 24 “Mihaopa chu ahung pengjah in, ‘Hepa Abraham, themkhat neilungset in! Lazarus hinsol in lang akhutjung twiyah hin delut henlang kalei hung sudap hen. Keima hiche meikong lah a hin kahesoh lheh jeng'e,’” ati.  
\v 25 “Ahin Abraham'in amapa jah a aseiyin, 'Chapa, geldoh in, nangman nahinlai sungin nadei jouse nanei sohkeiyin chule Lazarus in ima ana neipoi. Hijeh a chu tua hi ama hikom mun'a nomtah a kiumsah a nangman hesoh nathoh ahitai.  
\v 26 Chule chuche tilouvin jong, ikikah uva hin eikhen uvah onghom lentah aum'e. Koiman hikom mun'a pat a apal galkai theilou, chule chua pat a jong keiho kom lang koiman apal galkal theilou ahi,'” ati.  
\v 27 “Chuin mihaopan aseikit in, 'Lungset tah in, Hepa Abraham, kapa in beh a gasol in.  
\v 28 Ajeh chu keiman sopi pasal nga kaneiye, chule ama chun hikom thoh gentheina mun'a ahung louna diuva aga gihsal ding kadeiye,' ati.  
\v 29 “Ahin Abraham'in aseipeh in, ‘Mose le Themgaohon agihsal nauve. Nasopi hon chua ipi asut u hin kisimdoh nauvinte,’” atipeh e.  
\v 30 “Mihaopan adonbut kit in, ‘Ahipoi, Hepa Abraham! Koiham khat athilah a konna akisol le, achonset nauva konna lungheina anei diu chule Pathen lam'a kihei diu ahi,’” ati.  
\v 31 “Ahivangin Abraham'in aseikit in, ‘Ama hon Mose le Themgaoho thu angailou uleh, athilah a kon'in khat thoudoh jongleh ngaideh pouvinte,’” ati.   
\c 17  
\s1 Chonset lhepna a lhahna thei  
\p
\v 1 Nikhat Jesun aseijui te jah a aseiye, “Chonsetna dia lhepna hi aum jing ding mong ahi, hinlah itobang lungkham nan anga hitam alhem'a pang mi chu!  
\v 2 Na-ngongchanga sumhei song naki-o a twikhanglen'a nakilelut chu hiche aneocha ho nakipal lhuhsah sanga phachomjo ding ahi.  
\v 3 Hijeh chun kivephauvin!” “Tahsan cha adang khat achonset leh, ama chu sosal'in; chutia alung ahei le, ngaidam in.\x + \xo 17:3 \xt Matt 18:15\x*  
\v 4 Hiche mipa chun ihamtia nikhat a sagi vei nachunga thil dihlou abol'a, abol phat jousea jong ngaidam athum leh ngaidam in” ati.   
\s1 Ka tahsan u khansah in  
\p
\v 5 Seijuiten Pakai jah a aseiyun, “Tahsan na kangaichat be uve, iti kanei diu ham nei seipeh un” atiuve.  
\v 6 Pakaiyin adonbut in, “Nanghon tahsanna ankammu te cha hijongleh naneiyuleh, hiche thing theimi phung kom'a hi, ‘Kibotdoh in lang twikhanglen'ah kilehlut in’ tijongleu chun nathu u angai ding ahi!”   
\s1 Sohpa Natoh Ding  
\p
\v 7 “Soh khat chu aloukaina ham ahilou le akelngoi chinna ham'a pat a ahunglut teng, apakai pan, ‘Hunglut in an nekhom hite’ tin tem?  
\v 8 Tiponte! Hiti joh hin seiyinte, ‘Ka anneh ding nei gonpeh in, natai kigeh inlang, kaneh sungsen neijen in. chuteng ajoujep le nenan nate’ ati ding ahi.  
\v 9 Chuleh apakai pan asohpa chu atoh dinga lom atoh jeh a apachat em? Apahcha dehpoi.  
\v 10 Chutobang a chu nang hon kathua nanun tengu leh hitia hi nasei diu, ‘Keiho soh lhingjoulou kanatoh diuva lom bou tong kahiuve’ nati diu ahi,” ati.   
\s1 Jesun miphah som asuhtheng  
\p
\v 11 Jesu Jerusalem lam jon'a achejom jing laiyin, Galilee le Samaria kigamgitna mun alhung tai.  
\v 12 Chutia khokhat agalut laiyin, chua chun miphah som gamla thimtah in adingun,  
\v 13 ahung eodoh un, “Jesu, Pipu, nei khoto un!” atiuve.  
\v 14 Aman amaho chu aven, “Cheuvin lang thempuho gakimusah tauvin,” atipeh tai. Chutia acheuleh, aphah natnau chu suhtheng in aumtai.\x + \xo 17:14 \xt Thempu Dan 14:1-32\x*  
\v 15 Alah uva khat chun suhdam a aum chu akimu phat in, Jesu hengah ahung kilen, “Pathen Vahchoiyin umhen!” tin apengjah tai.  
\v 16 Ama Jesu kengbul'ah abohkhup in, athil bolpehna chungah kipathu aseiyin ahi. Hiche mipa chu Samaria mi ahi.  
\v 17 Jesun adongin, “Mi som kasuhdam hilou ham? Adang mi ko ho la?  
\v 18 Koiman Pathen loupina peh ding ageldoh lou hitam hiche gamdang mipa tailou?” atin ahi.  
\v 19 Chule Jesun hiche pa kom'a chun aseiyin, “Dingdoh inlang chetan. Na tahsan in nasuhdam ahitai,” ati.   
\s1 Pathen Lenggam  
\p
\v 20 Nikhat Pharisee hon Jesu adongun, “Pathen Lenggam itih le hunglhung ding ham?” atiuve. Jesun adonbut in, “Pathen Lenggam chu muthei melchihna ah akihedoh theipoi.  
\v 21 Nanghon, ‘Hikom'ah aum'e!’ ahilou le ‘hichea khun aum'e!’ tin seithei pouvin nate. Ajeh chu Pathen Lenggam chu nalah uva aumtai” ati.  
\v 22 Chuin aseijui te hengah hitin aseiye, “Phat ahung lhunge Mihem Chapa ahung kilena ding nikho munom'a naum diu, ahivanga namu lou diu ahi.  
\v 23 Mihon ahinsei diu, 'Veuvin, Mihem Chapa khukom'ah aum'e' ahilouleh 'hivah aum'e,' ati diu ahi, ahivangin potdoh hih un, chule jui hih un.  
\v 24 Ijeh inem itile kolphe ahung phet a van mong langkhat apat mong langkhat gei asalvah soh banga Mihem Chapa hung ni jong chutobang hi ding ahi.  
\v 25 Ahin amasa a Mihem Chapa hin thoh hahsa tampi athoh a hiche khang miten apampai diu ahi.”  
\v 26 “Mihem Chapa ahung kile tengleh, Noah nikholai toh bang ding ahi.\x + \xo 17:26 \xt Semtilbu 6:5-8\x*  
\v 27 Chuche nikholai chun mihon golvah neh le don chule kichen abol'un, Noah kongsunga alut a chule twisang ahunglet a abonchauva asuhmang nikho geiyin nomsatah in hinkho amangun ahi.”\x + \xo 17:27 \xt Semtilbu 7:6-24\x*  
\v 28 “Chule vannoi leiset jong Lot nikho lai toh bang ding ahi. Miho nitin akimanchah nauvah akisaboi un–neh le don, choh le joh, loulho le insah,\x + \xo 17:28 \xt Semtilbu 18:20—19:25\x*  
\v 29 Lot in Sodom khopi adalhah ni jingkah chan in abol'un ahi. Chuin van'a kon'in mei le kath ahung julhan abonchauvin asumang soh tan ahi.  
\v 30 Henge, 'angaima banga' kiseimona Mihem Chapa ahung kile kit ni geiya um ding ahi.  
\v 31 Chuche nikho chuleh indan chunga um chun insunga athil kisemtup din lutkit dahen. Mi louva kondoh jong inlam a kile dahen.\x + \xo 17:31 \xt Matt 24:17,18; Mk 13:15,16\x*  
\v 32 Lot inneipi chunga ipi anasoh em geldoh un!\x + \xo 17:32 \xt Semtilbu 19:26\x*  
\v 33 Nahinkho tuhchah jing nagot le namansah ding, chule nahinkho nachesah le, nahuhhing joh ding ahi.\x + \xo 17:33 \xt Matt 10:39; 16:25; Mk 8:35; Lk 9:24; Jn 12:25\x*  
\v 34 Chuche jan leh mini jalkhun khat a lumkhom ding; khat kila ding, khatpa kidalha ding.  
\v 35 Nupi nin sumhei khat a chang agoikhom lhon ding, khat kila ding khat kidalha ding,  
\v 36 lou mun'a um teni jong khat kida lhaa khat kila ding ahi, ati.  
\v 37 “Pakai, hitiho hi itih leh soh ding ham?” tin aseijui ten adongun ahi. Jesun adonbut in, “Muthong ho kititna achun mithi long naivel ah aum'e ti aphotchet banga hiche melchihna ho jong chun akichaina anaitai ti avetsah ahi,” ati.   
\c 18  
\s1 Pathen'in amite apanpi ding ahi  
\p
\v 1 Nikhat Jesun aseijui te atao jingna diu leh alhahdai louna diu vetsahnan thusim khat aseipeh e.  
\v 2 “Khopi khat a hin thutan khat Pathen ginglou chule miho khohsahna jong neilou khat aumin ahi.  
\v 3 Chuche khopia meithai khat chu kinong chel'in ahung jingin, ‘Ka galmiho toh kakiboi nau hi thu adih in nei tanpeh in,’ ahung tijin ahi.  
\v 4 Thutan pan phat chomkhat amanu chu isahlou tah in ana koiyin, ahin achainakeiyin hitin akihoulim in, 'Keiman Pathen kaging pon ahilou le miho jong holeh tilou kahi,  
\v 5 ahivangin hiche numei nu hin eisungol lhatai. Keiman thu adih a tanlhah peh ahina din vetpeh inge. Ajeh chu amanu hin athilthum jinga kon hin ei sulungvai lhatai,'” ati.  
\v 6 Chuin Pakaiyin aseiyin, “Hiche chondihlou thutanpa a kon'in kihil un.”  
\v 7 “Ama jengin jong achaina a thu adih a tan dia ahin gellhah ahi. Hijeh a chu Pathen'in alhenchom te, ama kom'a asun ajan'a kapjing te chu thu adih a atanpeh ding ahi ti nagel lou u ham? Amaho chu donlouvin koijingin te natim?  
\v 8 Ka seipeh nahiuve, aman kinloitah a thu adih a atanpeh ding ahi! Ahinlah Mihem Chapa hung kit teng, leiset chunga hin mi ijat tahsan nei mudoh intem?” ati.   
\s1 Pharisee ho le kaidong ho  
\p
\v 9 Chuin Jesun hiche thusim hi mi konkhat ama chonphatna a kisonga midang musit ho dingin aseiye:  
\v 10 “Mi ni Hou-In ah taona mangin ache lhon'e. Khat chu Pharisee mi ahin, chule adang khatpa chu musit umtah kaidong ahi.  
\v 11 Pharisee mipa chu adingin hitin ataove: ‘Kakipah'e Pathen, adang ho banga chonse kahilou jeh in. Ajeh chu lepthol in kabol pon, kachonse pon, chule jonthanhoi jong kabolpoi. Keima atahbeh in khuche kaidongpa tobang kahipoi!  
\v 12 Keiman hapta khat in nivei an kangol'in, kasum mu jat a kon'in som’a khat kapei,’” ati.  
\v 13 “Ahivangin kaidong pa chu gamla tah a adingin chule amit jeng'a jong vanlam ve ngam louvin ataove. Chusang chun lungkham tah in aman a-op achum'in hitin aseiye, ‘O Pathen, neilungset in, ijeh inem itile chonse kahi bouve,' ati.  
\v 14 Ka seipeh nahiuve, Pharisee pa hilou, hiche chonsepa chu Pathen ang-ah them achangin inlam akiletai. Ijeh inem itile ama kichoisang ho chu suhnem'a um ding, chule akineosah ho chu dopsang'a um diu ahi,” ati.\x + \xo 18:14 \xt Matt 23:12; Lk 14:11\x*   
\s1 Jesun chapang neo ho phatthei aboh  
\p
\v 15 Nikhat nu le pa phabep in achateu chapang neocha chaho chu Jesun atham'a phatthei aboh dingin ahin puiyun ahi. Ahivangin aseijui ten hichu amu phat un, anul e apateu kom'a chun ama nasuboi bep uve tin ahouse uvin ahi.  
\v 16 Chuin Jesun chapang ho chu akouvin chule aseijui te hengah aseitai, “Chapang ho chu kahengah hung uhen. Jahda hih un! Ajeh chu Pathen Lenggam chu hiche chapang neocha tobanghoa ding bou ahi.  
\v 17 Thutah ka seipeh nahiuve, koi hileh chapang neocha banga Pathen Lenggam sanglou chu lutlouhel ding ahi,” ati.   
\s1 Mi haopa  
\p
\v 18 Khatvei hou lamkai khat hin hiche thudoh hi adonge: “Houhil pha, tonsot hinna kanei theina dinga ipi kabol ding ham?” ati.  
\v 19 “Ipi bol'a apha tia nei kou ham?” tin aledoh in, “Pathen bouseh dihtah a pha ahi.  
\v 20 Ahin na thudoh donbut nan, thupeh ho nahet chula: “Nangman jon bol hih in, tolthat hih in, gucha hih in, jouvin mi hehse hih in, nanu napa jabol in,” ati.\x + \xo 18:20 \xt Potdohbu 20:14; Danbu Ni Na 5:18; \xt Potdohbu 20:13; Danbu Ni Na 5:17; \xt Potdohbu 20:15; Danbu Ni Na 5:19; \xt Potdohbu 20:16; Danbu Ni Na 5:20; \xt Potdohbu 20:12; Danbu Ni Na 5:16\x*  
\v 21 Mipan adonbut in, “Hiche thupeh ho jouse hi kachapan laiya pat kajui sohkei ahitai,” ati.  
\v 22 Jesun adonbutna thu ajah phat chun, hitin aseitai, “Nabol loulai thil khat aum'e. Nanei jouse joh in lang hiche sum chu mivaicha ho pen, chutileh van'a gou nanei ding ahi. Chuteng hungin, neijuiyin,” ati.  
\v 23 Ahivangin mipa chun hichu ajahdoh phat in alungkham lheh tan ahi, ijeh inem itile ama chu haosa tah ahi.  
\v 24 Jesun hichu amu phat in, aseitai, “Mihaosa Pathen Lenggam alut ding hi iti hah hitam!  
\v 25 “Atahbeh in, heobil hom'a sangongsao alut galkai ding hi mihaosa Pathen Lenggam a alut ding sangin abaijoi!” ati.  
\v 26 Hiche akisei jajouse chun aseiyun, “Achutileh vannoi leiset a koi ham huhhingna chang jou ding?” atiuve.  
\v 27 Aman adonbut in, “Mihem dinga hithei lou chu Pathen dinga hithei ahi,” ati.  
\v 28 Peter in aseiyin, “Keihon nangma jui dingin ka-in'u kadalha uve,” ati.  
\v 29 Jesun adonbut in, “Henge” chuleh ka lhamon nahiuve, “Koi hileh Pathen Lenggam jal'a a'in ham, ajinu ham, asopiho ham, ahilou le anu apa ham achate ham pedoh chan chu,  
\v 30 tamtah vei tu hinkhoa hi lepeh a um diu chule ahunglhung ding khang'a jong tonsot hinkemlou amu ding'u ahi,” ati.   
\s1 Athum channa Jesun athi ding le athokit ding asei  
\p
\v 31 Seijui som le ni ho atumbeh'in apuidoh in, Jesun ajah uva aseiye, “Ngaiyun, eiho Jerusalem chetou ding ihiuve, Mihem Chapa chung chang thudol'a themgao thusei jouse guilhun na ding mun chu ahi.  
\v 32 Ama chu Rome te khut a pehdoh a um ding ahi, chule ama chu tot thanghoia um ding, jachat umtah a kibol ding, chil kiset khum ding ahi.  
\v 33 Ama hon avoh uva chule atha diu ahi, ahivanga anithum nileh thoukit ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 34 Ahin, ama hon hitiho thu hi khatcha ahethei pouve. Athusei ho athupije chu amaho a konna ki immang ahi, hijeh a chu athusei chu amattoh theilou u ahitai.   
\s1 Jesun mitcho khat adamsah  
\p
\v 35 Jesun Jericho anaisuh lai hin, mitcho khutdo khat lamsih ah ana touve.  
\v 36 Aman mihonpi kijot khuto gin ajah phat in, ipi thu hitam ti adongin ahi.  
\v 37 Nazereth Jesun hikom chu ahopa ahi ti aseipeh tauve.  
\v 38 Hijeh chun amapa ahung eojah tan, “Jesu, David chapa, neilungset in!” ahintin ahi.  
\v 39 “Thip in” tin masang langa miho chun ahutot tauvin ahi. Ahivangin ama awgingjep in ahapen cheh tan, “David Chapa, neilungset in!” ati.  
\v 40 Jesun ajahdoh phat in, adingin mipa chu ahin puilut diuvin athupeh tai. Mipa ahung nai toh lhonin Jesun adongin,  
\v 41 “Ipi nabolpeh leng natim?” tin adong tai. Aman, “Pakai, kho muleng kati!” ati.  
\v 42 Chuin Jesun aseiyin, “Aphai, kho mutan! Natahsan in na damsah ahitai,” ati.  
\v 43 Apettah chun mipa chun kho amutai chuleh ama pan Jesu nung ajuiyin Pathen avahchoi tai. Chuleh amu jousen jong Pathen avahchoi cheh tauve.   
\c 19  
\s1 Zacchaeus in Jesu aki mupi  
\p
\v 1 Jesu Jericho alut in, chule akhopi sung chu ajot in ahi.  
\v 2 Mi khat amin Zacchaeus kiti chua chun aum'e. Ama chu hiche lhang'a dinga kaidong pipu ahin, ahaova haosa ahitai.  
\v 3 Aman Jesu chu mutei ding agon, hinlah ama anem behseh jeh chun mihonpi lah a chun amu theipoi.  
\v 4 Hijeh chun ana malhaijel'in lampi panga theiba phung khat ah anakal'e, ajeh chu Jesun hiche lampi chu aho ding ahi.  
\v 5 Jesu ahung phat chun, Zacchaeus chu avetouvin chule amin'in akouvin, “Zacchaeus! Gang'in, hungkum'in! tunia na in'a maljin kahi ding ahi,” ahinti.  
\v 6 Zacchaeus jong kinloitah in ahung kumlhan, Jesu chu a'in ah kipah le thanom tah in apuilut tai.  
\v 7 Ahivangin miho chu alungphamo uvin, “Michonse chungnung in'ah agalhung taget e,” tin aphunchel tauve.  
\v 8 Chuphat chun, Zacchaeus jong Pakai angsung'ah adingdoh in aseitai, “Pakai, kanei kagou akehkhat mivaicha ho peing'e, chule kai kadon na a miho lepthol'a kabol aum leh, amaho chu ajatli'n nungpeh inge!” ati.  
\v 9 Jesun adonbut in, “Tunin hiche in'ah huhhingna alhung tai, ajeh chu hiche mipa hin Abraham chapa dihtah ahi akimusah tai.  
\v 10 Ijeh inem itile Mihem Chapa chu amangsa holdoh le huhhing dinga hung'ah ahi,” ati.\x + \xo 19:10 \xt Matt 18:11\x*   
\s1 Sum som khat thulem  
\p
\v 11 Mihonpi chun Jesu thusei jouse chu angailha sohkeiyun ahi. Chule ama Jerusalem anaitoh kilhonin, aman thusim khat, Pathen Lenggam chu kipan pai dinga angaito'u suhdihna din aseiye.  
\v 12 Aman hitin aseiye, “Leng chapa te khat mun gamla tah a leng gachanga hung kile kit dingin koudoh in aumin ahi.  
\v 13 Achedoh masangin asohte lah a mi som akoukhom in dangka min'a som apen, ‘kachedoh sungin hiche hi nei veikan peh un’ ati.  
\v 14 Ahivangin amiten avetnom pouvin, achedoh nungin palai asol'un, ‘Ama hi ka lengpau dingin kadei pouve’ tin agasei sah uve.”  
\v 15 “Leng ahung chan jouvin, ahung kilen chule asohte sum apeh sese chu akoukhom tai. Aman aveikan jat u chu ahetnom ahi.  
\v 16 Soh masapan thu ahin lhut in, ‘Pipu, keiman nasum kaveikan in, neipeh chu ajat som in apunge!’” ati.  
\v 17 “Lengpan adonbut in, ‘Nabol pha e!’ ati. ‘Nangma sohpha nahi. Nangma themcha kapeh chunga kitah nahi, hijeh a chu natohphat kipaman'a khopi som chunga gamvaipo nahi ding ahi,’ atipeh e.”  
\v 18 “Soh anina pan thu ahin lhut kit in, ‘Pipu, nasum kaveikan in neipeh chu ajat ngan kapunsah be e’ ati.  
\v 19 “‘Nabol aphai!’ tin lengpan adonbut in, ‘Nangma khopi nga chunga vaipo nahi ding ahi’” ati.  
\v 20 “Ahivangin soh athumna pan sum amu mama chu ahinchoiyin aseitai, ‘Pipu, keiman nasum chu kasel'in kana koitup peh e.  
\v 21 Ka kichat nahi ajeh chu nangma mikikhel nahin, nanga hilou jong nakilah in, natu lou jong aga naki chomkhomji e.’” ati.  
\v 22 “‘Nangma soh gilou!’ tin lengpa ahung eojah in, ‘Nathu'n themmo nachan ahi. Nangman mikikhel kahi nahet a, keiya hilou kakilah theiya, katulou jong ka-at thei leh,  
\v 23 ipi dinga sumkoina in'a kasum chu nanakoi louham? Ken athoi themkhat beh kikimu tadinga,’” ati.  
\v 24 “Chuin akom avel'a ding ho hengah akiheiyin, hitin thupeh aneitai, ‘Hiche sohpa a kon chun sum chu lahpeh unlang min'a som neipa chu petauvin’” ati.  
\v 25 “‘Ahin, pipu, aman som aneitai!’ tin ahinsei yuve.”  
\v 26 “Lengpan adonbut in, 'ahinai,' 'akipe mangthem ho chu, kipeh be ding. Amavang imacha bollou ho kom'a pat, anei sun'u themcha jong chu kilahmang peh ding ahiuve.\x + \xo 19:26 \xt Matt 13:12; Mk 4:25; Lk 8:18\x*  
\v 27 Chuleh hiche kagalmi ho, lenga kapan ding deilou ho chu–hin puilut unlang ka-angsung tah a hin that doh tauvin,'” ati.\x + \xo 19:27 \xt Matt 25:14-30\x*   
\s1 Jesu loupi tah a Jerusalem alut  
\p
\v 28 Hiche thusim asei jouvin, Jesu Jerusalem lam jon'in, aseijui te sangin ana masan ahi.  
\v 29 Ama Bethphage le Bethany khopiho Olive molchung lang ahung gei phat in, aseijui mini asol masan,  
\v 30 “Hiche kho a khun galut lhonin lang,” tin aseipeh in, “Nalut lhon tengleh, sangan nou kihen koiman atouna nailou namu lhon ding ahi. Hin sutlha lhonin lang hilang'ah hinkai lhonin.  
\v 31 Khat touvin ahindoh a, ‘Ipi bol'a hiche sangan nou chu nasut lhah lhon ham?’ atileh, hitin seilhon'in, ‘Pakaiyin aman nom'e’ tilhon'in” ati.  
\v 32 Chuti chun amani jong ache lhonin, Jesu sei bangin sangan nou chu agamu lhon tai.  
\v 33 Chule atahbah in, asutlhon laiyin aneipan ahin adong lhonin, “Ipi bol'a hiche sangan nou chu nasut lhon ham?” ahin ti.  
\v 34 Chule seijui teni chun bailam tah in adonbut lhonin, “Pakaiyin aman nom'e” atilhon e.  
\v 35 Hiti chun sangan nou chu Jesu hengah ahin kaiyun chule aponsil hou chu achungah atouna dingin aphapeh un ahi.  
\v 36 Chutia ahung tou phei laiyin, mipi hon lampi ah aponsil hou ana phauvin ahi.  
\v 37 Olive mol'a pat a lampi chesuh kipatna aphah chun, anungjui jousen kholhang asam un, ache toh lasah akop un, Pathen'in thil kidang abol ho amujal un avahchoiyuve.  
\v 38 “Pakai min'a hung'ah lengpa chu anunnom e! Van'ah cham leng hen, chule van sangpena jong loupi hen!” atiuve.\x + \xo 19:38 \xt Labu 118:26\x*  
\v 39 Ahivangin mihonpi lah a Pharisee ho phabep khat chun aseiyun, “Houhil, na nungjui hon hitobang thu ho aseiyu khu phohthip in!” atiuve.  
\v 40 Aman adonbut in, “Amaho athipbeh uleh, lampam'a songho kipah a hung eodoh diu ahi!” ati.  
\v 41 “Ama Jerusalem ahung naijep a khopi chu amu phat in akap pan tai.  
\v 42 “Iti kadeisah nahi hitam tunikhon mijouse lah a nangman chamna lampi hi kihet tave lechun. Ahinlah, tun ageisang tan, chamna hi namit mua konna kisel ahitai.  
\v 43 Sot louva nagalmi teuvin nakul pam'a pansatna akisem diu, amai lang jousea na umchinto diu ahi.  
\v 44 ama hon tol'a nachil thang diu, chule nachateu jong chutia abol diu. Nagalmi teuvin song khatcha aumna a aumsah louding ahi, ajeh chu huhhingna dinga phat kilemchang nasan loujeh ahi,” ati.   
\s1 Jesun Jerusalem hou in asuhtheng  
\p
\v 45 Chuin Jesu Hou-In alut in, kilhaina ding gancha joh ho ahin nodoh pan tai.  
\v 46 Aman amaho jah a, “Pathen Lekhabun hitin aseiye, 'Ka in chu taona in kiti ding ahi,' ahin nang hon gucha michom ho kokhuh in nasem tauve” ati.\x + \xo 19:46 \xt Isa 56:7; Jeremiah 7:11\x*  
\v 47 Chujou chun, aman niseh leh Hou-In ah thu ahiljin, ahin thempuho, houdan thuhil ho chule adang mipi lamkai hon ama chu iti tha ding ham ti thilgon akisem pat un ahi.\x + \xo 19:47 \xt Lk 21:37\x*  
\v 48 Ahivangin ima dang ageldoh chom pouve, ajeh chu mijousen athuhil apomchah jeh chun.   
\c 20  
\s1 Jesun thuneidol adoh u  
\p
\v 1 Nikhat Jesun mipi thu ahil'a Kipana Thupha Hou-In'a aseiphong laiyin, thempu pipuiho, houdan thuhil ho, chule upaho cheng ahengah ahungun.  
\v 2 “Ipi thuneina noiya nangman hiche ho hi nabol ham? Kon thaneina napeh ham?” tin ahung dong uve.  
\v 3 “Ken thudoh khat nanei masauvinge” tin adonbut in,  
\v 4 “Twilutsah John thaneina chu van'a kon ham ahilouleh mihem a kon ham?” tin adongtai.  
\v 5 Amaho akihouvun, “Van'a kon ahi tileu hen, ibol'a John na tahsan lou u ham eiti kit diu.  
\v 6 Ahin iham tin mihem a kon ahi tileu hen, mipin songa eise kit diu, ajeh chu John chu themgao ahi tia apom'u ahi” akitiuvin ahi.  
\v 7 Hijeh chun achainakeiyin kahepouve tin ahin donbut tauve.  
\v 8 Chuin Jesun adonbut in, “Achutileh kenjong ipi thuneina noiya kabol ham ti naseipeh pouvinge,” ati.   
\s1 Lengpi-Lei Le Alei Lhouho Thulem  
\p
\v 9 Tun Jesun mipi lam angakit in hiche thusim hi aseipeh e: Mikhat hin lengpilei abol in, aloulhou miho kom'ah apedoh in, gamdang khat ah kum sottah thaam dingin achetai.\x + \xo 20:9 \xt Isa 5:1\x*  
\v 10 Lengpi ga khoptup phat alhin in, asohte khat ama chan ding lan asol'e. Ahin loulhou ho chun sohpa chu ahin bolseuvin, avouvin, khutgoh keovin ahin lesol tauve.  
\v 11 Hijeh chun lou neipan soh dang khat asol kit in, ahivangin ama hon ahinsujum kit un, avouvin, khutgoh keovin ahin lesol kit tauve.  
\v 12 Athumna pa asolkit in, chule ama jong chu ahin mavouvin adelmang tauve.”  
\v 13 “'Ipi kabol ding hitam?' tin louneipa akihoulim in ahi. 'Kahetai! Keiman kachapa kasahlut tah hi sol'inge. Tahbeh in jana hinpe nauvinte'” ati.  
\v 14 “Ahinlah, aloulhou hon achapa amu phat un, amaho akihou som'un, 'Agoulo ding pa ahunge, thatdoh utin agoulo ding hi eiho chang tau hite!'” akitiuve.  
\v 15 Hijeh chun ama chu lengpilei pam langah akaidoh un athat tauve. “Lengpilei neipa chun amaho chungah ipi bol'in te tia na ngaitouvam?” tin Jesun ahin dongin,  
\v 16 “Naseipeh unge–ama hungin tin loulhou ho chu athadoh a lengpilei chu midang asan sah ding ahitai” ati. “Iti khoh hitam chutobang thil aso jeng ding chu,” atiuvin athusei jaho chun ahin donbut uve.  
\v 17 Jesun amaho chu aven aseitai, “Achutileh, Pathen Lekhabun ipi atina ham? 'Insa hon apaidoh u song chu Inning songpin apangtai,'\x + \xo 20:17 \xt Labu 118:22\x*  
\v 18 Hiche songpia kipal jouse chu ahal hal'a keh ding, chule achunga lhu chu ipi hijongleh chip ding ahi” ati.  
\v 19 Houdan thuhil ho le thempu pipui hon Jesu chu kintah a mat ding adeilheh un ahi ajeh chu athusim sei chu amaho kiseina ahi ahin kihetdoh u ahitai–amaho chu loulhou agilou ho chu hiuvah ahi. Ahivangin mipi ho lethuhna chu akichauvin ahi.   
\s1 Caesar henga kaipeh thudol  
\p
\v 20 Phat kilemchang vepum'in, alamkai houvin avelhi le ding miphalhem asol uve. Jesun seikhel khat neihen Rome gamvaipo kom'ah amatna dingin kipedoh le ti agon u ahi.  
\v 21 ama hon “Houhil, Nangman adih chu nahil'a nasei ahi chule midang lunggel in nasuhboi joulou ahi keihon kaheuve.”  
\v 22 “Tun nei seipeh un–Caesar henga kai peh ding hi dih hai dihlou ham?” tin adong tauve.  
\v 23 Aman alungthim bol'u ahi chu ahen aseitai,  
\v 24 “Rome te sumpum khat nei vetsah un. Koi lim le thucheng kijih ham achunga chu?” tin adongtai. Ama hon adonbut un, “Caesar a ahi,” atiuve.  
\v 25 Aman asei kit in, “Aphai ahileh, Caesar a chu Caesar peuvin lang Pathen a chu Pathen peuvin,” ati.  
\v 26 Chuti chun ama hon mipi masanga athu seikhel'a kipalsah ding atiu chu ajou tapouve. Chusang chun, ama hon athu donbut ho chu kidang asauvin, athipchet tauve.   
\s1 Thina a kon thokitna thudol'a Jesu adoh u  
\p
\v 27 Chuin Jesu chu Sadducee–hou lamkai, thokitna aumpoi tihon kimupi din ahin naiyun ahi.\x + \xo 20:27 \xt Act 23:8\x*  
\v 28 Hiche thudoh hi adongun ahi: “Houhil, Mose’n dan khat eipeuvin, mikhat chu athia ajinu adalhah a chaneilou ahileh, asopipan hiche meithai chu akichenpi ding, cha aneipi ding hichun asopipa min apoh ding ahi.\x + \xo 20:28 \xt Danbu Ni Na 25:5\x*  
\v 29 Aphai, tun tekahnan ucha pasal sagi aum'e. A'upen ajineiyin chanei louvin athitai.  
\v 30 Hijeh chun anina pan akichenpin, ama jong athitai.  
\v 31 Chuin athumna pan akichenpi kit in ahi. Hiti hin asagiuvin achelhan abon'uva chaneilou ahi tauve.  
\v 32 Achainan numeinu jong athi tai.  
\v 33 Hijeh chun nei seipeh un, thokitna a chu koi ji a pang ding ham? Ajeh chu asagiuva chu akichenpi cheh u anahi!”  
\v 34 Jesun adonbut in, “Kichen hi hiche leiset chunga cheng miho ding bou ahi.  
\v 35 Ahin, ahunglhung ding khang'ah, athilah a konna thoudoh dinga lom ho chu akicheng tapouvin chule chen jong akichensah tapouve.  
\v 36 Chule amaho thikit talou diu, hitia chu amaho van'a Vantil te tobang hidiu ahitai. Amaho Pathen chate ahitauvin chule thoukit chate ahi tauve.”  
\v 37 “Ahin tun, mithi thoukit mong ding hinam ti thudol ah—Mose jengin jong naanglah a meikong thudol asut chun avetsah in ahi. Abraham, Isaac, le Jacob thijou phat sottah jou nungin, Pakai chu 'Abraham Pathen, Isaac Pathen, Jacob Pathen' tia akou ahi.\x + \xo 20:37 \xt Potdohbu 3:6\x*  
\v 38 Hijeh a chu ama chu ahingho Pathen ahin, athiho a hilou ahi, ajeh chu amaho abonchauva ama a hingah ahi tauve.”  
\v 39 Chukom mun'a ding, houdan thuhil ho phabep khat chun, “Nasei hoiye, houhil” atiuve.  
\v 40 Chule koiman thudoh adong ngam tapouvin ahi.   
\s1 Jesu David chapa ahina thua adoh u  
\p
\v 41 Chuin Jesun thudoh toh thon hiche hi aseipeh kit e, “Ipi jeh a Messiah chu David chapa kiti ding ham?  
\v 42 Ajeh chu David ama tah in jong Labua ana jihlut ahi: 'Pakaiyin ka Pakai jah a, Kajet lam'a kijana mun'ah touvin,”\x + \xo 20:42 \xt Labu 110:1\x*  
\v 43 Namelmate kasuh nem a, Nakengto chotpha a kakoi masang sen,' ati.  
\v 44 David in Messiah chu Pakai, tia akou leh, Messiah chu iti David chapa hithei ding ham?” ati.   
\s1 Jesun danthu sunho aphosal  
\p
\v 45 Chuin mihonpi jah dingin, aseijui te kom langah akiheiyin aseitai,  
\v 46 “Hiche houdan thuhil hoa kon hin kichih theiyun! Ajeh chu ama hon vonhoi tahtah kivon a kailhang lah dunga min chibai aboh diu adeiyun, chule kikhopna in le golvahna mun ho ah touna mun thupi lai lai aholjiuve.  
\v 47 Ahin, ama hon jahcha louhel in meithai ho anei agou uva konna lheplhah ding agel uvin, chule kilhagao misah tah bangin taona sottah tah japi lah a amang jiuvin ahi; hiche jeh a hi amaho hatah a bolgimna chang ding ahiuve,” ati.   
\c 21  
\s1 Meithainu Sumto  
\p
\v 1 Jesu Hou-In aumlaiyin, mihao hon sumdolna bom'a athilpeh hou chu aven ahi.  
\v 2 Chuin meithai mivaicha khat jong ahungin sumsan pehni alehlut in ahi.  
\v 3 Jesun aseitai, “Thutah ka seipeh nahiuve, hiche mivaicha meithainu hin adang jouse sangin atamto joi.  
\v 4 Ajeh chu ama hon aneival hou lah a themkhat bou atou ahin, amavang amanu hin, avaichat to-toh a, anei chasun apeh ahitai,” ati.   
\s1 Jesun ahunglhung ding asei masah  
\p
\v 5 Aseijui te lah a phabep khat chun Hou-In kisah na a song kikheng ho chule bang'a melchihna kijempah ho chu anatsat dan aseipan tauvin ahi. Ahivangin Jesun aseitai,  
\v 6 “Phat ahunglhung e, hiti ho jouse hi aboncha kisuchim ding ahi. Song khatcha khat chunga kisethom namulou diu ahi,” ati.  
\v 7 ama hon adongun, “Houhil, hitiho hi itih le soh ding ham? Melchihna itobangin hitiho chu soh ding ahitai ti eivetsah diu ham?” atiuve.  
\v 8 Aman adonbut in, “Koima kilheplhah sah hih un, ajeh chu mi tamtah kamin'a hung ding, ‘Keima Messiah kahi’ tia asei diu ‘Phat ahunglhung tai!’ ahinti diu ahi. Ahivangin tahsan hih un.  
\v 9 Chuleh gal kisat le thunoh najah tengu leh tija hih un. Ahinai, hiti ho hi soh masa ding ahi, ahin achaina chu hijeng loulai ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 10 Chuin aman aseiben, “Namkhat chu namkhat toh gal kisat a kon ding, chule lenggam khat jong lenggam dang khattoh kidou ding ahi.  
\v 11 Lingpi nasatah tah kihot ding, kellha ding, chule muntin'a gamna hise lang ding, tijat um tahtah thilsoh chule van'a melchihna kidangtahtah namu diu ahi.”  
\v 12 “Ahivanga hiche ho ahung so masanga, suhgenthei na phat nasatah um ding ahi. Nangho kikhopna intin le songkul hoa nakikai diu, chule kanungjui nahi jeh uva lengho le gamvaipo ho thutanna angsunga nadin diu ahi.  
\v 13 Ahivanga hiche hi nangho dinga keima nei seiphongna diu phat kilemchang chu hi ding ahi.  
\v 14 Hijeh chun nakihehset nau chu iti kadonbut dem tin lunggim masat dauvin,\x + \xo 21:14 \xt Lk 12:11,12\x*  
\v 15 ajeh chu keiman nangho thu adihtah chule chihna, na doudal teuvin nahin donbut theilouna diu ahilou le nanelkal joulouna diuva kapeh ding nahiuve!  
\v 16 Nakinaipi pen'u–nanu napa, nasopiho, na inkote, chule naloi le pai ho jengin jong nahin pehdoh nahlai diu ahi. Ama hon nangho abangkhat nahin tha nahlai diu ahi.  
\v 17 Chule mijousen kanungjui nahi jeh uva nahin muda diu ahi.  
\v 18 Amavang naluchung'a na samjang khat jeng jong mahthah louding ahi!  
\v 19 Dettah a nadin uleh, na lhagao naki huhdoh diu ahi.”   
\s1 Jesun Jerusalem kisuh mang ding asei masah  
\p
\v 20 “Chuleh nang hon Jerusalem galmi sepai hon aum kimvel namu tengu leh, nang hon alhuhna ding phat hunglhung ahitai ti nahet diu ahi.  
\v 21 Chuteng Judea gam'a cheng ho thinglhang langa najam doh diu ahi. Jerusalem'a umho napotdoh diu, chule thinglhang langa umdoh ho khopi langa nakile lou diu ahi.  
\v 22 Ajeh chu hiche ho chu Pathen phulah nikholai hi ding, chule Pathen Lekhabua themgao thusei ho guilhung ding ahi.\x + \xo 21:22 \xt Hosea 9:7\x*  
\v 23 Chuche nikholai chu numei naovop ho leh naosen sin minute dinga iti da um ding hitam. Ajeh chu gamsunga hesoh genthei khohtah chule hiche miho chunga lunghanna nasatah chuding ahi.  
\v 24 Amaho chemjam'a kithat diu ahilouleh sohchang'a vannoi nam jouse lah a solmanga um diu ahi. Chuleh chidang namdang te phatsung kichai kahsea Jerusalem hi chidang namdang ten achotpha ding ahi.”   
\s1 Mihem chapa hung kitna ding  
\p
\v 25 “Chule nisa, lha, chule ahsi hoa melchihna kidangtahtah hung um ding ahi. Chule leichung'a hi namtin boina a dim ding, twikhanglen kitum le twikinong gimnei chun asuh lungjing diu ahi.\x + \xo 21:25 \xt Isa 13:10; Ezekiel 32:7; Joel 2:31; Rev 6:12,13\x*  
\v 26 Miho chu leiset chunga thillhung ho amu uva konna kicha diu ahi, ajeh chu vanmun hoa thaneina cheng kihot ling gam ding ahitai.  
\v 27 Chuteng mijousen Mihem Chapa meilom chunga thahat le loupi tah a ahung amu diu ahi.\x + \xo 21:27 \xt Daniel 7:13; Rev 1:7\x*  
\v 28 Hijeh a chu hitiho jouse hi ahung kipat tengleh, dingun lang chunglam veuvin, ajeh chu nasochat nau nai ahitai!” ati.   
\s1 Theichang phunga tilkhouna  
\p
\v 29 Chuin aman hiche thutekah hi apen ahi: “Theichang phung khu veuvin, ahilou le thingphung dang hijongleh.  
\v 30 Ado ahung pullhah teng, nang hon seipeh louvin jong naheuve, nipi anaitai.  
\v 31 Chutobang chun, hitiho jouse aguilhun namu tengu leh, Pathen Lenggam chu anaitai ti nahet thei diu ahi.  
\v 32 Thutah ka seipeh nahiuve, hiche khang hi chemang louding ahi, hitiho jouse aguilhun masang sea.  
\v 33 Van le lei mang ding ahi, ahin kathu ho vang manglou beh ding ahi.”   
\s1 Kigin jingna dinga tilkhouna  
\p
\v 34 “Kihong phauvin! Nalungu, nopchonna le juneh motchonna jeh, chule tuhinkhoa lunggimna ho jeh in motsah hih un. Hiche nikho chu hetlou kah a thang banga kimatsah bol-hih un.  
\v 35 Ajeh chu hiche nikho chu leiset chunga hing mijouse chunga lhung ding ahi.  
\v 36 Phat jousen kiging jingin um'un. Chuleh hitobang kichat umtah hunglhung ding peldohna dia nahat jing theina diu le Mihem Chapa angsunga nadin jou theina diuvin taovun,” ati.  
\v 37 Niseh le Jesu Hou-In'ah thuhil dingin achejin, chule nilhah seh le Olive mol'a jan phat mang dingin ahung kile jin ahi.\x + \xo 21:37 \xt Lk 19:47\x*  
\v 38 Mihonpi chu Hou-In'ah jingkah seh le athuhil ngai dingin akikhom jiuvin ahi.   
\c 22  
\s1 Jesu thana ding agon u  
\p
\v 1 Cholsolou Changlhah Kut, Kalchuh Kut tia jong kihe chu ahung naitai.\x + \xo 22:1 \xt Potdohbu 12:1-27\x*  
\v 2 Thempu pipuiho leh houdan thuhil hon Jesu chu iti tha ding ham ti agong pan tauvin, ahin mipin ahin lethuh ding akichauvin ahi.  
\v 3 Chuin Judas Iscariot, seijui som le ni holah a khat, sungah Satan alut tan,  
\v 4 chule ama thempu pipuiho leh Hou-In ngahtup lamkaiho toh Jesu amaho henga pehdohna dinga lampi phapen ho kihoulim dingin achetai.  
\v 5 Amaho akipah un, sum peh dingin akitem tauve.  
\v 6 Chuti chun ama jong anom in chule Jesu pehdohna dinga phat kilemchang chu avelhi jingin, mihonpi umlou pet a amat theina diuvin avejinge.   
\ms1 Seijuihon Kalchuh Kut anneh ding angoh u  
\p
\v 7 Tun Cholsolou Changlhah Kut chu ahunglhung tai, Kalchuh Kut a kelngoi akitha chun.  
\v 8 Jesun Peter le John asol masan, “Chelhonin lang Kalchuh Kut anneh na ding hin gongtup lhon tan, thakhat a ineh khom theina diuvin” ati.  
\v 9 Amanin jong ahindong lhonin, “Hoilai mun'ah gongtup lhon leng natim?” ati lhon'e.  
\v 10 Aman adonbut in, “Jerusalem nalut lut lhon leh mikhat twibel a twi pu khat namu lhon ding ahi.” Ama chu juilhon'in. Alutna in a chun,  
\v 11 inneipa jah a seilhonin, 'Houhil'in adonge: jinlhun in, ka seijui te toh Kalchuh Kut an kanehna ding mun chu hoiba ham? ati tilhon'in.'  
\v 12 Aman indan chung ka-lentah gotsa um khat a napuilut lhon ding ahi. Hiche lai mun'a chu nangnin i-anneh diu nagon lhon ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 13 Amani khopi lam'a chun achelhonin ahileh ima jouse Jesun asei bang bangin agatoh lhonin chukom'a chun Kalchuh Kut anneh ahinsem lhon tai.  
\v 14 Phat ahung lhun phat in Jesu le aseijui te dokhang ah atoukhom tauve.   
\s1 Pakai Jan Anjon kiphudoh  
\p
\v 15 Jesun aseiye, “Ka thohgim kipat kah a hitobang Kalchuh Kut ankong nangho toh nehkhom ding hi kana ngalel jing ahi.  
\v 16 Ajeh chu tua ka seipeh nahiuve, Pathen Lenggam'a aguilhunna aum tokah a hiche an hi kaneh kit louding ahitai,” ati.  
\v 17 Chuin khon'a lengpitwi chu alan Pathen thangvahna apen ahi. Chuin aseitai, “Hiche hi kilah unlang nangho kihom un,  
\v 18 ajeh chu Pathen Lenggam ahung lhun kah a lengpitwi kadon louding ahitai,” ati.  
\v 19 Aman changlhah themkhat alan Pathen thangvahna apen ahi. Chuin ahehbal bal'in aseijui te apen, “Hiche hi katahsa, nangho dinga kipe chu ahi. Keima geldoh nan bol'un” ati.  
\v 20 Jan anneh jouvin, lengpitwi khon dang khat alan hitin aseiye, “Hiche khon hi Pathen le amite kikah a kitepna thah–kinoptona ka thisan a kisudet, nangho dinga kilhaina a kisunglha chu ahi,” ati.\x + \xo 22:20 \xt Jeremiah 31:31-34\x*  
\v 21 “Ahivangin hiche dokhang a hin, ilah uva jol le gol hina a tou, mikhat eipedoh ding aum'e.\x + \xo 22:21 \xt Labu 41:9\x*  
\v 22 Ajeh chu Mihem Chapa athi ding chu gotsa anahitai. Ahin, itobang lungkham nan anga hitam apedoh a pang pa chu,” ati.  
\v 23 Seijuite khat le khat akidongto un, alah uva koipen chun chutobang chu abol mong ding ham akitiuve.   
\s1 Let Thudol'a Kinelna  
\p
\v 24 Chuin amaho khat le khat alenpen koi ahidiu thu ah aki nelkal lah lah jeng tauve.\x + \xo 22:24 \xt Matt 18:1; Mk 9:34; Lk 9:46\x*  
\v 25 Jesun aseipeh un, “Hiche vannoi leiset a hin lengho le milen milal ten amiho potgih apohsah un ahin ‘mipi ho jol le gol’ tin akiminvo uve.  
\v 26 \x + \xo 22:26 \xt Matt 20:25-27; Mk 10:42-44\x*Ahin, nangho lah a vang achomdeu ngai ahi. Nalah uva alenpen chun panmun nem pen alo ngai ahi, chule alamkai chu soh tobang ahi ngai ahi.\x + \xo 22:26 \xt Matt 23:11; Mk 9:35\x*  
\v 27 Koi thupijo ham, dokhanga toupa le ajenlea pangpa? Ahinai, dokhanga toupa athupijo nai. Amavang hikom'a chutilou ahi! ajeh chu keima nangho lah a ajenlea kapan ahi.”\x + \xo 22:27 \xt Jn 13:12-15\x*  
\v 28 “Nanghon kathoh gentheina ah nei umpiuve.  
\v 29 Chule kapan Lenggam eipeh banga, kenjong tua thaneina kapeh nahiuve,  
\v 30 Chuche lenggam'a chu ka dokhanga naneh uva chule nadon theina diuvin. Chule nangho laltouna a natou diu Israel phungsom le phungni chunga thu natan diu ahi.”   
\s1 Jesun Peter in Aseilep Ding Asei Masah\x + \xo 22:30 \xt Matt 19:28\x*  
\p
\v 31 Simon, Simon, Satan in na boncha uvin chang kilhah chil banga lhah chil dingin nathum uve.  
\v 32 Ahivangin taona ah kathumpeh uve, Simon chule na tahsan chu alosap lou ngai ahi. Hijeh a chu nalung naheiya keilam a nahung kile kit teng nasopi ho suthahat in,” ati.  
\v 33 Peter in aseiyin, “Pakai, nangma to songkullut dinga kigosa kahi, chule thina hijongleh thi ngapcha kahi,” ati.  
\v 34 Ahivangin Jesun adonbut in, “Peter, thil khat naseipeh inge. Jing jingkah ahchal khon masanga, nangman thumvei nei seilep ding, kahe khapoi nati ding ahi,” ati.   
\s1 Sum, sakhao chule chemjam  
\p
\v 35 Chuin Jesun amaho chu adongin, “Keiman Kipana Thupha seiphonga kanasol uva, sum polou, sakhao kiken lou, ahilou le kengchot khel kiken louva naum uva chu ipi ngaichat nanei uvam?” atileh, ama hon adonbut un, “Imacha” atiuve.\x + \xo 22:35 \xt Matt 10:9,10; Mk 6:8,9; Lk 9:3; 10:4\x*  
\v 36 “Ahinlah tunvang nasum ule sakhao kipoh tauvin. Chule chemjam naneilou uleh naponsil joh unlang khat kichoh un!  
\v 37 Ajeh chu phat ahung lhunge kei chung changa hiche themgao thusei guilhunna dingin: ‘Ama adoudal hotoh akisimtha tai’ tia kisun chu. Henge keima chung changa kisun themgao thusei jouse guilhung ding ahi,” ati.\x + \xo 22:37 \xt Isa 53:12\x*  
\v 38 “Ven Pakai” tin ahin donbut un, “Chemjam ni eiho lah a aumnai,” atiuvin, “Hichu aphatai,” tin aseiye.   
\s1 Gethsemane honcsunga Jesu atao  
\p
\v 39 Chuin, seijui te toh kivop in, Jesun indan chung adalhan chule abolngai ma bangin Olive mol langah achetai.  
\v 40 Hiche a chun amaho aseipeh in, “Taovun, lhepna a nalhah louna diuvin,” ati.  
\v 41 Themkhat, song sephahna thei chan bep ah, ache chon jep in, chule adilsun ataotai,  
\v 42 “Hepa, nalung ahileh, lungsettah in thoh gentheina khon hi keiya kon'in ladoh in. Ahin, keima lunggot hilouvin, nangma lunggot joh akibol ding kadeiye,” ati.  
\v 43 Chuin van'a kon'in vantil khat ahung kilah in chule atha asuhhat peh in ahi.  
\v 44 Ama lungluttah in ataoben, chule alhagao thohgim natsat dan chu, a-ulsa chu thisan vat lentah tah bangin alenglhan ahi.  
\v 45 Achainan adingdoh kit in aseijui te hengah ahung kilen ahileh ana ihmut u ahung mun, lungkhamna a kon joilha gamu ahitai.  
\v 46 “Ipi bol'a na imut uham?” tin adongin, “Thoudoh unlang taovun, lhepna a nalhah lut louna dingun,” ati.   
\s1 Jesu chu bengchop pum a kijohdoh  
\p
\v 47 Ahivangin Jesun chutia asei jeng vang chun, mihonpin ahin nai pheiyun, Judas, seijui som le ni lah a khat, in ahin lamkai ahi. Judas jong Jesu kom langah chibai boh a chop dingin achen ahi.  
\v 48 Ahin Jesun aseiyin, “Judas, nangman Mihem Chapa hi chop a pehdoh ding nagot ham?” ati.  
\v 49 Seijui dang hon thilsoh ding chu amu phat un ahung eojah un, “Pakai, ikidelpi diu ham? Chemjam kahin pouve!” ahin tiuve.  
\v 50 Chule alah uva khat chun Thempu Chungnung sohpa jetlang kol asatlhah peh in ahi.  
\v 51 Ahin Jesun aseiyin, “Kidoupi tahih un,” atin chule mipa kol chu atham in asuhdam peh e.  
\v 52 Chuin Jesun ama man dinga hungho thempu pipuiho, Hou-In ngah lamkaiho, chule upaho kom'ah thu aseiye. Amaho chu adongin, “Keima tijat umtah doudal natong kahim, chemjam toh moltum thoa keima man dinga nahung u?  
\v 53 Ipi jeh a Hou-In a neimat lou uham? Keima niseh a ana kium jinga. Ahivangin tuhi naphat u ahi, muthim thaneinan vai apoh pet ahi,” ati.\x + \xo 22:53 \xt Lk 19:47; 21:37\x*   
\s1 Peter in Jesu aseilep  
\p
\v 54 Hijeh chun ama hon aman'un Thempu Chungnung pa in'ah apuiphei tauve. Chule Peter chun galkang in ahinjuiye.  
\v 55 Angah ho chun leitol lailunga chu mei atiuva toubem u ahin, chule Peter jong agajaovin ahi.  
\v 56 Soh numei chapang khat in mei kitivahna a kon chun ahin mun ama chu ave vejeng tai. Achainan amanun ahinseiyin, “Hiche mipa hi Jesu nungjui holah a khat ahi,” ahin ti.  
\v 57 Ahin Peter in aseilep in, “Numei, ama khu koi ahi jong kahet lou ahi,” ati.  
\v 58 Chomkhat jouvin koiham khat in ahinven aseitai, “Nang jong amaho lah a khat nahi tei ding ahi,” ati. Peter in adonbut in, “Ahipoiye, kahipoi,” ati.  
\v 59 Nidan khat jou lang hin koiham khat in angoh kit in, “Hiche mipa jong hi amaho lah a khat hitei tei ding ahi, ajeh chu ama jong Galilee gammi ahi,” ati.  
\v 60 Ahivangin Peter in aseiyin, “Ipi nasei ham kahe hihbeh e,” atitai. Chuin chutia asei laitah chun ahchal ahung khong tai.  
\v 61 Hiche pettah chun Pakai chu ahung kiheiyin Peter chu ahin ven ahi. Kinloitah in Peter lungsung'ah Pakai thusei ho chu ahung kilangin: “Ahkhon masanga, jing jingkah le, nangman nei seilep ding, kahe khapoi nati ding ahi” ati chu.  
\v 62 Chuin Peter chun leitol adalhan, lainatah in agakap tai.   
\s1 Jesu totnopna a aneiyu chule achunga khut alhau  
\p
\v 63 Jesu ngah a pangho lah a mopopa chun totnopnan aneiyin chule avopan tai.  
\v 64 Amit atompeh un, “Gaovin lang seiyin, koiham nadeng'a chu?” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 65 Chule ama suhjum nan bolthei jouse abol'un ahi.   
\s1 Hou Vaipo Ho Ang-Sunga Jesu  
\p
\v 66 Jingkho avah in, upaho jouse, thempu pipuiho leh houdan thuhil ho pan nan akikhom un ahi. Jesu chu akikhom mipi angsung'ah ahin puiyun,  
\v 67 chule ama hon adongun, “Nei seipeh un nangma Messiah chu nahim?” atiuve. Ahivangin aman adonbut in, “Naseipeh uleng, nei tahsan lou diu ahi.  
\v 68 Chule thudoh naneiyu leng nei donbut lou diu ahi.  
\v 69 Ahin, tu apat a Mihem Chapa hi thaneitah a Pathen khut jetlam a tou ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 70 Amaho abonchauvin ahung eojah jeng'un, “Ahileh, Pathen Chapa kahie natina ham?” ahinti uve. Chuin aman adonbut in, “Naseiyu chu kahi” ati.  
\v 71 Chuin ama hon, “Ipi dinga hettohsah dang ingaikhoh uham? Eiho tah in athusei ija tauve,” atiuve.   
\c 23  
\s1 Pilate in Jesu thudoh anei  
\p
\v 1 Chuin mipi kikhom chengse chun Jesu chu Rome Gamvaipo, Pilate hengah ahinpui tauve.  
\v 2 ama hon apansat nau thu chu aseipan un: “Hiche mipa hin kamiteu apuileng'in, Rome solkal kom'a kai pehlou ding tin aseiyin chule ama tah jong Messiah, Leng akihisah e,” atiuve.  
\v 3 Hijeh chun Pilate in ama chu adongin, “Nangma Juda te Lengpa nahim?” ati. Jesun adonbut in, “Kahi chu nasei khai” ati.  
\v 4 Pilate chu thempu pipuiho leh mihonpi hengah ahung kiheiyin chule aseitai, “Hiche mipa chunga hin ima adihlou kamupoi!” ati.   
\s1 Herod angsunga Jesu  
\p
\v 5 Chuin ama hon asei teitei jengun, “Ahivanga, ama hin achena chan'a athuhil a konna boina asem jing jeng ahi–Judea pumpia, Galilee a pat Jerusalem geiya!” atiuve.  
\v 6 “Oh, Galilee gammi ham?” tin Pilate in ahin dong'e.  
\v 7 ama hon ahi atipeh phat un, Pilate in Herod Antipas kom'a dingin asol tai, ajeh chu Galilee chu Herod vaipohna noi anahi, chule Herod jong chu Jerusalem a aumpet anahi khan ahi.  
\v 8 Herod in Jesu mu na dinga phat hoitah amujeh chun akitai lheh jengin ahi, ajeh chu ama chung chang thudol anajah a chule sot apat a thil kidang abol ho ana munom ten ahi.  
\v 9 Aman Jesu chu thudoh tamtah adongin, ahivangin Jesun adonbut nom poi.  
\v 10 Hiche lai chun thempu pipuiho leh houdan thuhil ho chua chun adingun ahehsetna thu u chu asam un ahi.  
\v 11 Chuin Herod le asepai ten Jesu chu totnopnan aneiyun adai chavai pan tauve. Achainan, ama hon leng ponsil asilpeh un Pilate hengah ahin lesol tauve.  
\v 12 (Herod le Pilate, masanga kimelmah teni chu, hiche ni chun jol le gol ahung hilhon'e).   
\s1 Jesu Tha Dinga Athu Atan-U  
\p
\v 13 Chuin Pilate in thempu pipuiho leh hou lamkai adang ho, mipi ho jaonan, akoukhom in,  
\v 14 chule athulhuh sem aphongdoh in ahi. “Nanghon hiche mipa hi kakom'a nahin puiyun, doudal natoh atonge tia ngohna naneiyu ahi. Keiman hiche thudol'a hin phatah in nangho mitmun kavelhan chule bolset neilou ahi kamudoh e.  
\v 15 Herod in jong themmona amulou jeh a eiho kom'a ahin lesol ahi. Thina thei chan gotna pehna ding natoh hiche mipan abolpoi.  
\v 16 Hijeh chun keiman gimbolna peing ting, hin lhadoh tange,” ahinti.  
\v 17 Ajeh chu kut sunga chu ama hon mikhat alhadoh jing'u ahi.  
\v 18 Chutah chun mihonpi lah a kon chun awgin sangtah ahung gingin, thakhat tah in ahin sam'un, “Ama hi thatdoh in, chule Barabbas chu nei lhadoh peh un!” atiuve.  
\v 19 (Barabbas chu agam solkal douna natoh jeh le toltha jeh a songkul'a kikhum anahi.)  
\v 20 Pilate in amaho anelkal'in ahi, ajeh chu aman Jesu alhadoh nom jeh ahi.  
\v 21 Ahivangin ama hon asam sam jengun, “Thingpel'a khenbeh in! thingpel'a khenbeh in!” atiuve.  
\v 22 Athumvei channa din aman adongin, “Ipi bol'in em? Ipi themmona aneiyem? Keiman thina chan'a gotna pehna ding thu ima kamupoi. Hijeh chun hin vogim ingting hin lhadoh tange,” ati.  
\v 23 Ahivangin mihonpi chun awsang jep in ahasap cheh un, Jesu chu thingpel'a khetbeh ahina din athum'un, chule a-awgin u chun ajoujo tai.  
\v 24 Hijeh chun Pilate in Jesu chu angeh dungjuiyun athi dingin atanlhah peh tai.  
\v 25 ama hon athum dungjuiyun Barabbas, michohnoh le toltha jeh a songkul'a umpa, alhadoh peh in ahi. Ahin Jesu vang chu amaho khut ah anop nop alo diuvin apedoh tai.   
\s1 Jesu thingpel a kikhetbeh  
\p
\v 26 Chutia Jesu ahin puidoh uchun, Simon kiti Cyrene gam mi khat thinglhang langa pat a ahung pettah anahi. Sepai ho chun aman un thingpel chu achungah akoiyun Jesu nunga chun apohsah tauve.  
\v 27 Mihonpi tamtah in anung ahinjuiyun, a-op chum'a kap nupiho jong ahiuve.  
\v 28 Ahivangin Jesu amaho langah akiheiyin aseitai, “Jerusalem chanute, keiya dingin kap hih'un, amavang nangho le nachateu dingin kap jouvin.  
\v 29 Ijeh inem itile ama hon hitia aseina diu nikho hunglhung ding ahi. 'Cha neilou numeiho, naovop khalou naobu, chule nao noichepsah khalou ho anunnom uve,' kiti ding ahi.  
\v 30 Mihon mol ho jah a ‘Neilhuh khum'un’ tia athum dingu, lhang jah a ‘neikhu khum'un’ atidiu ahi.\x + \xo 23:30 \xt Hosea 10:8; Rev 6:16\x*  
\v 31 Ajeh chu thingphung ahinlai'a bon hitia hi abol ule, iti da ding ham agot teng?” ati.  
\v 32 Adang mini, anilhona miphalou, teni jong chu ama toh tha tha dingin ahin puidoh uve.  
\v 33 Lugu mun atinau mun ahung lhun phat un, ama hon thingpel ah thingkil'in akilbeh un ahi. Chuleh miphalou teni jong chu akhetbeh tauve–khat ajet ah chule khat aveiyah.  
\v 34 Jesun aseitai, “Hepa, ngaidam in, ajeh chu ipi abol'u ahepouve,” ati. Chule sepai hon aponsil chu vang asang'un achang ding akive lhauve.\x + \xo 23:34 \xt Labu 22:18\x*  
\v 35 Mihonpi chun aveuvin chule alamkai hon ajontai'un. “Aman midang ho ahuhhingin” tin ama hon aseiyun, “Ama le ama kihuhhing tahta Pathen thaonu, Akilhengdoh pa chu ahi mong mong leh,” atiuvin ahi.\x + \xo 23:35 \xt Labu 22:7\x*  
\v 36 Sepai hon jong adai chavaiyun, don ding juthuh apeuvin ahi.\x + \xo 23:36 \xt Labu 69:21\x*  
\v 37 Ama ahin kou uvin, “Nangma Juda te lengpa nahileh, kihuhhing in!” atiuve.  
\v 38 Achungah chun melchihna khat atah uvin, “Hiche hi Juda te lengpa ahi” tin asun uve.   
\s1 Miphalou pan Jesu atahsan  
\p
\v 39 Miphalou akikhetbehpi teni khatpa chun ahin jontaiyin, “Nang, Messiah nahi hilou ham?” Nahi vetsahnan nang le nang kihuhhing in lang chule keini jong neihuhdoh lhon tang'em, hitia na thohgim laihin! ati.  
\v 40 Ahivangin miphalou khatpa chun ahin phohsal in, “Pathen nagin lou ham athi dinga naum kisan'a?  
\v 41 Eini hi athi dinga lom ihi ithil bolkhel jeh a, ahin hiche pa hin imacha bolkhel aneipoi,” ati.  
\v 42 Chuin aman aseitai, “Jesu, nei geldoh in na lenggam'a nahung teng,” ati.  
\v 43 Jesun adonbut in, “Tahbeh a ka seipeh nahi, tunia Paradise a iumkhom ding ahi,” ati.   
\s1 Jesu thingpel chunga athi  
\p
\v 44 Hiche phat hi sunkim dontah ahin, chule nidan thum chan in gamsung pumpi muthim ahung jingin ahi.\x + \xo 23:44 \xt Potdohbu 26:31-33\x*  
\v 45 Nisa a kon vah achemang in, chule kinloitah in Hou-In muntheng'a pondal chu akimlai tah a akehlhasuh in ahi.  
\v 46 Chutah chun Jesu ahung peng in, “Pa, nakhut ah kalhagao kapedoh e” ati. Chule chuche thucheng asei toh kilhonin ahinna alhatai.\x + \xo 23:46 \xt Labu 31:5\x*  
\v 47 Rome sepai jalamkaipa, kithana velhalea pang pan thilsoh umchan chu amun, Pathen chibai aboh in aseitai, “Hiche mipa vang michonpha ahi,” ati.  
\v 48 Chuleh mihonpi akikhetbeh ve'a hung sesen jong thilsoh umchan chu amu uvin, amaho lungkham tah in inlam ache tauve.  
\v 49 Ahivangin Jesu jol le golte, Galilee gam'a pat a hinjui numeiho chengtoh, amaho chu gamla thimtah in adingun ahin galvet uve.   
\s1 Jesu Long Avui-U\x + \xo 23:49 \xt Lk 8:2,3\x*  
\p
\v 50 Tun Joseph kiti mipha le chondih tah khat aum'e. Ama chu Juda te vaipoloi lah a khat ahi.  
\v 51 Ahin aman houlamkai dang ho thulhuh sem le natoh chu ana noppeh lou ahi. Ama chu Judea gam'a Arimathea khoa kon ahi, chule Pathen Lenggam hung ding chu anga jing ahi.  
\v 52 Ama Pilate kom'a achen Jesu long chu athum'in ahi.  
\v 53 Chuin aman atahsa chu thingpel a pat in alalhan, tupat ponnem ajolsao thimtah khat in atom in, chule song kilai lhanthah khat ah alupsah tai.  
\v 54 Hiche chu kigotni nilhangkai don a vaigei thimtah a kibol ahi, ajeh chu Cholngahni kipat ding kon cha ahitai.  
\v 55 Atahsa akilah mang phat chun, Galilee apat a hung numei ho chun ahin juiyun, atahsa kikoina lhan chu agamu uvin ahi.  
\v 56 Chuin inlam acheuvin chule thil namtui le atahsa a nuding nuthei akisem uvin ahi. Ahin athilsem u ajo phat un Cholngahni anakipan tai, hijeh chun dan thun angeh dungjuijin akichol tauve.\x + \xo 23:56 \xt Potdohbu 20:10; Danbu Ni Na 5:14\x*   
\c 24  
\s1 Jesu thodoh kitna  
\p
\v 1 Ahin nimasani jingpi tah in, numeiho chu lhan lam'ah acheuvin, thil namtui asem u jong akichoiyun ahi.  
\v 2 Lhan sung lutna a um song ana kitangdoh chu agamu uve.  
\v 3 Hijeh chun alut un, ahivangin Jesu long chu amu tapouve.  
\v 4 Chutia lungboi tah a adin laitah un, mini apettah in ahung kilah in, ponbang vallah lah akisil lhone.  
\v 5 Numei ho chu atijauvin chule amaiyu tol'ah akunlhah sah un ahi. Chuin miteni chun ahin sei lhonin, “Ipi bol'a athiho lah a ahingdoh khat nahol uham?  
\v 6 Ama hikom'ah aum tapoi! Ama athilah a kon'in athoudoh tai! Galilee a aumlaiya nana seipeh ho'u chu geldoh un,\x + \xo 24:6 \xt Matt 16:21; 17:22,23; 20:18,19; Mk 8:31; 9:31; 10:33,34; Lk 9:22; 18:31-33\x*  
\v 7 Mihem Chapa michonse ho khut a pehdoh a um ding, thingpel'a akhetbeh diu, chule anithum ni le thoukit ding ahi, tia anasei chu,” atilhon e.  
\v 8 Chuin ama hon hiche hi anasei mongnai ti ageldoh un ahi.  
\v 9 Hijeh chun amaho lhan mun'a kon'in aseijui som le khat ho–chule adang ho jouse–thilsoh umchan seipeh dingin kintah in akile loi tauve.  
\v 10 Solchah ho thilsoh umchan seipeh chu Mary Magdalene, Joanna, James nu Mary, chule numei adang ho jong ahiuve.  
\v 11 Ahivangin miho ding chun athusim jah u chu mohthu homkeo danin agel uvin, hijeh chun atahsan tapouve.  
\v 12 Ahin Peter vang chu achomdoh in lhan veding chun alhaijel'in ahi. Abung'in aven ahileh tompon akeova um bouseh chu amun, chuin inlam akile kit in, ipi iti hitam alungdong lheh jeng tai.   
\s1 Emmaus Kho Lampia Jesu Akilah  
\p
\v 13 Hiche ni mama chun Jesu nungjui mini, Emmaus kho jotna lampi, Jerusalem a pat mile sagia gamla achun ache lhone.  
\v 14 Amanin lamjot toh thilsoh umchan jouse chung chang thudol kihoulim toh akop lhon ahi.  
\v 15 Hitiho jouse thu akihoulim lhon laiyin, Jesu jong ama tah kinloi tah in ahungin amani toh alhon khom tai.  
\v 16 Ahivangin Pathen'in ahetdoh lhon louna din aumsah e.  
\v 17 Aman adongin, “Nalamjot pum lhon'a chu ipi thu lom lunglut tah a nakihoulim lhon hitaimo?” ati. Chomkhat akhongai lhonin, amaiso lhon lungkhamna maiso apulhonin.  
\v 18 Chuin amani lah a khat pa, Cleopas chun adonbut in, “Tu niphabep masanga thilsoh ho jouse helou Jerusalem miho lah a nang bouseh hin nate,” ati lhon'e.  
\v 19 Jesun adongin, “Ipi thilsoh ho am?” ati. “Nazareth a hung kon Jesu chunga thilsoh umchan ho,” tin aseipeh lhontai, “Ama thil kidang nasatah bolthei themgao khat anahin, chule Pathen le miho mitmu a thaneitah houhil ahi.  
\v 20 Ahivangin kathempu pipuihou le adang hou lamkai hon thina chan gotna chang din themmo achan'un, chule ama hon thingpel'ah akhenbeh tauve.  
\v 21 Keihon Israel huhdoh dinga hungpa Messiah chu ahi tia kakineppiu ahi. Hiche hi nithum masanga thilsoh ahitai.  
\v 22 Chuti chun keiho lah a ama nungjui numei phabep khat tujingkah matah chun alhan'ah aum uvin, chule amaho ahung kileuvin kidangtah thulhut ahinpo uvin ahi.  
\v 23 ama hon atahsa akiholmoi atiuvin, chule vantil amu uvin, aman Jesu ahingkit tai ati.  
\v 24 Keiho lah a pasal phabep khat ave dingin alhaidoh un, atahbeh in, Jesu long chu numei ho seibang chun anaum tapoi,” ati lhon'e.  
\v 25 Chuin Jesun amani jah a, “Vo lungthim bei miho! Themgao hon Pathen Lekhabua ajihlut ho tahsan ding hahsa nasah uve.  
\v 26 Messiah chu aloupina a alut masanga hitiho jouse hi athoh galkai ding ahi ti kichen tah a kivetsah ana hilou ham?” ati.  
\v 27 Chuin Jesun amani chu Mose le themgao lekhasut ho jouse le Pathen Lekhabu jousea kipat in ama chung chang hilchet abolpeh in ahi.  
\v 28 Hiche pet a hi amaho Emmaus kho lhung koncha ahi tauve. Jesu chu achejom ding danin aum'in,  
\v 29 ahin amanin alho lhonin, “Tujan keini kom'ah gehtan, ajeh chu avaigei tai,” ati lhon'e. Hiti chun ama jong amani chutoh alhon tai.  
\v 30 Anne dinga atoulhah uchun, aman changlhah chu alan phatthei aboh'e. Chuin ahehbal in amani chu apen ahi.  
\v 31 Chupet tah chun amit lhon ahung hahdoh in, chule amanin koi ahi chu ahin hedoh lhon tai. Chuin hiche pettah chun Ama amangtai!  
\v 32 Amani khat in khat jah a asei lhonin, “Lampia ikihoulim uva Pathen Lekhabu hilchet abola chu ilungchang lhon kileojap bang lou ham?” ati lhon'e.  
\v 33 Chule hiche nidan kah sung mama chun Jerusalem langah akile lhon tai. Chua chun seijui som le khat le adang amaho toh ana kikhom khom ho amu lhonin,  
\v 34 ama hon, “Pakai chu tahbeh in athoudoh tai! Peter henga akilah'e!” tin ahinsei uve.  
\v 35 Chuin Emmaus khoa pat hung tenin jong amani thusim, Jesu aheng lhona lampia akijot laiyuva ahung kilah dan, chule changlhah ahin hebal phat a ahin hetdoh lhon dan, asei lhonin ahi.   
\s1 Jesu aseijui te henga akilah  
\p
\v 36 Chule chutia asei laitah uvin, Jesu alah uva hetmanlou kah in ana dingin ahi. Aman ahin seijin, “Chamnan naumpiu hen,” ahinti.  
\v 37 Ahivangin amaho abonchauvin atijauvin akichauvin, thilha mudan'in akigel uve!  
\v 38 “Ipi jeh a kicha nahiu ham?” tin ahin dongin, “Ipi bol'a nalung sungu chu lungthoina a dim ham?  
\v 39 Kakhut veuvin, kakeng veuvin, nang hon keima mong mong kahinai ti namu uve. Nei tham uvin lang thilha kahilou hi hechen un, ajeh chu thilhan tahsa mel tua neimu bangu hi aneipoi,” ati.  
\v 40 Thu aseitoh thon akhut le akeng avetsah in ahi.  
\v 41 Chuti chun amaho tahsan loutah in ading jing nalaiyun, kipana le lungdon nan adimset un ahi. Chuin aman ajah uva, “Neh ding nanei uvam?” ahinti.   
\p
\v 42 ama hon nga kikang khat apeuvin ahi,  
\v 43 chule aman hichu anen ama hon aveuve.  
\v 44 Chuin Aman aseiyin, “Masanga nangho toh iumkhom laiyuva, kana seipeh soh nahi tauve, Kei chung chang thudol Mose danthua, themgao ho lekhabua, chule labua kisun jouse chu guilhung ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 45 Chuin aman alungkot u Pathen Lekhabua thu ho ahettheina diuvin ahonpeh in ahi.  
\v 46 Chuin aseitai, “Henge, masanglai a pat a chu Messiah hi thohgim ding chule thi ding chule anithum ni le athilah a konna thoudoh ding tia ana kisun ahi.  
\v 47 Hitia jong hi ana kisun ahi, hiche thu hi namtin jouse henga amin thaneina a seiphonga um ding ahi, Jerusalem a kipan ding: ‘Chonset ngaidamna alunghei jousea dingin aum'e.’  
\v 48 Nangho hiche ho jouse hettohsah nahiuve.”  
\v 49 “Chuleh tua Lhagao Theng kahinsol peh ding nahiuve, kapa ana kitepna banga. Ahin Lhagao Theng ahung'a van'a kon thilbol theina nadimset tokah uvin hiche khopi a hin um uvin,” ati.\x + \xo 24:49 \xt Act 1:4\x*   
\s1 Jesu van'a akaltou  
\p
\v 50 Chuin Jesun amaho chu Bethany langah apuiyin, vanlam'a akhut alhaangin amaho chu phatthei aboh'e.\x + \xo 24:50 \xt Act 1:9-11\x*  
\v 51 Amaho phatthei aboh laitah in, amaho chu adalhan chule van langah lahtouvin aumtai.  
\v 52 Hijeh chun ama hon ama chu ahouvun chuin Jerusalem lamah kipana dimset pumin ahung kile tauve.  
\v 53 Chuin aphat jouseu chu Hou-In ah Pathen vahchoinan amang tauve.   